var book = {
	"name": "Isaiah",
	"numChapters": 66,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The vision<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17656A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17656A\"></sup> concerning Judah and Jerusalem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17656B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17656B\"></sup> that Isaiah son of Amoz saw<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17656C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17656C\"></sup> during the reigns of Uzziah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17656D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17656D\"></sup> Jotham,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17656E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17656E\"></sup> Ahaz<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17656F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17656F\"></sup> and Hezekiah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17656G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17656G\"></sup> kings of Judah.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Hear me, you heavens! Listen, earth!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17657H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17657H\"></sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17657I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17657I\"></sup>“I reared children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17657J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17657J\"></sup> and brought them up,but they have rebelled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17657K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17657K\"></sup> against me.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The ox knows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17658L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17658L\"></sup> its master,the donkey its owner’s manger,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17658M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17658M\"></sup>but Israel does not know,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17658N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17658N\"></sup>my people do not understand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17658O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17658O\"></sup>”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Woe to the sinful nation,a people whose guilt is great,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17659P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17659P\"></sup>a brood of evildoers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17659Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17659Q\"></sup>children given to corruption!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17659R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17659R\"></sup>They have forsaken<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17659S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17659S\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;they have spurned the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17659T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17659T\"></sup> of Israeland turned their backs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17659U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17659U\"></sup> on him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Why should you be beaten<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17660V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17660V\"></sup> anymore?Why do you persist<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17660W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17660W\"></sup> in rebellion?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17660X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17660X\"></sup>Your whole head is injured,your whole heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17660Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17660Y\"></sup> afflicted.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17660Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17660Z\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>From the sole of your foot to the top of your head<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17661AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17661AA\"></sup>there is no soundness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17661AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17661AB\"></sup>—only wounds and welts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17661AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17661AC\"></sup>and open sores,not cleansed or bandaged<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17661AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17661AD\"></sup>or soothed with olive oil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17661AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17661AE\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Your country is desolate,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17662AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17662AF\"></sup>your cities burned with fire;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17662AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17662AG\"></sup>your fields are being stripped by foreigners<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17662AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17662AH\"></sup>right before you,laid waste as when overthrown by strangers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17662AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17662AI\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Daughter Zion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17663AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17663AJ\"></sup> is left<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17663AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17663AK\"></sup>like a shelter in a vineyard,like a hut<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17663AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17663AL\"></sup> in a cucumber field,like a city under siege.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Unless the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almightyhad left us some survivors,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17664AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17664AM\"></sup>we would have become like Sodom,we would have been like Gomorrah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17664AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17664AN\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17665AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17665AO\"></sup>you rulers of Sodom;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17665AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17665AP\"></sup>listen to the instruction<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17665AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17665AQ\"></sup> of our God,you people of Gomorrah!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17665AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17665AR\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“The multitude of your sacrifices—what are they to me?” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“I have more than enough of burnt offerings,of rams and the fat of fattened animals;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17666AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17666AS\"></sup>I have no pleasure<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17666AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17666AT\"></sup>in the blood of bulls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17666AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17666AU\"></sup> and lambs and goats.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17666AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17666AV\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When you come to appear before me,who has asked this of you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17667AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17667AW\"></sup>this trampling of my courts?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Stop bringing meaningless offerings!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17668AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17668AX\"></sup>Your incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17668AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17668AY\"></sup> is detestable<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17668AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17668AZ\"></sup> to me.New Moons,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17668BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17668BA\"></sup> Sabbaths and convocations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17668BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17668BB\"></sup>—I cannot bear your worthless assemblies.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Your New Moon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17669BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17669BC\"></sup> feasts and your appointed festivals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17669BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17669BD\"></sup>I hate with all my being.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17669BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17669BE\"></sup>They have become a burden to me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17669BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17669BF\"></sup>I am weary<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17669BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17669BG\"></sup> of bearing them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>When you spread out your hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17670BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17670BH\"></sup> in prayer,I hide<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17670BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17670BI\"></sup> my eyes from you;even when you offer many prayers,I am not listening.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17670BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17670BJ\"></sup>Your hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17670BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17670BK\"></sup> are full of blood!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17670BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17670BL\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Wash<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17671BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17671BM\"></sup> and make yourselves clean.Take your evil deeds out of my sight;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17671BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17671BN\"></sup>stop doing wrong.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17671BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17671BO\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Learn to do right;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17672BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17672BP\"></sup> seek justice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17672BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17672BQ\"></sup>Defend the oppressed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17672BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17672BR\"></sup>Take up the cause of the fatherless;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17672BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17672BS\"></sup>plead the case of the widow.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17672BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17672BT\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Come now, let us settle the matter,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17673BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17673BU\"></sup>says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“Though your sins are like scarlet,they shall be as white as snow;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17673BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17673BV\"></sup>though they are red as crimson,they shall be like wool.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17673BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17673BW\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>If you are willing and obedient,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17674BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17674BX\"></sup>you will eat the good things of the land;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17674BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17674BY\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>but if you resist and rebel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17675BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17675BZ\"></sup>you will be devoured by the sword.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17675CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17675CA\"></sup>For the mouth of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17675CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17675CB\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>See how the faithful cityhas become a prostitute!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17676CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17676CC\"></sup>She once was full of justice;righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17676CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17676CD\"></sup> used to dwell in her—but now murderers!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17676CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17676CE\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Your silver has become dross,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17677CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17677CF\"></sup>your choice wine is diluted with water.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Your rulers are rebels,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17678CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17678CG\"></sup>partners with thieves;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17678CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17678CH\"></sup>they all love bribes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17678CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17678CI\"></sup>and chase after gifts.They do not defend the cause of the fatherless;the widow’s case does not come before them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17678CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17678CJ\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Therefore the Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty,the Mighty One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17679CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17679CK\"></sup> of Israel, declares:“Ah! I will vent my wrath on my foesand avenge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17679CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17679CL\"></sup> myself on my enemies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17679CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17679CM\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I will turn my hand against you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17680CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17680CN\"></sup>I will thoroughly purge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17680CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17680CO\"></sup> away your dross<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17680CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17680CP\"></sup>and remove all your impurities.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17680CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17680CQ\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I will restore your leaders as in days of old,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17681CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17681CR\"></sup>your rulers as at the beginning.Afterward you will be called<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17681CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17681CS\"></sup>the City of Righteousness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17681CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17681CT\"></sup>the Faithful City.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17681CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17681CU\"></sup>”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Zion will be delivered with justice,her penitent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17682CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17682CV\"></sup> ones with righteousness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17682CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17682CW\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But rebels and sinners<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17683CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17683CX\"></sup> will both be broken,and those who forsake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17683CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17683CY\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will perish.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17683CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17683CZ\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“You will be ashamed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17684DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17684DA\"></sup> because of the sacred oaks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17684DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17684DB\"></sup>in which you have delighted;you will be disgraced because of the gardens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17684DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17684DC\"></sup>that you have chosen.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>You will be like an oak with fading leaves,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17685DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17685DD\"></sup>like a garden without water.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The mighty man will become tinderand his work a spark;both will burn together,with no one to quench the fire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17686DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17686DE\"></sup>”"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>This is what Isaiah son of Amoz saw concerning Judah and Jerusalem:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17687B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17687B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>In the last days<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17688C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17688C\"></sup>the mountain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17688D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17688D\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s temple will be establishedas the highest of the mountains;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17688E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17688E\"></sup>it will be exalted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17688F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17688F\"></sup> above the hills,and all nations will stream to it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17688G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17688G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Many peoples<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17689H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17689H\"></sup> will come and say,“Come, let us go<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17689I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17689I\"></sup> up to the mountain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17689J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17689J\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,to the temple of the God of Jacob.He will teach us his ways,so that we may walk in his paths.”The law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17689K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17689K\"></sup> will go out from Zion,the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> from Jerusalem.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17689L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17689L\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He will judge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17690M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17690M\"></sup> between the nationsand will settle disputes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17690N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17690N\"></sup> for many peoples.They will beat their swords into plowsharesand their spears into pruning hooks.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17690O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17690O\"></sup>Nation will not take up sword against nation,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17690P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17690P\"></sup>nor will they train for war anymore.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Come, descendants of Jacob,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17691Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17691Q\"></sup>let us walk in the light<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17691R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17691R\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>You, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have abandoned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17692S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17692S\"></sup> your people,the descendants of Jacob.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17692T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17692T\"></sup>They are full of superstitions from the East;they practice divination<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17692U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17692U\"></sup> like the Philistines<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17692V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17692V\"></sup>and embrace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17692W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17692W\"></sup> pagan customs.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17692X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17692X\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Their land is full of silver and gold;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17693Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17693Y\"></sup>there is no end to their treasures.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17693Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17693Z\"></sup>Their land is full of horses;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17693AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17693AA\"></sup>there is no end to their chariots.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17693AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17693AB\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Their land is full of idols;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17694AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17694AC\"></sup>they bow down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17694AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17694AD\"></sup> to the work of their hands,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17694AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17694AE\"></sup>to what their fingers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17694AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17694AF\"></sup> have made.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So people will be brought low<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17695AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17695AG\"></sup>and everyone humbled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17695AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17695AH\"></sup>—do not forgive them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17695AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17695AI\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Go into the rocks, hide<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17696AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17696AJ\"></sup> in the groundfrom the fearful presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and the splendor of his majesty!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17696AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17696AK\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The eyes of the arrogant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17697AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17697AL\"></sup> will be humbled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17697AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17697AM\"></sup>and human pride<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17697AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17697AN\"></sup> brought low;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17697AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17697AO\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> alone will be exalted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17697AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17697AP\"></sup> in that day.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17697AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17697AQ\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty has a day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17698AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17698AR\"></sup> in storefor all the proud<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17698AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17698AS\"></sup> and lofty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17698AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17698AT\"></sup>for all that is exalted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17698AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17698AU\"></sup>(and they will be humbled),<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17698AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17698AV\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>for all the cedars of Lebanon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17699AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17699AW\"></sup> tall and lofty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17699AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17699AX\"></sup>and all the oaks of Bashan,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17699AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17699AY\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>for all the towering mountainsand all the high hills,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17700AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17700AZ\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>for every lofty tower<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17701BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17701BA\"></sup>and every fortified wall,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17701BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17701BB\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>for every trading ship<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17702BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17702BC\"></sup>and every stately vessel.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The arrogance of man will be brought low<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17703BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17703BD\"></sup>and human pride humbled;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17703BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17703BE\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> alone will be exalted in that day,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17703BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17703BF\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>and the idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17704BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17704BG\"></sup> will totally disappear.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17704BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17704BH\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>People will flee to caves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17705BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17705BI\"></sup> in the rocksand to holes in the ground<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17705BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17705BJ\"></sup>from the fearful presence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17705BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17705BK\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and the splendor of his majesty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17705BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17705BL\"></sup>when he rises to shake the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17705BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17705BM\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17706BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17706BN\"></sup> people will throw awayto the moles and bats<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17706BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17706BO\"></sup>their idols of silver and idols of gold,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17706BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17706BP\"></sup>which they made to worship.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17706BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17706BQ\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>They will flee to caverns in the rocks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17707BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17707BR\"></sup>and to the overhanging cragsfrom the fearful presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and the splendor of his majesty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17707BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17707BS\"></sup>when he rises<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17707BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17707BT\"></sup> to shake the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17707BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17707BU\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Stop trusting in mere humans,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17708BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17708BV\"></sup>who have but a breath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17708BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17708BW\"></sup> in their nostrils.Why hold them in esteem?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17708BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17708BX\"></sup>"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>See now, the Lord,the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty,is about to take from Jerusalem and Judahboth supply and support:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17709A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17709A\"></sup>all supplies of food<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17709B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17709B\"></sup> and all supplies of water,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17709C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17709C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>the hero and the warrior,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17710D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17710D\"></sup>the judge and the prophet,the diviner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17710E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17710E\"></sup> and the elder,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17710F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17710F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>the captain of fifty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17711G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17711G\"></sup> and the man of rank,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17711H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17711H\"></sup>the counselor, skilled craftsman<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17711I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17711I\"></sup> and clever enchanter.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17711J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17711J\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“I will make mere youths their officials;children will rule over them.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17712K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17712K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>People will oppress each other—man against man, neighbor against neighbor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17713L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17713L\"></sup>The young will rise up against the old,the nobody against the honored.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>A man will seize one of his brothersin his father’s house, and say,“You have a cloak, you be our leader;take charge of this heap of ruins!”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But in that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17715M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17715M\"></sup> he will cry out,“I have no remedy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17715N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17715N\"></sup>I have no food<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17715O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17715O\"></sup> or clothing in my house;do not make me the leader of the people.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17715P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17715P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Jerusalem staggers,Judah is falling;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17716Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17716Q\"></sup>their words<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17716R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17716R\"></sup> and deeds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17716S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17716S\"></sup> are against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,defying<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17716T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17716T\"></sup> his glorious presence.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The look on their faces testifies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17717U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17717U\"></sup> against them;they parade their sin like Sodom;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17717V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17717V\"></sup>they do not hide it.Woe to them!They have brought disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17717W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17717W\"></sup> upon themselves.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Tell the righteous it will be well<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17718X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17718X\"></sup> with them,for they will enjoy the fruit of their deeds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17718Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17718Y\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Woe to the wicked!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17719Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17719Z\"></sup>Disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17719AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17719AA\"></sup> is upon them!They will be paid back<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17719AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17719AB\"></sup>for what their hands have done.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17719AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17719AC\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Youths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17720AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17720AD\"></sup> oppress my people,women rule over them.My people, your guides lead you astray;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17720AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17720AE\"></sup>they turn you from the path.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> takes his place in court;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17721AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17721AF\"></sup>he rises to judge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17721AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17721AG\"></sup> the people.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> enters into judgment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17722AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17722AH\"></sup>against the elders and leaders of his people:“It is you who have ruined my vineyard;the plunder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17722AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17722AI\"></sup> from the poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17722AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17722AJ\"></sup> is in your houses.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>What do you mean by crushing my people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17723AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17723AK\"></sup>and grinding<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17723AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17723AL\"></sup> the faces of the poor?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17723AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17723AM\"></sup>declares the Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17723AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17723AN\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says,“The women of Zion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17724AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17724AO\"></sup> are haughty,walking along with outstretched necks,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17724AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17724AP\"></sup>flirting with their eyes,strutting along with swaying hips,with ornaments jingling on their ankles.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Therefore the Lord will bring sores on the heads of the women of Zion;the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will make their scalps bald.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17725AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17725AQ\"></sup>”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17726AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17726AR\"></sup> the Lord will snatch away their finery: the bangles and headbands and crescent necklaces,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17726AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17726AS\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>the earrings and bracelets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17727AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17727AT\"></sup> and veils,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17727AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17727AU\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>the headdresses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17728AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17728AV\"></sup> and anklets and sashes, the perfume bottles and charms,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>the signet rings and nose rings,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17729AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17729AW\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>the fine robes and the capes and cloaks,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17730AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17730AX\"></sup> the purses",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and mirrors, and the linen garments<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17731AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17731AY\"></sup> and tiaras<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17731AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17731AZ\"></sup> and shawls.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Instead of fragrance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17732BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17732BA\"></sup> there will be a stench;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17732BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17732BB\"></sup>instead of a sash,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17732BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17732BC\"></sup> a rope;instead of well-dressed hair, baldness;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17732BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17732BD\"></sup>instead of fine clothing, sackcloth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17732BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17732BE\"></sup>instead of beauty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17732BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17732BF\"></sup> branding.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17732BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17732BG\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Your men will fall by the sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17733BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17733BH\"></sup>your warriors in battle.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17733BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17733BI\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The gates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17734BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17734BJ\"></sup> of Zion will lament and mourn;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17734BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17734BK\"></sup>destitute,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17734BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17734BL\"></sup> she will sit on the ground.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17734BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17734BM\"></sup>"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span><sup class=\"versenum mid-line\">1 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17735A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17735A\"></sup> seven womenwill take hold of one man<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17735B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17735B\"></sup>and say, “We will eat our own food<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17735C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17735C\"></sup>and provide our own clothes;only let us be called by your name.Take away our disgrace!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17735D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17735D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17736E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17736E\"></sup> the Branch of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17736F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17736F\"></sup> will be beautiful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17736G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17736G\"></sup> and glorious, and the fruit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17736H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17736H\"></sup> of the land will be the pride and glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17736I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17736I\"></sup> of the survivors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17736J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17736J\"></sup> in Israel.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Those who are left in Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17737K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17737K\"></sup> who remain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17737L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17737L\"></sup> in Jerusalem, will be called holy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17737M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17737M\"></sup> all who are recorded<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17737N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17737N\"></sup> among the living in Jerusalem.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The Lord will wash away the filth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17738O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17738O\"></sup> of the women of Zion;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17738P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17738P\"></sup> he will cleanse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17738Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17738Q\"></sup> the bloodstains<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17738R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17738R\"></sup> from Jerusalem by a spirit of judgment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17738S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17738S\"></sup> and a spirit of fire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17738T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17738T\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will create<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17739U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17739U\"></sup> over all of Mount Zion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17739V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17739V\"></sup> and over those who assemble there a cloud of smoke by day and a glow of flaming fire by night;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17739W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17739W\"></sup> over everything the glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17739X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17739X\"></sup> will be a canopy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17739Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17739Y\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>It will be a shelter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17740Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17740Z\"></sup> and shade from the heat of the day, and a refuge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17740AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17740AA\"></sup> and hiding place from the storm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17740AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17740AB\"></sup> and rain."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>I will sing for the one I lovea song about his vineyard:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17741A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17741A\"></sup>My loved one had a vineyardon a fertile hillside.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He dug it up and cleared it of stonesand planted it with the choicest vines.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17742B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17742B\"></sup>He built a watchtower<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17742C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17742C\"></sup> in itand cut out a winepress<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17742D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17742D\"></sup> as well.Then he looked for a crop of good grapes,but it yielded only bad fruit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17742E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17742E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Now you dwellers in Jerusalem and people of Judah,judge between me and my vineyard.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17743F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17743F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>What more could have been done for my vineyardthan I have done for it?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17744G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17744G\"></sup>When I looked for good grapes,why did it yield only bad?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17744H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17744H\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now I will tell youwhat I am going to do to my vineyard:I will take away its hedge,and it will be destroyed;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17745I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17745I\"></sup>I will break down its wall,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17745J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17745J\"></sup>and it will be trampled.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17745K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17745K\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I will make it a wasteland,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17746L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17746L\"></sup>neither pruned nor cultivated,and briers and thorns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17746M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17746M\"></sup> will grow there.I will command the cloudsnot to rain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17746N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17746N\"></sup> on it.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The vineyard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17747O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17747O\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almightyis the nation of Israel,and the people of Judahare the vines he delighted in.And he looked for justice,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17747P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17747P\"></sup> but saw bloodshed;for righteousness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17747Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17747Q\"></sup> but heard cries of distress.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17747R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17747R\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17748S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17748S\"></sup> to you who add house to houseand join field to field<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17748T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17748T\"></sup>till no space is leftand you live alone in the land.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17749U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17749U\"></sup> has declared in my hearing:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17749V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17749V\"></sup>“Surely the great houses will become desolate,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17749W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17749W\"></sup>the fine mansions left without occupants.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>A ten-acre vineyard will produce only a bath of wine;a homer of seed will yield only an ephah of grain.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17750X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17750X\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17751Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17751Y\"></sup> to those who rise early in the morningto run after their drinks,who stay up late at nighttill they are inflamed with wine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17751Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17751Z\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They have harps and lyres at their banquets,pipes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17752AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17752AA\"></sup> and timbrels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17752AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17752AB\"></sup> and wine,but they have no regard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17752AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17752AC\"></sup> for the deeds of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,no respect for the work of his hands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17752AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17752AD\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore my people will go into exile<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17753AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17753AE\"></sup>for lack of understanding;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17753AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17753AF\"></sup>those of high rank<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17753AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17753AG\"></sup> will die of hungerand the common people will be parched with thirst.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17753AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17753AH\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore Death<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17754AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17754AI\"></sup> expands its jaws,opening wide its mouth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17754AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17754AJ\"></sup>into it will descend their nobles and masseswith all their brawlers and revelers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17754AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17754AK\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So people will be brought low<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17755AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17755AL\"></sup>and everyone humbled,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17755AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17755AM\"></sup>the eyes of the arrogant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17755AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17755AN\"></sup> humbled.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty will be exalted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17756AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17756AO\"></sup> by his justice,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17756AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17756AP\"></sup>and the holy God will be proved holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17756AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17756AQ\"></sup> by his righteous acts.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then sheep will graze as in their own pasture;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17757AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17757AR\"></sup>lambs will feed among the ruins of the rich.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17758AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17758AS\"></sup> to those who draw sin along with cords<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17758AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17758AT\"></sup> of deceit,and wickedness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17758AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17758AU\"></sup> as with cart ropes,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>to those who say, “Let God hurry;let him hasten<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17759AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17759AV\"></sup> his workso we may see it.The plan of the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17759AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17759AW\"></sup> of Israel—let it approach, let it come into view,so we may know it.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17759AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17759AX\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17760AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17760AY\"></sup> to those who call evil good<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17760AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17760AZ\"></sup>and good evil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17760BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17760BA\"></sup>who put darkness for lightand light for darkness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17760BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17760BB\"></sup>who put bitter for sweetand sweet for bitter.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17760BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17760BC\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Woe to those who are wise in their own eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17761BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17761BD\"></sup>and clever in their own sight.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Woe to those who are heroes at drinking wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17762BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17762BE\"></sup>and champions at mixing drinks,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17762BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17762BF\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>who acquit the guilty for a bribe,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17763BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17763BG\"></sup>but deny justice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17763BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17763BH\"></sup> to the innocent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17763BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17763BI\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Therefore, as tongues of fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17764BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17764BJ\"></sup> lick up straw<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17764BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17764BK\"></sup>and as dry grass sinks down in the flames,so their roots will decay<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17764BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17764BL\"></sup>and their flowers blow away like dust;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17764BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17764BM\"></sup>for they have rejected the law of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almightyand spurned the word<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17764BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17764BN\"></sup> of the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17764BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17764BO\"></sup> of Israel.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Therefore the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17765BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17765BP\"></sup> burns against his people;his hand is raised and he strikes them down.The mountains shake,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17765BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17765BQ\"></sup>and the dead bodies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17765BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17765BR\"></sup> are like refuse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17765BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17765BS\"></sup> in the streets.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17765BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17765BT\"></sup>Yet for all this, his anger is not turned away,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17765BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17765BU\"></sup>his hand is still upraised.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17765BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17765BV\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>He lifts up a banner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17766BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17766BW\"></sup> for the distant nations,he whistles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17766BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17766BX\"></sup> for those at the ends of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17766BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17766BY\"></sup>Here they come,swiftly and speedily!",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Not one of them grows tired<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17767BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17767BZ\"></sup> or stumbles,not one slumbers or sleeps;not a belt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17767CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17767CA\"></sup> is loosened at the waist,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17767CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17767CB\"></sup>not a sandal strap is broken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17767CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17767CC\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Their arrows are sharp,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17768CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17768CD\"></sup>all their bows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17768CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17768CE\"></sup> are strung;their horses’ hooves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17768CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17768CF\"></sup> seem like flint,their chariot wheels like a whirlwind.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17768CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17768CG\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Their roar is like that of the lion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17769CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17769CH\"></sup>they roar like young lions;they growl as they seize<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17769CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17769CI\"></sup> their preyand carry it off with no one to rescue.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17769CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17769CJ\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17770CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17770CK\"></sup> they will roar over itlike the roaring of the sea.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17770CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17770CL\"></sup>And if one looks at the land,there is only darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17770CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17770CM\"></sup> and distress;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17770CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17770CN\"></sup>even the sun will be darkened<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17770CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17770CO\"></sup> by clouds."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>In the year that King Uzziah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17771A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17771A\"></sup> died,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17771B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17771B\"></sup> I saw the Lord,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17771C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17771C\"></sup> high and exalted,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17771D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17771D\"></sup> seated on a throne;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17771E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17771E\"></sup> and the train of his robe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17771F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17771F\"></sup> filled the temple.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Above him were seraphim,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17772G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17772G\"></sup> each with six wings: With two wings they covered their faces, with two they covered their feet,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17772H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17772H\"></sup> and with two they were flying.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And they were calling to one another:“Holy, holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17773I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17773I\"></sup>, holy is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17773J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17773J\"></sup>the whole earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17773K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17773K\"></sup> is full of his glory.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17773L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17773L\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>At the sound of their voices the doorposts and thresholds shook and the temple was filled with smoke.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17774M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17774M\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17775N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17775N\"></sup> to me!” I cried. “I am ruined!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17775O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17775O\"></sup> For I am a man of unclean lips,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17775P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17775P\"></sup> and I live among a people of unclean lips,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17775Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17775Q\"></sup> and my eyes have seen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17775R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17775R\"></sup> the King,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17775S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17775S\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17775T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17775T\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then one of the seraphim flew to me with a live coal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17776U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17776U\"></sup> in his hand, which he had taken with tongs from the altar.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>With it he touched my mouth and said, “See, this has touched your lips;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17777V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17777V\"></sup> your guilt is taken away and your sin atoned for.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17777W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17777W\"></sup>”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then I heard the voice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17778X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17778X\"></sup> of the Lord saying, “Whom shall I send?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17778Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17778Y\"></sup> And who will go for us?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17778Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17778Z\"></sup>”And I said, “Here am I.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17778AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17778AA\"></sup> Send me!”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He said, “Go<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17779AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17779AB\"></sup> and tell this people:“‘Be ever hearing, but never understanding;be ever seeing, but never perceiving.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17779AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17779AC\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Make the heart of this people calloused;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17780AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17780AD\"></sup>make their ears dulland close their eyes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17780AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17780AE\"></sup>Otherwise they might see with their eyes,hear with their ears,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17780AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17780AF\"></sup>understand with their hearts,and turn and be healed.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17780AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17780AG\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then I said, “For how long, Lord?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17781AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17781AH\"></sup>And he answered:“Until the cities lie ruined<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17781AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17781AI\"></sup>and without inhabitant,until the houses are left deserted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17781AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17781AJ\"></sup>and the fields ruined and ravaged,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17781AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17781AK\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>until the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has sent everyone far away<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17782AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17782AL\"></sup>and the land is utterly forsaken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17782AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17782AM\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And though a tenth remains<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17783AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17783AN\"></sup> in the land,it will again be laid waste.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17783AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17783AO\"></sup>But as the terebinth and oakleave stumps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17783AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17783AP\"></sup> when they are cut down,so the holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17783AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17783AQ\"></sup> seed will be the stump in the land.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17783AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17783AR\"></sup>"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>When Ahaz<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17784A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17784A\"></sup> son of Jotham, the son of Uzziah, was king of Judah, King Rezin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17784B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17784B\"></sup> of Aram<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17784C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17784C\"></sup> and Pekah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17784D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17784D\"></sup> son of Remaliah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17784E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17784E\"></sup> king of Israel marched up to fight against Jerusalem, but they could not overpower it.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Now the house of David<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17785F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17785F\"></sup> was told, “Aram has allied itself with Ephraim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17785G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17785G\"></sup>”; so the hearts of Ahaz and his people were shaken,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17785H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17785H\"></sup> as the trees of the forest are shaken by the wind.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Isaiah, “Go out, you and your son Shear-Jashub,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17786I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17786I\"></sup> to meet Ahaz at the end of the aqueduct of the Upper Pool, on the road to the Launderer’s Field.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17786J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17786J\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Say to him, ‘Be careful, keep calm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17787K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17787K\"></sup> and don’t be afraid.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17787L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17787L\"></sup> Do not lose heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17787M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17787M\"></sup> because of these two smoldering stubs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17787N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17787N\"></sup> of firewood—because of the fierce anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17787O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17787O\"></sup> of Rezin and Aram and of the son of Remaliah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17787P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17787P\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Aram, Ephraim and Remaliah’s<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17788Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17788Q\"></sup> son have plotted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17788R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17788R\"></sup> your ruin, saying,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Let us invade Judah; let us tear it apart and divide it among ourselves, and make the son of Tabeel king over it.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Yet this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17790S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17790S\"></sup>“‘It will not take place,it will not happen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17790T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17790T\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>for the head of Aram is Damascus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17791U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17791U\"></sup>and the head of Damascus is only Rezin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17791V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17791V\"></sup>Within sixty-five yearsEphraim will be too shattered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17791W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17791W\"></sup> to be a people.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The head of Ephraim is Samaria,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17792X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17792X\"></sup>and the head of Samaria is only Remaliah’s son.If you do not stand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17792Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17792Y\"></sup> firm in your faith,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17792Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17792Z\"></sup>you will not stand at all.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17792AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17792AA\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Again the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke to Ahaz,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Ask the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God for a sign,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17794AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17794AB\"></sup> whether in the deepest depths or in the highest heights.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17794AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17794AC\"></sup>”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But Ahaz said, “I will not ask; I will not put the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to the test.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17795AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17795AD\"></sup>”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then Isaiah said, “Hear now, you house of David!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17796AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17796AE\"></sup> Is it not enough<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17796AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17796AF\"></sup> to try the patience of humans? Will you try the patience<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17796AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17796AG\"></sup> of my God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17796AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17796AH\"></sup> also?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore the Lord himself will give you a sign:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17797AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17797AI\"></sup> The virgin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17797AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17797AJ\"></sup> will conceive and give birth to a son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17797AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17797AK\"></sup> and will call him Immanuel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17797AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17797AL\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He will be eating curds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17798AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17798AM\"></sup> and honey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17798AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17798AN\"></sup> when he knows enough to reject the wrong and choose the right,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>for before the boy knows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17799AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17799AO\"></sup> enough to reject the wrong and choose the right,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17799AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17799AP\"></sup> the land of the two kings you dread will be laid waste.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17799AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17799AQ\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will bring on you and on your people and on the house of your father a time unlike any since Ephraim broke away<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17800AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17800AR\"></sup> from Judah—he will bring the king of Assyria.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17800AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17800AS\"></sup>”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17801AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17801AT\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will whistle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17801AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17801AU\"></sup> for flies from the Nile delta in Egypt and for bees from the land of Assyria.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17801AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17801AV\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>They will all come and settle in the steep ravines and in the crevices<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17802AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17802AW\"></sup> in the rocks, on all the thornbushes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17802AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17802AX\"></sup> and at all the water holes.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17803AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17803AY\"></sup> the Lord will use<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17803AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17803AZ\"></sup> a razor hired from beyond the Euphrates River<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17803BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17803BA\"></sup>—the king of Assyria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17803BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17803BB\"></sup>—to shave your head and private parts, and to cut off your beard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17803BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17803BC\"></sup> also.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17803BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17803BD\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>In that day,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17804BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17804BE\"></sup> a person will keep alive a young cow and two goats.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17804BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17804BF\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And because of the abundance of the milk they give, there will be curds to eat. All who remain in the land will eat curds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17805BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17805BG\"></sup> and honey.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17805BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17805BH\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>In that day,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17806BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17806BI\"></sup> in every place where there were a thousand vines worth a thousand silver shekels,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17806BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17806BJ\"></sup> there will be only briers and thorns.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17806BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17806BK\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Hunters will go there with bow and arrow, for the land will be covered with briers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17807BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17807BL\"></sup> and thorns.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>As for all the hills<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17808BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17808BM\"></sup> once cultivated by the hoe, you will no longer go there for fear of the briers and thorns;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17808BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17808BN\"></sup> they will become places where cattle are turned loose and where sheep run.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17808BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17808BO\"></sup>"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Take a large scroll<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17809A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17809A\"></sup> and write on it with an ordinary pen: Maher-Shalal-Hash-Baz.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17809B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17809B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So I called in Uriah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17810C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17810C\"></sup> the priest and Zechariah son of Jeberekiah as reliable witnesses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17810D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17810D\"></sup> for me.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then I made love to the prophetess,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17811E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17811E\"></sup> and she conceived and gave birth to a son.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17811F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17811F\"></sup> And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Name him Maher-Shalal-Hash-Baz.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17811G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17811G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For before the boy knows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17812H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17812H\"></sup> how to say ‘My father’ or ‘My mother,’ the wealth of Damascus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17812I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17812I\"></sup> and the plunder of Samaria will be carried off by the king of Assyria.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17812J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17812J\"></sup>”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke to me again:",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Because this people has rejected<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17814K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17814K\"></sup>the gently flowing waters of Shiloah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17814L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17814L\"></sup>and rejoices over Rezinand the son of Remaliah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17814M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17814M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>therefore the Lord is about to bring against themthe mighty floodwaters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17815N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17815N\"></sup> of the Euphrates—the king of Assyria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17815O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17815O\"></sup> with all his pomp.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17815P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17815P\"></sup>It will overflow all its channels,run over all its banks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17815Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17815Q\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and sweep on into Judah, swirling over it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17816R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17816R\"></sup>passing through it and reaching up to the neck.Its outspread wings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17816S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17816S\"></sup> will cover the breadth of your land,Immanuel!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17816T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17816T\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Raise the war cry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17817U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17817U\"></sup> you nations, and be shattered!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17817V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17817V\"></sup>Listen, all you distant lands.Prepare<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17817W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17817W\"></sup> for battle, and be shattered!Prepare for battle, and be shattered!",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Devise your strategy, but it will be thwarted;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17818X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17818X\"></sup>propose your plan, but it will not stand,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17818Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17818Y\"></sup>for God is with us.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17818Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17818Z\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says to me with his strong hand upon me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17819AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17819AA\"></sup> warning me not to follow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17819AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17819AB\"></sup> the way of this people:",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Do not call conspiracy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17820AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17820AC\"></sup>everything this people calls a conspiracy;do not fear what they fear,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17820AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17820AD\"></sup>and do not dread it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17820AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17820AE\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty is the one you are to regard as holy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17821AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17821AF\"></sup>he is the one you are to fear,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17821AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17821AG\"></sup>he is the one you are to dread.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17821AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17821AH\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>He will be a holy place;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17822AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17822AI\"></sup>for both Israel and Judah he will bea stone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17822AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17822AJ\"></sup> that causes people to stumble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17822AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17822AK\"></sup>and a rock that makes them fall.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17822AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17822AL\"></sup>And for the people of Jerusalem he will bea trap and a snare.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17822AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17822AM\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Many of them will stumble;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17823AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17823AN\"></sup>they will fall and be broken,they will be snared and captured.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Bind up this testimony of warning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17824AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17824AO\"></sup>and seal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17824AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17824AP\"></sup> up God’s instruction among my disciples.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I will wait<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17825AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17825AQ\"></sup> for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,who is hiding<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17825AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17825AR\"></sup> his face from the descendants of Jacob.I will put my trust in him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17825AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17825AS\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Here am I, and the children the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has given me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17826AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17826AT\"></sup> We are signs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17826AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17826AU\"></sup> and symbols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17826AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17826AV\"></sup> in Israel from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, who dwells on Mount Zion.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17826AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17826AW\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>When someone tells you to consult<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17827AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17827AX\"></sup> mediums and spiritists,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17827AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17827AY\"></sup> who whisper and mutter,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17827AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17827AZ\"></sup> should not a people inquire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17827BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17827BA\"></sup> of their God? Why consult the dead on behalf of the living?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Consult God’s instruction<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17828BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17828BB\"></sup> and the testimony of warning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17828BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17828BC\"></sup> If anyone does not speak according to this word, they have no light<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17828BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17828BD\"></sup> of dawn.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Distressed and hungry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17829BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17829BE\"></sup> they will roam through the land;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17829BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17829BF\"></sup> when they are famished, they will become enraged and, looking upward, will curse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17829BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17829BG\"></sup> their king and their God.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Then they will look toward the earth and see only distress and darkness and fearful gloom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17830BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17830BH\"></sup> and they will be thrust into utter darkness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17830BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17830BI\"></sup>"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>Nevertheless, there will be no more gloom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17831A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17831A\"></sup> for those who were in distress. In the past he humbled the land of Zebulun and the land of Naphtali,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17831B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17831B\"></sup> but in the future he will honor Galilee of the nations, by the Way of the Sea, beyond the Jordan—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The people walking in darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17832C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17832C\"></sup>have seen a great light;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17832D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17832D\"></sup>on those living in the land of deep darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17832E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17832E\"></sup>a light has dawned.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17832F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17832F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You have enlarged the nation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17833G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17833G\"></sup>and increased their joy;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17833H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17833H\"></sup>they rejoice before youas people rejoice at the harvest,as warriors rejoicewhen dividing the plunder.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17833I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17833I\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For as in the day of Midian’s defeat,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17834J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17834J\"></sup>you have shattered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17834K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17834K\"></sup>the yoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17834L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17834L\"></sup> that burdens them,the bar across their shoulders,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17834M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17834M\"></sup>the rod of their oppressor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17834N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17834N\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Every warrior’s boot used in battleand every garment rolled in bloodwill be destined for burning,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17835O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17835O\"></sup>will be fuel for the fire.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For to us a child is born,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17836P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17836P\"></sup>to us a son is given,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17836Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17836Q\"></sup>and the government<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17836R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17836R\"></sup> will be on his shoulders.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17836S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17836S\"></sup>And he will be calledWonderful Counselor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17836T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17836T\"></sup> Mighty God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17836U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17836U\"></sup>Everlasting<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17836V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17836V\"></sup> Father,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17836W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17836W\"></sup> Prince of Peace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17836X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17836X\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Of the greatness of his government<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17837Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17837Y\"></sup> and peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17837Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17837Z\"></sup>there will be no end.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17837AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17837AA\"></sup>He will reign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17837AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17837AB\"></sup> on David’s throneand over his kingdom,establishing and upholding itwith justice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17837AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17837AC\"></sup> and righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17837AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17837AD\"></sup>from that time on and forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17837AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17837AE\"></sup>The zeal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17837AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17837AF\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almightywill accomplish this.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The Lord has sent a message<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17838AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17838AG\"></sup> against Jacob;it will fall on Israel.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>All the people will know it—Ephraim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17839AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17839AH\"></sup> and the inhabitants of Samaria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17839AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17839AI\"></sup>—who say with prideand arrogance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17839AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17839AJ\"></sup> of heart,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“The bricks have fallen down,but we will rebuild with dressed stone;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17840AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17840AK\"></sup>the fig<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17840AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17840AL\"></sup> trees have been felled,but we will replace them with cedars.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17840AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17840AM\"></sup>”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has strengthened Rezin’s<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17841AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17841AN\"></sup> foes against themand has spurred their enemies on.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Arameans<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17842AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17842AO\"></sup> from the east and Philistines<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17842AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17842AP\"></sup> from the westhave devoured<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17842AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17842AQ\"></sup> Israel with open mouth.Yet for all this, his anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17842AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17842AR\"></sup> is not turned away,his hand is still upraised.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17842AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17842AS\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But the people have not returned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17843AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17843AT\"></sup> to him who struck<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17843AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17843AU\"></sup> them,nor have they sought<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17843AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17843AV\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will cut off from Israel both head and tail,both palm branch and reed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17844AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17844AW\"></sup> in a single day;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17844AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17844AX\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>the elders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17845AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17845AY\"></sup> and dignitaries<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17845AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17845AZ\"></sup> are the head,the prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17845BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17845BA\"></sup> who teach lies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17845BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17845BB\"></sup> are the tail.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Those who guide<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17846BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17846BC\"></sup> this people mislead them,and those who are guided are led astray.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17846BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17846BD\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Therefore the Lord will take no pleasure in the young men,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17847BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17847BE\"></sup>nor will he pity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17847BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17847BF\"></sup> the fatherless and widows,for everyone is ungodly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17847BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17847BG\"></sup> and wicked,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17847BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17847BH\"></sup>every mouth speaks folly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17847BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17847BI\"></sup>Yet for all this, his anger is not turned away,his hand is still upraised.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17847BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17847BJ\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Surely wickedness burns like a fire;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17848BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17848BK\"></sup>it consumes briers and thorns,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17848BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17848BL\"></sup>it sets the forest thickets ablaze,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17848BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17848BM\"></sup>so that it rolls upward in a column of smoke.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>By the wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17849BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17849BN\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almightythe land will be scorched<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17849BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17849BO\"></sup>and the people will be fuel for the fire;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17849BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17849BP\"></sup>they will not spare one another.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17849BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17849BQ\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>On the right they will devour,but still be hungry;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17850BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17850BR\"></sup>on the left they will eat,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17850BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17850BS\"></sup>but not be satisfied.Each will feed on the flesh of their own offspring:",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Manasseh will feed on Ephraim, and Ephraim on Manasseh;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17851BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17851BT\"></sup>together they will turn against Judah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17851BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17851BU\"></sup>Yet for all this, his anger is not turned away,his hand is still upraised.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17851BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17851BV\"></sup>"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17852A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17852A\"></sup> to those who make unjust laws,to those who issue oppressive decrees,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17852B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17852B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>to deprive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17853C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17853C\"></sup> the poor of their rightsand withhold justice from the oppressed of my people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17853D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17853D\"></sup>making widows their preyand robbing the fatherless.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17853E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17853E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>What will you do on the day of reckoning,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17854F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17854F\"></sup>when disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17854G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17854G\"></sup> comes from afar?To whom will you run for help?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17854H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17854H\"></sup>Where will you leave your riches?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Nothing will remain but to cringe among the captives<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17855I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17855I\"></sup>or fall among the slain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17855J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17855J\"></sup>Yet for all this, his anger is not turned away,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17855K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17855K\"></sup>his hand is still upraised.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17856L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17856L\"></sup> to the Assyrian,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17856M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17856M\"></sup> the rod<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17856N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17856N\"></sup> of my anger,in whose hand is the club<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17856O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17856O\"></sup> of my wrath!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17856P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17856P\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I send him against a godless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17857Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17857Q\"></sup> nation,I dispatch<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17857R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17857R\"></sup> him against a people who anger me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17857S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17857S\"></sup>to seize loot and snatch plunder,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17857T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17857T\"></sup>and to trample<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17857U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17857U\"></sup> them down like mud in the streets.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But this is not what he intends,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17858V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17858V\"></sup>this is not what he has in mind;his purpose is to destroy,to put an end to many nations.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>‘Are not my commanders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17859W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17859W\"></sup> all kings?’ he says.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>‘Has not Kalno<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17860X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17860X\"></sup> fared like Carchemish?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17860Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17860Y\"></sup>Is not Hamath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17860Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17860Z\"></sup> like Arpad,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17860AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17860AA\"></sup>and Samaria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17860AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17860AB\"></sup> like Damascus?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17860AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17860AC\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>As my hand seized the kingdoms of the idols,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17861AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17861AD\"></sup>kingdoms whose images excelled those of Jerusalem and Samaria—",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>shall I not deal with Jerusalem and her imagesas I dealt with Samaria and her idols?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17862AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17862AE\"></sup>’”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When the Lord has finished all his work<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17863AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17863AF\"></sup> against Mount Zion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17863AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17863AG\"></sup> and Jerusalem, he will say, “I will punish the king of Assyria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17863AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17863AH\"></sup> for the willful pride<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17863AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17863AI\"></sup> of his heart and the haughty look<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17863AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17863AJ\"></sup> in his eyes.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For he says:“‘By the strength of my hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17864AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17864AK\"></sup> I have done this,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17864AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17864AL\"></sup>and by my wisdom, because I have understanding.I removed the boundaries of nations,I plundered their treasures;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17864AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17864AM\"></sup>like a mighty one I subdued their kings.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17864AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17864AN\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>As one reaches into a nest,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17865AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17865AO\"></sup>so my hand reached for the wealth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17865AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17865AP\"></sup> of the nations;as people gather abandoned eggs,so I gathered all the countries;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17865AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17865AQ\"></sup>not one flapped a wing,or opened its mouth to chirp.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17865AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17865AR\"></sup>’”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Does the ax raise itself above the person who swings it,or the saw boast against the one who uses it?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17866AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17866AS\"></sup>As if a rod were to wield the person who lifts it up,or a club<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17866AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17866AT\"></sup> brandish the one who is not wood!",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore, the Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty,will send a wasting disease<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17867AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17867AU\"></sup> upon his sturdy warriors;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17867AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17867AV\"></sup>under his pomp<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17867AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17867AW\"></sup> a fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17867AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17867AX\"></sup> will be kindledlike a blazing flame.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The Light of Israel will become a fire,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17868AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17868AY\"></sup>their Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17868AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17868AZ\"></sup> a flame;in a single day it will burn and consumehis thorns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17868BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17868BA\"></sup> and his briers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17868BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17868BB\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The splendor of his forests<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17869BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17869BC\"></sup> and fertile fieldsit will completely destroy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17869BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17869BD\"></sup>as when a sick person wastes away.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And the remaining trees of his forests<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17870BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17870BE\"></sup> will be so few<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17870BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17870BF\"></sup>that a child could write them down.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17871BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17871BG\"></sup> the remnant of Israel,the survivors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17871BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17871BH\"></sup> of Jacob,will no longer rely<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17871BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17871BI\"></sup> on himwho struck them down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17871BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17871BJ\"></sup>but will truly rely<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17871BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17871BK\"></sup> on the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,the Holy One of Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17871BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17871BL\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>A remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17872BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17872BM\"></sup> will return,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17872BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17872BN\"></sup> a remnant of Jacobwill return to the Mighty God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17872BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17872BO\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Though your people be like the sand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17873BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17873BP\"></sup> by the sea, Israel,only a remnant will return.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17873BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17873BQ\"></sup>Destruction has been decreed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17873BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17873BR\"></sup>overwhelming and righteous.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, will carry outthe destruction decreed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17874BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17874BS\"></sup> upon the whole land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17874BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17874BT\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Therefore this is what the Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, says:“My people who live in Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17875BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17875BU\"></sup>do not be afraid<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17875BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17875BV\"></sup> of the Assyrians,who beat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17875BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17875BW\"></sup> you with a rod<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17875BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17875BX\"></sup>and lift up a club against you, as Egypt did.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Very soon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17876BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17876BY\"></sup> my anger against you will endand my wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17876BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17876BZ\"></sup> will be directed to their destruction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17876CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17876CA\"></sup>”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty will lash<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17877CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17877CB\"></sup> them with a whip,as when he struck down Midian<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17877CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17877CC\"></sup> at the rock of Oreb;and he will raise his staff<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17877CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17877CD\"></sup> over the waters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17877CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17877CE\"></sup>as he did in Egypt.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17878CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17878CF\"></sup> their burden<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17878CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17878CG\"></sup> will be lifted from your shoulders,their yoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17878CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17878CH\"></sup> from your neck;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17878CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17878CI\"></sup>the yoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17878CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17878CJ\"></sup> will be brokenbecause you have grown so fat.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>They enter Aiath;they pass through Migron;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17879CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17879CK\"></sup>they store supplies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17879CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17879CL\"></sup> at Mikmash.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17879CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17879CM\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>They go over the pass, and say,“We will camp overnight at Geba.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17880CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17880CN\"></sup>”Ramah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17880CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17880CO\"></sup> trembles;Gibeah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17880CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17880CP\"></sup> of Saul flees.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17880CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17880CQ\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Cry out, Daughter Gallim!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17881CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17881CR\"></sup>Listen, Laishah!Poor Anathoth!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17881CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17881CS\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Madmenah is in flight;the people of Gebim take cover.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>This day they will halt at Nob;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17883CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17883CT\"></sup>they will shake their fist<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17883CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17883CU\"></sup>at the mount of Daughter Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17883CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17883CV\"></sup>at the hill of Jerusalem.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>See, the Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty,will lop off<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17884CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17884CW\"></sup> the boughs with great power.The lofty trees will be felled,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17884CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17884CX\"></sup>the tall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17884CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17884CY\"></sup> ones will be brought low.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17884CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17884CZ\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>He will cut down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17885DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17885DA\"></sup> the forest thickets with an ax;Lebanon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17885DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17885DB\"></sup> will fall before the Mighty One.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17885DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17885DC\"></sup>"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>A shoot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17886A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17886A\"></sup> will come up from the stump<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17886B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17886B\"></sup> of Jesse;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17886C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17886C\"></sup>from his roots a Branch<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17886D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17886D\"></sup> will bear fruit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17886E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17886E\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17887F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17887F\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will rest on him—the Spirit of wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17887G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17887G\"></sup> and of understanding,the Spirit of counsel and of might,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17887H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17887H\"></sup>the Spirit of the knowledge and fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>—",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and he will delight in the fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17888I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17888I\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.He will not judge by what he sees with his eyes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17888J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17888J\"></sup>or decide by what he hears with his ears;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17888K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17888K\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>but with righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17889L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17889L\"></sup> he will judge the needy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17889M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17889M\"></sup>with justice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17889N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17889N\"></sup> he will give decisions for the poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17889O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17889O\"></sup> of the earth.He will strike<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17889P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17889P\"></sup> the earth with the rod of his mouth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17889Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17889Q\"></sup>with the breath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17889R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17889R\"></sup> of his lips he will slay the wicked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17889S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17889S\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Righteousness will be his belt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17890T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17890T\"></sup>and faithfulness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17890U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17890U\"></sup> the sash around his waist.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17890V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17890V\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The wolf will live with the lamb,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17891W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17891W\"></sup>the leopard will lie down with the goat,the calf and the lion and the yearling together;and a little child will lead them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The cow will feed with the bear,their young will lie down together,and the lion will eat straw like the ox.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17892X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17892X\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The infant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17893Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17893Y\"></sup> will play near the cobra’s den,and the young child will put its hand into the viper’s<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17893Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17893Z\"></sup> nest.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They will neither harm nor destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17894AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17894AA\"></sup>on all my holy mountain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17894AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17894AB\"></sup>for the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17894AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17894AC\"></sup> will be filled with the knowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17894AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17894AD\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>as the waters cover the sea.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17895AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17895AE\"></sup> the Root of Jesse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17895AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17895AF\"></sup> will stand as a banner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17895AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17895AG\"></sup> for the peoples; the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17895AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17895AH\"></sup> will rally to him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17895AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17895AI\"></sup> and his resting place<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17895AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17895AJ\"></sup> will be glorious.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17895AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17895AK\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17896AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17896AL\"></sup> the Lord will reach out his hand a second time to reclaim the surviving remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17896AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17896AM\"></sup> of his people from Assyria,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17896AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17896AN\"></sup> from Lower Egypt, from Upper Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17896AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17896AO\"></sup> from Cush,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17896AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17896AP\"></sup> from Elam,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17896AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17896AQ\"></sup> from Babylonia, from Hamath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17896AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17896AR\"></sup> and from the islands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17896AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17896AS\"></sup> of the Mediterranean.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17896AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17896AT\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He will raise a banner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17897AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17897AU\"></sup> for the nationsand gather<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17897AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17897AV\"></sup> the exiles of Israel;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17897AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17897AW\"></sup>he will assemble the scattered people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17897AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17897AX\"></sup> of Judahfrom the four quarters of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17897AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17897AY\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Ephraim’s jealousy will vanish,and Judah’s enemies will be destroyed;Ephraim will not be jealous of Judah,nor Judah hostile toward Ephraim.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17898AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17898AZ\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They will swoop down on the slopes of Philistia<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17899BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17899BA\"></sup> to the west;together they will plunder the people to the east.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17899BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17899BB\"></sup>They will subdue Edom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17899BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17899BC\"></sup> and Moab,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17899BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17899BD\"></sup>and the Ammonites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17899BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17899BE\"></sup> will be subject to them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17899BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17899BF\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will dry up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17900BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17900BG\"></sup>the gulf of the Egyptian sea;with a scorching wind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17900BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17900BH\"></sup> he will sweep his hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17900BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17900BI\"></sup>over the Euphrates River.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17900BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17900BJ\"></sup>He will break it up into seven streamsso that anyone can cross over in sandals.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17900BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17900BK\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>There will be a highway<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17901BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17901BL\"></sup> for the remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17901BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17901BM\"></sup> of his peoplethat is left from Assyria,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17901BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17901BN\"></sup>as there was for Israelwhen they came up from Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17901BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17901BO\"></sup>"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17902A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17902A\"></sup> you will say:“I will praise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17902B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17902B\"></sup> you, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.Although you were angry with me,your anger has turned away<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17902C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17902C\"></sup>and you have comforted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17902D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17902D\"></sup> me.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Surely God is my salvation;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17903E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17903E\"></sup>I will trust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17903F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17903F\"></sup> and not be afraid.The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> himself,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17903G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17903G\"></sup> is my strength<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17903H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17903H\"></sup> and my defense;he has become my salvation.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17903I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17903I\"></sup>”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>With joy you will draw water<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17904J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17904J\"></sup>from the wells<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17904K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17904K\"></sup> of salvation.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17905L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17905L\"></sup> you will say:“Give praise to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, proclaim his name;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17905M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17905M\"></sup>make known among the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17905N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17905N\"></sup> what he has done,and proclaim that his name is exalted.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17905O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17905O\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Sing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17906P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17906P\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, for he has done glorious things;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17906Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17906Q\"></sup>let this be known to all the world.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Shout aloud and sing for joy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17907R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17907R\"></sup> people of Zion,for great<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17907S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17907S\"></sup> is the Holy One of Israel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17907T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17907T\"></sup> among you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17907U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17907U\"></sup>”"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>A prophecy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17908A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17908A\"></sup> against Babylon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17908B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17908B\"></sup> that Isaiah son of Amoz<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17908C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17908C\"></sup> saw:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17908D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17908D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Raise a banner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17909E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17909E\"></sup> on a bare hilltop,shout to them;beckon to themto enter the gates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17909F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17909F\"></sup> of the nobles.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I have commanded those I prepared for battle;I have summoned my warriors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17910G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17910G\"></sup> to carry out my wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17910H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17910H\"></sup>—those who rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17910I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17910I\"></sup> in my triumph.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Listen, a noise on the mountains,like that of a great multitude!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17911J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17911J\"></sup>Listen, an uproar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17911K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17911K\"></sup> among the kingdoms,like nations massing together!The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17911L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17911L\"></sup> is mustering<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17911M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17911M\"></sup>an army for war.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They come from faraway lands,from the ends of the heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17912N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17912N\"></sup>—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and the weapons<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17912O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17912O\"></sup> of his wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17912P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17912P\"></sup>—to destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17912Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17912Q\"></sup> the whole country.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Wail,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17913R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17913R\"></sup> for the day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17913S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17913S\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is near;it will come like destruction<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17913T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17913T\"></sup> from the Almighty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17913U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17913U\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Because of this, all hands will go limp,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17914V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17914V\"></sup>every heart will melt with fear.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17914W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17914W\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Terror<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17915X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17915X\"></sup> will seize them,pain and anguish will grip<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17915Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17915Y\"></sup> them;they will writhe like a woman in labor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17915Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17915Z\"></sup>They will look aghast at each other,their faces aflame.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17915AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17915AA\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>See, the day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17916AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17916AB\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is coming—a cruel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17916AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17916AC\"></sup> day, with wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17916AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17916AD\"></sup> and fierce anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17916AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17916AE\"></sup>—to make the land desolateand destroy the sinners within it.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The stars of heaven and their constellationswill not show their light.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17917AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17917AF\"></sup>The rising sun<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17917AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17917AG\"></sup> will be darkened<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17917AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17917AH\"></sup>and the moon will not give its light.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17917AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17917AI\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I will punish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17918AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17918AJ\"></sup> the world for its evil,the wicked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17918AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17918AK\"></sup> for their sins.I will put an end to the arrogance of the haughty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17918AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17918AL\"></sup>and will humble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17918AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17918AM\"></sup> the pride of the ruthless.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17918AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17918AN\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will make people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17919AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17919AO\"></sup> scarcer than pure gold,more rare than the gold of Ophir.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17919AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17919AP\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore I will make the heavens tremble;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17920AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17920AQ\"></sup>and the earth will shake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17920AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17920AR\"></sup> from its placeat the wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17920AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17920AS\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty,in the day of his burning anger.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17920AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17920AT\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Like a hunted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17921AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17921AU\"></sup> gazelle,like sheep without a shepherd,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17921AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17921AV\"></sup>they will all return to their own people,they will flee<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17921AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17921AW\"></sup> to their native land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17921AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17921AX\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Whoever is captured will be thrust through;all who are caught will fall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17922AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17922AY\"></sup> by the sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17922AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17922AZ\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Their infants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17923BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17923BA\"></sup> will be dashed to pieces before their eyes;their houses will be looted and their wives violated.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17923BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17923BB\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>See, I will stir up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17924BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17924BC\"></sup> against them the Medes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17924BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17924BD\"></sup>who do not care for silverand have no delight in gold.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17924BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17924BE\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Their bows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17925BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17925BF\"></sup> will strike down the young men;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17925BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17925BG\"></sup>they will have no mercy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17925BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17925BH\"></sup> on infants,nor will they look with compassion on children.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17925BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17925BI\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Babylon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17926BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17926BJ\"></sup> the jewel of kingdoms,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17926BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17926BK\"></sup>the pride and glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17926BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17926BL\"></sup> of the Babylonians,will be overthrown<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17926BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17926BM\"></sup> by Godlike Sodom and Gomorrah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17926BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17926BN\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>She will never be inhabited<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17927BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17927BO\"></sup>or lived in through all generations;there no nomads<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17927BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17927BP\"></sup> will pitch their tents,there no shepherds will rest their flocks.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But desert creatures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17928BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17928BQ\"></sup> will lie there,jackals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17928BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17928BR\"></sup> will fill her houses;there the owls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17928BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17928BS\"></sup> will dwell,and there the wild goats<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17928BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17928BT\"></sup> will leap about.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Hyenas<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17929BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17929BU\"></sup> will inhabit her strongholds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17929BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17929BV\"></sup>jackals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17929BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17929BW\"></sup> her luxurious palaces.Her time is at hand,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17929BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17929BX\"></sup>and her days will not be prolonged.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17929BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17929BY\"></sup>"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will have compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17930A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17930A\"></sup> on Jacob;once again he will choose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17930B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17930B\"></sup> Israeland will settle them in their own land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17930C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17930C\"></sup>Foreigners<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17930D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17930D\"></sup> will join themand unite with the descendants of Jacob.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Nations will take themand bring<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17931E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17931E\"></sup> them to their own place.And Israel will take possession of the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17931F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17931F\"></sup>and make them male and female servants in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s land.They will make captives<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17931G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17931G\"></sup> of their captorsand rule over their oppressors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17931H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17931H\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>On the day the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gives you relief<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17932I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17932I\"></sup> from your suffering and turmoil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17932J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17932J\"></sup> and from the harsh labor forced on you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17932K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17932K\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>you will take up this taunt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17933L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17933L\"></sup> against the king of Babylon:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17933M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17933M\"></sup>How the oppressor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17933N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17933N\"></sup> has come to an end!How his fury has ended!",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has broken the rod<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17934O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17934O\"></sup> of the wicked,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17934P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17934P\"></sup>the scepter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17934Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17934Q\"></sup> of the rulers,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>which in anger struck down peoples<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17935R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17935R\"></sup>with unceasing blows,and in fury subdued<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17935S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17935S\"></sup> nationswith relentless aggression.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17935T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17935T\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>All the lands are at rest and at peace;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17936U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17936U\"></sup>they break into singing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17936V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17936V\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Even the junipers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17937W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17937W\"></sup> and the cedars of Lebanongloat over you and say,“Now that you have been laid low,no one comes to cut us down.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17937X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17937X\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The realm of the dead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17938Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17938Y\"></sup> below is all astirto meet you at your coming;it rouses the spirits of the departed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17938Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17938Z\"></sup> to greet you—all those who were leaders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17938AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17938AA\"></sup> in the world;it makes them rise from their thrones—all those who were kings over the nations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17938AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17938AB\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They will all respond,they will say to you,“You also have become weak, as we are;you have become like us.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17939AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17939AC\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>All your pomp has been brought down to the grave,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17940AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17940AD\"></sup>along with the noise of your harps;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17940AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17940AE\"></sup>maggots are spread out beneath youand worms<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17940AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17940AF\"></sup> cover you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17940AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17940AG\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>How you have fallen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17941AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17941AH\"></sup> from heaven,morning star,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17941AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17941AI\"></sup> son of the dawn!You have been cast down to the earth,you who once laid low the nations!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17941AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17941AJ\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>You said in your heart,“I will ascend<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17942AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17942AK\"></sup> to the heavens;I will raise my throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17942AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17942AL\"></sup>above the stars of God;I will sit enthroned on the mount of assembly,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17942AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17942AM\"></sup>on the utmost heights<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17942AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17942AN\"></sup> of Mount Zaphon.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will ascend above the tops of the clouds;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17943AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17943AO\"></sup>I will make myself like the Most High.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17943AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17943AP\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But you are brought down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17944AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17944AQ\"></sup> to the realm of the dead,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17944AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17944AR\"></sup>to the depths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17944AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17944AS\"></sup> of the pit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17944AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17944AT\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Those who see you stare at you,they ponder your fate:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17945AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17945AU\"></sup>“Is this the man who shook<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17945AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17945AV\"></sup> the earthand made kingdoms tremble,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>the man who made the world a wilderness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17946AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17946AW\"></sup>who overthrew<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17946AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17946AX\"></sup> its citiesand would not let his captives go home?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17946AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17946AY\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>All the kings of the nations lie in state,each in his own tomb.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17947AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17947AZ\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But you are cast out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17948BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17948BA\"></sup> of your tomblike a rejected branch;you are covered with the slain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17948BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17948BB\"></sup>with those pierced by the sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17948BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17948BC\"></sup>those who descend to the stones of the pit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17948BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17948BD\"></sup>Like a corpse trampled underfoot,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>you will not join them in burial,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17949BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17949BE\"></sup>for you have destroyed your landand killed your people.Let the offspring<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17949BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17949BF\"></sup> of the wicked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17949BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17949BG\"></sup>never be mentioned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17949BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17949BH\"></sup> again.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Prepare a place to slaughter his children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17950BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17950BI\"></sup>for the sins of their ancestors;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17950BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17950BJ\"></sup>they are not to rise to inherit the landand cover the earth with their cities.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“I will rise up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17951BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17951BK\"></sup> against them,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.“I will wipe out Babylon’s name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17951BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17951BL\"></sup> and survivors,her offspring and descendants,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17951BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17951BM\"></sup>”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“I will turn her into a place for owls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17952BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17952BN\"></sup>and into swampland;I will sweep her with the broom of destruction,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17952BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17952BO\"></sup>”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17952BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17952BP\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty has sworn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17953BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17953BQ\"></sup>“Surely, as I have planned,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17953BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17953BR\"></sup> so it will be,and as I have purposed, so it will happen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17953BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17953BS\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I will crush the Assyrian<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17954BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17954BT\"></sup> in my land;on my mountains I will trample him down.His yoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17954BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17954BU\"></sup> will be taken from my people,and his burden removed from their shoulders.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17954BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17954BV\"></sup>”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>This is the plan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17955BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17955BW\"></sup> determined for the whole world;this is the hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17955BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17955BX\"></sup> stretched out over all nations.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty has purposed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17956BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17956BY\"></sup> and who can thwart him?His hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17956BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17956BZ\"></sup> is stretched out, and who can turn it back?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17956CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17956CA\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>This prophecy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17957CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17957CB\"></sup> came in the year<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17957CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17957CC\"></sup> King Ahaz<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17957CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17957CD\"></sup> died:",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Do not rejoice, all you Philistines,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17958CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17958CE\"></sup>that the rod that struck you is broken;from the root of that snake will spring up a viper,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17958CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17958CF\"></sup>its fruit will be a darting, venomous serpent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17958CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17958CG\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>The poorest of the poor will find pasture,and the needy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17959CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17959CH\"></sup> will lie down in safety.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17959CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17959CI\"></sup>But your root I will destroy by famine;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17959CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17959CJ\"></sup>it will slay<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17959CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17959CK\"></sup> your survivors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17959CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17959CL\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Wail,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17960CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17960CM\"></sup> you gate!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17960CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17960CN\"></sup> Howl, you city!Melt away, all you Philistines!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17960CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17960CO\"></sup>A cloud of smoke comes from the north,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17960CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17960CP\"></sup>and there is not a straggler in its ranks.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17960CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17960CQ\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>What answer shall be givento the envoys<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17961CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17961CR\"></sup> of that nation?“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has established Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17961CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17961CS\"></sup>and in her his afflicted people will find refuge.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17961CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17961CT\"></sup>”"
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>A prophecy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17962B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17962B\"></sup> against Moab:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17962C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17962C\"></sup>Ar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17962D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17962D\"></sup> in Moab is ruined,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17962E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17962E\"></sup>destroyed in a night!Kir<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17962F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17962F\"></sup> in Moab is ruined,destroyed in a night!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Dibon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17963G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17963G\"></sup> goes up to its temple,to its high places<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17963H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17963H\"></sup> to weep;Moab wails<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17963I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17963I\"></sup> over Nebo<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17963J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17963J\"></sup> and Medeba.Every head is shaved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17963K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17963K\"></sup>and every beard cut off.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17963L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17963L\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>In the streets they wear sackcloth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17964M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17964M\"></sup>on the roofs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17964N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17964N\"></sup> and in the public squares<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17964O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17964O\"></sup>they all wail,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17964P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17964P\"></sup>prostrate with weeping.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17964Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17964Q\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Heshbon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17965R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17965R\"></sup> and Elealeh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17965S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17965S\"></sup> cry out,their voices are heard all the way to Jahaz.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17965T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17965T\"></sup>Therefore the armed men of Moab cry out,and their hearts are faint.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>My heart cries out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17966U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17966U\"></sup> over Moab;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17966V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17966V\"></sup>her fugitives<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17966W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17966W\"></sup> flee as far as Zoar,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17966X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17966X\"></sup>as far as Eglath Shelishiyah.They go up the hill to Luhith,weeping as they go;on the road to Horonaim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17966Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17966Y\"></sup>they lament their destruction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17966Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17966Z\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The waters of Nimrim are dried up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17967AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17967AA\"></sup>and the grass is withered;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17967AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17967AB\"></sup>the vegetation is gone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17967AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17967AC\"></sup>and nothing green is left.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17967AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17967AD\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So the wealth they have acquired<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17968AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17968AE\"></sup> and stored upthey carry away over the Ravine of the Poplars.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Their outcry echoes along the border of Moab;their wailing reaches as far as Eglaim,their lamentation as far as Beer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17969AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17969AF\"></sup> Elim.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The waters of Dimon are full of blood,but I will bring still more upon Dimon—a lion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17970AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17970AG\"></sup> upon the fugitives of Moab<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17970AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17970AH\"></sup>and upon those who remain in the land."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>Send lambs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17971A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17971A\"></sup> as tribute<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17971B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17971B\"></sup>to the ruler of the land,from Sela,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17971C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17971C\"></sup> across the desert,to the mount of Daughter Zion.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17971D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17971D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Like fluttering birdspushed from the nest,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17972E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17972E\"></sup>so are the women of Moab<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17972F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17972F\"></sup>at the fords<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17972G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17972G\"></sup> of the Arnon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17972H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17972H\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Make up your mind,” Moab says.“Render a decision.Make your shadow like night—at high noon.Hide the fugitives,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17973I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17973I\"></sup>do not betray the refugees.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Let the Moabite fugitives stay with you;be their shelter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17974J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17974J\"></sup> from the destroyer.”The oppressor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17974K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17974K\"></sup> will come to an end,and destruction will cease;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17974L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17974L\"></sup>the aggressor will vanish from the land.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>In love a throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17975M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17975M\"></sup> will be established;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17975N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17975N\"></sup>in faithfulness a man will sit on it—one from the house of David<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17975O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17975O\"></sup>—one who in judging seeks justice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17975P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17975P\"></sup>and speeds the cause of righteousness.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>We have heard of Moab’s<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17976Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17976Q\"></sup> pride<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17976R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17976R\"></sup>—how great is her arrogance!—of her conceit, her pride and her insolence;but her boasts are empty.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore the Moabites wail,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17977S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17977S\"></sup>they wail together for Moab.Lament and grievefor the raisin cakes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17977T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17977T\"></sup> of Kir Hareseth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17977U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17977U\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The fields of Heshbon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17978V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17978V\"></sup> wither,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17978W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17978W\"></sup>the vines of Sibmah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17978X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17978X\"></sup> also.The rulers of the nationshave trampled down the choicest vines,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17978Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17978Y\"></sup>which once reached Jazer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17978Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17978Z\"></sup>and spread toward the desert.Their shoots spread out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17978AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17978AA\"></sup>and went as far as the sea.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17978AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17978AB\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So I weep,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17979AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17979AC\"></sup> as Jazer weeps,for the vines of Sibmah.Heshbon and Elealeh,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17979AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17979AD\"></sup>I drench you with tears!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17979AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17979AE\"></sup>The shouts of joy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17979AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17979AF\"></sup> over your ripened fruitand over your harvests<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17979AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17979AG\"></sup> have been stilled.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Joy and gladness are taken away from the orchards;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17980AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17980AH\"></sup>no one sings or shouts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17980AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17980AI\"></sup> in the vineyards;no one treads<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17980AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17980AJ\"></sup> out wine at the presses,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17980AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17980AK\"></sup>for I have put an end to the shouting.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>My heart laments for Moab<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17981AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17981AL\"></sup> like a harp,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17981AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17981AM\"></sup>my inmost being<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17981AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17981AN\"></sup> for Kir Hareseth.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When Moab appears at her high place,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17982AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17982AO\"></sup>she only wears herself out;when she goes to her shrine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17982AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17982AP\"></sup> to pray,it is to no avail.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17982AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17982AQ\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>This is the word the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has already spoken concerning Moab.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But now the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: “Within three years,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17984AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17984AR\"></sup> as a servant bound by contract<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17984AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17984AS\"></sup> would count them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17984AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17984AT\"></sup> Moab’s splendor and all her many people will be despised,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17984AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17984AU\"></sup> and her survivors will be very few and feeble.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17984AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17984AV\"></sup>"
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>A prophecy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17985A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17985A\"></sup> against Damascus:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17985B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17985B\"></sup>“See, Damascus will no longer be a citybut will become a heap of ruins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17985C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17985C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The cities of Aroer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17986D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17986D\"></sup> will be desertedand left to flocks,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17986E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17986E\"></sup> which will lie down,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17986F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17986F\"></sup>with no one to make them afraid.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17986G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17986G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The fortified<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17987H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17987H\"></sup> city will disappear from Ephraim,and royal power from Damascus;the remnant of Aram will belike the glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17987I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17987I\"></sup> of the Israelites,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17987J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17987J\"></sup>declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17988K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17988K\"></sup> the glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17988L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17988L\"></sup> of Jacob will fade;the fat of his body will waste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17988M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17988M\"></sup> away.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>It will be as when reapers harvest the standing grain,gathering<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17989N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17989N\"></sup> the grain in their arms—as when someone gleans heads of grain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17989O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17989O\"></sup>in the Valley of Rephaim.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17989P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17989P\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Yet some gleanings will remain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17990Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17990Q\"></sup>as when an olive tree is beaten,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17990R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17990R\"></sup>leaving two or three olives on the topmost branches,four or five on the fruitful boughs,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17991S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17991S\"></sup> people will look<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17991T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17991T\"></sup> to their Maker<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17991U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17991U\"></sup>and turn their eyes to the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17991V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17991V\"></sup> of Israel.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They will not look to the altars,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17992W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17992W\"></sup>the work of their hands,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17992X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17992X\"></sup>and they will have no regard for the Asherah poles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17992Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17992Y\"></sup>and the incense altars their fingers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17992Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17992Z\"></sup> have made.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>In that day their strong cities, which they left because of the Israelites, will be like places abandoned to thickets and undergrowth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17993AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17993AA\"></sup> And all will be desolation.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>You have forgotten<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17994AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17994AB\"></sup> God your Savior;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17994AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17994AC\"></sup>you have not remembered the Rock,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17994AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17994AD\"></sup> your fortress.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17994AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17994AE\"></sup>Therefore, though you set out the finest plantsand plant imported vines,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17994AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17994AF\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>though on the day you set them out, you make them grow,and on the morning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17995AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17995AG\"></sup> when you plant them, you bring them to bud,yet the harvest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17995AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17995AH\"></sup> will be as nothing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17995AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17995AI\"></sup>in the day of disease and incurable<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17995AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17995AJ\"></sup> pain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17995AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17995AK\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Woe to the many nations that rage<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17996AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17996AL\"></sup>—they rage like the raging sea!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17996AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17996AM\"></sup>Woe to the peoples who roar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17996AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17996AN\"></sup>—they roar like the roaring of great waters!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17996AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17996AO\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Although the peoples roar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17997AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17997AP\"></sup> like the roar of surging waters,when he rebukes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17997AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17997AQ\"></sup> them they flee<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17997AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17997AR\"></sup> far away,driven before the wind like chaff<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17997AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17997AS\"></sup> on the hills,like tumbleweed before a gale.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17997AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17997AT\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>In the evening, sudden<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17998AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17998AU\"></sup> terror!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17998AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17998AV\"></sup>Before the morning, they are gone!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17998AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17998AW\"></sup>This is the portion of those who loot us,the lot of those who plunder us."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17999A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17999A\"></sup> to the land of whirring wingsalong the rivers of Cush,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17999B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17999B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>which sends envoys<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18000C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18000C\"></sup> by seain papyrus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18000D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18000D\"></sup> boats over the water.Go, swift messengers,to a people tall and smooth-skinned,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18000E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18000E\"></sup>to a people feared far and wide,an aggressive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18000F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18000F\"></sup> nation of strange speech,whose land is divided by rivers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18000G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18000G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>All you people of the world,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18001H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18001H\"></sup>you who live on the earth,when a banner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18001I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18001I\"></sup> is raised on the mountains,you will see it,and when a trumpet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18001J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18001J\"></sup> sounds,you will hear it.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says to me:“I will remain quiet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18002K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18002K\"></sup> and will look on from my dwelling place,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18002L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18002L\"></sup>like shimmering heat in the sunshine,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18002M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18002M\"></sup>like a cloud of dew<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18002N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18002N\"></sup> in the heat of harvest.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For, before the harvest, when the blossom is goneand the flower becomes a ripening grape,he will cut off<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18003O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18003O\"></sup> the shoots with pruning knives,and cut down and take away the spreading branches.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18003P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18003P\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>They will all be left to the mountain birds of prey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18004Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18004Q\"></sup>and to the wild animals;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18004R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18004R\"></sup>the birds will feed on them all summer,the wild animals all winter.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>At that time gifts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18005S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18005S\"></sup> will be brought to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almightyfrom a people tall and smooth-skinned,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18005T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18005T\"></sup>from a people feared<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18005U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18005U\"></sup> far and wide,an aggressive nation of strange speech,whose land is divided by rivers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18005V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18005V\"></sup>—the gifts will be brought to Mount Zion, the place of the Name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18005W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18005W\"></sup>"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>A prophecy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18006A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18006A\"></sup> against Egypt:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18006B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18006B\"></sup>See, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> rides on a swift cloud<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18006C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18006C\"></sup>and is coming to Egypt.The idols of Egypt tremble before him,and the hearts of the Egyptians melt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18006D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18006D\"></sup> with fear.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“I will stir up Egyptian against Egyptian—brother will fight against brother,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18007E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18007E\"></sup>neighbor against neighbor,city against city,kingdom against kingdom.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18007F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18007F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The Egyptians will lose heart,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18008G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18008G\"></sup>and I will bring their plans<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18008H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18008H\"></sup> to nothing;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18008I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18008I\"></sup>they will consult the idols and the spirits of the dead,the mediums and the spiritists.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18008J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18008J\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will hand the Egyptians overto the power of a cruel master,and a fierce king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18009K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18009K\"></sup> will rule over them,”declares the Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The waters of the river will dry up,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18010L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18010L\"></sup>and the riverbed will be parched and dry.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18010M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18010M\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The canals will stink;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18011N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18011N\"></sup>the streams of Egypt will dwindle and dry up.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18011O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18011O\"></sup>The reeds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18011P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18011P\"></sup> and rushes will wither,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18011Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18011Q\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>also the plants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18012R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18012R\"></sup> along the Nile,at the mouth of the river.Every sown field<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18012S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18012S\"></sup> along the Nilewill become parched, will blow away and be no more.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18012T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18012T\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The fishermen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18013U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18013U\"></sup> will groan and lament,all who cast hooks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18013V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18013V\"></sup> into the Nile;those who throw nets on the waterwill pine away.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Those who work with combed flax<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18014W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18014W\"></sup> will despair,the weavers of fine linen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18014X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18014X\"></sup> will lose hope.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The workers in cloth will be dejected,and all the wage earners will be sick at heart.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The officials of Zoan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18016Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18016Y\"></sup> are nothing but fools;the wise counselors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18016Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18016Z\"></sup> of Pharaoh give senseless advice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18016AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18016AA\"></sup>How can you say to Pharaoh,“I am one of the wise men,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18016AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18016AB\"></sup>a disciple of the ancient kings”?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Where are your wise men<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18017AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18017AC\"></sup> now?Let them show you and make knownwhat the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almightyhas planned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18017AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18017AD\"></sup> against Egypt.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The officials of Zoan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18018AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18018AE\"></sup> have become fools,the leaders of Memphis<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18018AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18018AF\"></sup> are deceived;the cornerstones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18018AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18018AG\"></sup> of her peopleshave led Egypt astray.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has poured into thema spirit of dizziness;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18019AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18019AH\"></sup>they make Egypt stagger in all that she does,as a drunkard staggers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18019AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18019AI\"></sup> around in his vomit.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>There is nothing Egypt can do—head or tail, palm branch or reed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18020AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18020AJ\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18021AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18021AK\"></sup> the Egyptians will become weaklings.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18021AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18021AL\"></sup> They will shudder with fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18021AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18021AM\"></sup> at the uplifted hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18021AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18021AN\"></sup> that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty raises against them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And the land of Judah will bring terror to the Egyptians; everyone to whom Judah is mentioned will be terrified,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18022AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18022AO\"></sup> because of what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty is planning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18022AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18022AP\"></sup> against them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18023AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18023AQ\"></sup> five cities<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18023AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18023AR\"></sup> in Egypt will speak the language of Canaan and swear allegiance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18023AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18023AS\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty. One of them will be called the City of the Sun.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18023AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18023AT\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18024AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18024AU\"></sup> there will be an altar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18024AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18024AV\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in the heart of Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18024AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18024AW\"></sup> and a monument<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18024AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18024AX\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> at its border.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>It will be a sign and witness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18025AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18025AY\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty in the land of Egypt. When they cry out to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> because of their oppressors, he will send them a savior<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18025AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18025AZ\"></sup> and defender, and he will rescue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18025BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18025BA\"></sup> them.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will make himself known to the Egyptians, and in that day they will acknowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18026BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18026BB\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. They will worship<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18026BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18026BC\"></sup> with sacrifices and grain offerings; they will make vows to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and keep them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18026BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18026BD\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will strike<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18027BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18027BE\"></sup> Egypt with a plague;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18027BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18027BF\"></sup> he will strike them and heal them. They will turn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18027BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18027BG\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and he will respond to their pleas and heal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18027BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18027BH\"></sup> them.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18028BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18028BI\"></sup> there will be a highway<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18028BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18028BJ\"></sup> from Egypt to Assyria.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18028BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18028BK\"></sup> The Assyrians will go to Egypt and the Egyptians to Assyria. The Egyptians and Assyrians will worship<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18028BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18028BL\"></sup> together.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18029BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18029BM\"></sup> Israel will be the third, along with Egypt and Assyria,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18029BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18029BN\"></sup> a blessing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18029BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18029BO\"></sup> on the earth.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty will bless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18030BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18030BP\"></sup> them, saying, “Blessed be Egypt my people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18030BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18030BQ\"></sup> Assyria my handiwork,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18030BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18030BR\"></sup> and Israel my inheritance.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18030BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18030BS\"></sup>”"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>In the year that the supreme commander,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18031A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18031A\"></sup> sent by Sargon king of Assyria, came to Ashdod<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18031B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18031B\"></sup> and attacked and captured it—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>at that time the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke through Isaiah son of Amoz.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18032C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18032C\"></sup> He said to him, “Take off the sackcloth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18032D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18032D\"></sup> from your body and the sandals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18032E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18032E\"></sup> from your feet.” And he did so, going around stripped<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18032F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18032F\"></sup> and barefoot.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18032G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18032G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said, “Just as my servant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18033H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18033H\"></sup> Isaiah has gone stripped and barefoot for three years,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18033I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18033I\"></sup> as a sign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18033J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18033J\"></sup> and portent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18033K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18033K\"></sup> against Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18033L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18033L\"></sup> and Cush,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18033M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18033M\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>so the king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18034N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18034N\"></sup> of Assyria will lead away stripped<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18034O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18034O\"></sup> and barefoot the Egyptian captives<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18034P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18034P\"></sup> and Cushite<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18034Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18034Q\"></sup> exiles, young and old, with buttocks bared<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18034R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18034R\"></sup>—to Egypt’s shame.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18034S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18034S\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Those who trusted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18035T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18035T\"></sup> in Cush<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18035U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18035U\"></sup> and boasted in Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18035V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18035V\"></sup> will be dismayed and put to shame.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18035W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18035W\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18036X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18036X\"></sup> the people who live on this coast will say, ‘See what has happened<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18036Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18036Y\"></sup> to those we relied on,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18036Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18036Z\"></sup> those we fled to for help<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18036AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18036AA\"></sup> and deliverance from the king of Assyria! How then can we escape?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18036AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18036AB\"></sup>’”"
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>A prophecy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18037A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18037A\"></sup> against the Desert<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18037B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18037B\"></sup> by the Sea:Like whirlwinds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18037C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18037C\"></sup> sweeping through the southland,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18037D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18037D\"></sup>an invader comes from the desert,from a land of terror.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>A dire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18038E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18038E\"></sup> vision has been shown to me:The traitor betrays,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18038F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18038F\"></sup> the looter takes loot.Elam,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18038G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18038G\"></sup> attack! Media,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18038H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18038H\"></sup> lay siege!I will bring to an end all the groaning she caused.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>At this my body is racked with pain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18039I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18039I\"></sup>pangs seize me, like those of a woman in labor;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18039J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18039J\"></sup>I am staggered by what I hear,I am bewildered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18039K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18039K\"></sup> by what I see.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>My heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18040L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18040L\"></sup> falters,fear makes me tremble;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18040M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18040M\"></sup>the twilight I longed forhas become a horror<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18040N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18040N\"></sup> to me.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They set the tables,they spread the rugs,they eat, they drink!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18041O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18041O\"></sup>Get up, you officers,oil the shields!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18041P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18041P\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>This is what the Lord says to me:“Go, post a lookout<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18042Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18042Q\"></sup>and have him report what he sees.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When he sees chariots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18043R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18043R\"></sup>with teams of horses,riders on donkeysor riders on camels,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18043S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18043S\"></sup>let him be alert,fully alert.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And the lookout<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18044T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18044T\"></sup> shouted,“Day after day, my lord, I stand on the watchtower;every night I stay at my post.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Look, here comes a man in a chariot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18045U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18045U\"></sup>with a team of horses.And he gives back the answer:‘Babylon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18045V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18045V\"></sup> has fallen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18045W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18045W\"></sup> has fallen!All the images of its gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18045X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18045X\"></sup>lie shattered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18045Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18045Y\"></sup> on the ground!’”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>My people who are crushed on the threshing floor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18046Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18046Z\"></sup>I tell you what I have heardfrom the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty,from the God of Israel.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>A prophecy against Dumah:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18047AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18047AA\"></sup>Someone calls to me from Seir,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18047AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18047AB\"></sup>“Watchman, what is left of the night?Watchman, what is left of the night?”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The watchman replies,“Morning is coming, but also the night.If you would ask, then ask;and come back yet again.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>A prophecy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18049AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18049AC\"></sup> against Arabia:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18049AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18049AD\"></sup>You caravans of Dedanites,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18049AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18049AE\"></sup>who camp in the thickets of Arabia,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>bring water for the thirsty;you who live in Tema,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18050AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18050AF\"></sup>bring food for the fugitives.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>They flee<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18051AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18051AG\"></sup> from the sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18051AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18051AH\"></sup>from the drawn sword,from the bent bowand from the heat of battle.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>This is what the Lord says to me: “Within one year, as a servant bound by contract<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18052AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18052AI\"></sup> would count it, all the splendor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18052AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18052AJ\"></sup> of Kedar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18052AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18052AK\"></sup> will come to an end.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The survivors of the archers, the warriors of Kedar, will be few.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18053AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18053AL\"></sup>” The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, has spoken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18053AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18053AM\"></sup>"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>A prophecy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18054A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18054A\"></sup> against the Valley<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18054B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18054B\"></sup> of Vision:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18054C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18054C\"></sup>What troubles you now,that you have all gone up on the roofs,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18054D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18054D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>you town so full of commotion,you city of tumult<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18055E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18055E\"></sup> and revelry?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18055F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18055F\"></sup>Your slain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18055G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18055G\"></sup> were not killed by the sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18055H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18055H\"></sup>nor did they die in battle.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>All your leaders have fled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18056I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18056I\"></sup> together;they have been captured<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18056J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18056J\"></sup> without using the bow.All you who were caught were taken prisoner together,having fled while the enemy was still far away.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Therefore I said, “Turn away from me;let me weep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18057K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18057K\"></sup> bitterly.Do not try to console meover the destruction of my people.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18057L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18057L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, has a day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18058M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18058M\"></sup>of tumult and trampling<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18058N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18058N\"></sup> and terror<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18058O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18058O\"></sup>in the Valley of Vision,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18058P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18058P\"></sup>a day of battering down walls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18058Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18058Q\"></sup>and of crying out to the mountains.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Elam<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18059R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18059R\"></sup> takes up the quiver,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18059S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18059S\"></sup>with her charioteers and horses;Kir<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18059T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18059T\"></sup> uncovers the shield.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Your choicest valleys<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18060U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18060U\"></sup> are full of chariots,and horsemen are posted at the city gates.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18060V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18060V\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The Lord stripped away the defenses of Judah,and you looked in that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18061W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18061W\"></sup>to the weapons<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18061X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18061X\"></sup> in the Palace of the Forest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18061Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18061Y\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>You saw that the walls of the City of Davidwere broken through<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18062Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18062Z\"></sup> in many places;you stored up waterin the Lower Pool.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18062AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18062AA\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>You counted the buildings in Jerusalemand tore down houses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18063AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18063AB\"></sup> to strengthen the wall.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18063AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18063AC\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>You built a reservoir between the two walls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18064AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18064AD\"></sup>for the water of the Old Pool,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18064AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18064AE\"></sup>but you did not look to the One who made it,or have regard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18064AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18064AF\"></sup> for the One who planned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18064AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18064AG\"></sup> it long ago.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty,called you on that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18065AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18065AH\"></sup>to weep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18065AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18065AI\"></sup> and to wail,to tear out your hair<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18065AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18065AJ\"></sup> and put on sackcloth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18065AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18065AK\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But see, there is joy and revelry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18066AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18066AL\"></sup>slaughtering of cattle and killing of sheep,eating of meat and drinking of wine!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18066AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18066AM\"></sup>“Let us eat and drink,” you say,“for tomorrow we die!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18066AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18066AN\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty has revealed this in my hearing:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18067AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18067AO\"></sup> “Till your dying day this sin will not be atoned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18067AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18067AP\"></sup> for,” says the Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>This is what the Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, says:“Go, say to this steward,to Shebna<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18068AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18068AQ\"></sup> the palace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18068AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18068AR\"></sup> administrator:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18068AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18068AS\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>What are you doing here and who gave you permissionto cut out a grave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18069AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18069AT\"></sup> for yourself<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18069AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18069AU\"></sup> here,hewing your grave on the heightand chiseling your resting place in the rock?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Beware, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is about to take firm hold of youand hurl<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18070AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18070AV\"></sup> you away, you mighty man.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>He will roll you up tightly like a balland throw<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18071AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18071AW\"></sup> you into a large country.There you will dieand there the chariots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18071AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18071AX\"></sup> you were so proud ofwill become a disgrace to your master’s house.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I will depose you from your office,and you will be ousted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18072AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18072AY\"></sup> from your position.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18072AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18072AZ\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18073BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18073BA\"></sup> I will summon my servant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18073BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18073BB\"></sup> Eliakim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18073BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18073BC\"></sup> son of Hilkiah.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I will clothe him with your robe and fasten your sash<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18074BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18074BD\"></sup> around him and hand your authority<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18074BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18074BE\"></sup> over to him. He will be a father to those who live in Jerusalem and to the people of Judah.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>I will place on his shoulder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18075BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18075BF\"></sup> the key<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18075BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18075BG\"></sup> to the house of David;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18075BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18075BH\"></sup> what he opens no one can shut, and what he shuts no one can open.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18075BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18075BI\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I will drive him like a peg<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18076BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18076BJ\"></sup> into a firm place;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18076BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18076BK\"></sup> he will become a seat of honor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18076BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18076BL\"></sup> for the house of his father.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>All the glory of his family will hang on him: its offspring and offshoots—all its lesser vessels, from the bowls to all the jars.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“In that day,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18078BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18078BM\"></sup>” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, “the peg<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18078BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18078BN\"></sup> driven into the firm place will give way; it will be sheared off and will fall, and the load hanging on it will be cut down.” The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18078BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18078BO\"></sup>"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span>A prophecy against Tyre:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18079A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18079A\"></sup>Wail,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18079B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18079B\"></sup> you ships<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18079C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18079C\"></sup> of Tarshish!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18079D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18079D\"></sup>For Tyre is destroyed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18079E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18079E\"></sup>and left without house or harbor.From the land of Cyprusword has come to them.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Be silent,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18080F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18080F\"></sup> you people of the islandand you merchants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18080G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18080G\"></sup> of Sidon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18080H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18080H\"></sup>whom the seafarers have enriched.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>On the great waterscame the grain of the Shihor;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18081I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18081I\"></sup>the harvest of the Nile<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18081J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18081J\"></sup> was the revenue of Tyre,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18081K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18081K\"></sup>and she became the marketplace of the nations.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Be ashamed, Sidon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18082L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18082L\"></sup> and you fortress of the sea,for the sea has spoken:“I have neither been in labor nor given birth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18082M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18082M\"></sup>I have neither reared sons nor brought up daughters.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When word comes to Egypt,they will be in anguish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18083N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18083N\"></sup> at the report from Tyre.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18083O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18083O\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Cross over to Tarshish;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18084P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18084P\"></sup>wail, you people of the island.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Is this your city of revelry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18085Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18085Q\"></sup>the old, old city,whose feet have taken herto settle in far-off lands?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Who planned this against Tyre,the bestower of crowns,whose merchants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18086R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18086R\"></sup> are princes,whose traders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18086S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18086S\"></sup> are renowned in the earth?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty planned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18087T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18087T\"></sup> it,to bring down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18087U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18087U\"></sup> her pride in all her splendorand to humble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18087V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18087V\"></sup> all who are renowned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18087W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18087W\"></sup> on the earth.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Till your land as they do along the Nile,Daughter Tarshish,for you no longer have a harbor.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has stretched out his hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18089X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18089X\"></sup> over the seaand made its kingdoms tremble.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18089Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18089Y\"></sup>He has given an order concerning Phoeniciathat her fortresses be destroyed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18089Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18089Z\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He said, “No more of your reveling,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18090AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18090AA\"></sup>Virgin Daughter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18090AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18090AB\"></sup> Sidon, now crushed!“Up, cross over to Cyprus;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18090AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18090AC\"></sup>even there you will find no rest.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Look at the land of the Babylonians,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18091AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18091AD\"></sup>this people that is now of no account!The Assyrians<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18091AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18091AE\"></sup> have made ita place for desert creatures;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18091AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18091AF\"></sup>they raised up their siege towers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18091AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18091AG\"></sup>they stripped its fortresses bareand turned it into a ruin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18091AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18091AH\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Wail, you ships<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18092AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18092AI\"></sup> of Tarshish;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18092AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18092AJ\"></sup>your fortress is destroyed!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18092AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18092AK\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>At that time Tyre<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18093AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18093AL\"></sup> will be forgotten for seventy years,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18093AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18093AM\"></sup> the span of a king’s life. But at the end of these seventy years, it will happen to Tyre as in the song of the prostitute:",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Take up a harp, walk through the city,you forgotten prostitute;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18094AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18094AN\"></sup>play the harp well, sing many a song,so that you will be remembered.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>At the end of seventy years,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18095AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18095AO\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will deal with Tyre. She will return to her lucrative prostitution<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18095AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18095AP\"></sup> and will ply her trade with all the kingdoms on the face of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18095AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18095AQ\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Yet her profit and her earnings will be set apart for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18096AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18096AR\"></sup> they will not be stored up or hoarded. Her profits will go to those who live before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18096AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18096AS\"></sup> for abundant food and fine clothes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18096AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18096AT\"></sup>"
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span>See, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is going to lay waste the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18097A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18097A\"></sup>and devastate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18097B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18097B\"></sup> it;he will ruin its faceand scatter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18097C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18097C\"></sup> its inhabitants—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>it will be the samefor priest as for people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18098D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18098D\"></sup>for the master as for his servant,for the mistress as for her servant,for seller as for buyer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18098E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18098E\"></sup>for borrower as for lender,for debtor as for creditor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18098F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18098F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The earth will be completely laid waste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18099G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18099G\"></sup>and totally plundered.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18099H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18099H\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18099I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18099I\"></sup> this word.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The earth dries up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18100J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18100J\"></sup> and withers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18100K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18100K\"></sup>the world languishes and withers,the heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18100L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18100L\"></sup> languish with the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18100M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18100M\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The earth is defiled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18101N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18101N\"></sup> by its people;they have disobeyed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18101O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18101O\"></sup> the laws,violated the statutesand broken the everlasting covenant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18101P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18101P\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore a curse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18102Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18102Q\"></sup> consumes the earth;its people must bear their guilt.Therefore earth’s inhabitants are burned up,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18102R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18102R\"></sup>and very few are left.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The new wine dries up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18103S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18103S\"></sup> and the vine withers;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18103T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18103T\"></sup>all the merrymakers groan.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18103U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18103U\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The joyful timbrels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18104V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18104V\"></sup> are stilled,the noise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18104W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18104W\"></sup> of the revelers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18104X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18104X\"></sup> has stopped,the joyful harp<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18104Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18104Y\"></sup> is silent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18104Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18104Z\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>No longer do they drink wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18105AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18105AA\"></sup> with a song;the beer is bitter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18105AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18105AB\"></sup> to its drinkers.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The ruined city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18106AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18106AC\"></sup> lies desolate;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18106AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18106AD\"></sup>the entrance to every house is barred.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>In the streets they cry out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18107AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18107AE\"></sup> for wine;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18107AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18107AF\"></sup>all joy turns to gloom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18107AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18107AG\"></sup>all joyful sounds are banished from the earth.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The city is left in ruins,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18108AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18108AH\"></sup>its gate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18108AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18108AI\"></sup> is battered to pieces.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So will it be on the earthand among the nations,as when an olive tree is beaten,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18109AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18109AJ\"></sup>or as when gleanings are left after the grape harvest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18109AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18109AK\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They raise their voices, they shout for joy;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18110AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18110AL\"></sup>from the west<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18110AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18110AM\"></sup> they acclaim the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s majesty.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Therefore in the east<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18111AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18111AN\"></sup> give glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18111AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18111AO\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;exalt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18111AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18111AP\"></sup> the name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18111AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18111AQ\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel,in the islands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18111AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18111AR\"></sup> of the sea.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>From the ends of the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18112AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18112AS\"></sup> we hear singing:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18112AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18112AT\"></sup>“Glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18112AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18112AU\"></sup> to the Righteous One.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18112AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18112AV\"></sup>But I said, “I waste away, I waste away!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18112AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18112AW\"></sup>Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18112AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18112AX\"></sup> to me!The treacherous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18112AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18112AY\"></sup> betray!With treachery the treacherous betray!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18112AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18112AZ\"></sup>”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Terror<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18113BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18113BA\"></sup> and pit and snare<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18113BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18113BB\"></sup> await you,people of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18113BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18113BC\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Whoever flees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18114BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18114BD\"></sup> at the sound of terrorwill fall into a pit;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18114BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18114BE\"></sup>whoever climbs out of the pitwill be caught in a snare.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18114BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18114BF\"></sup>The floodgates of the heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18114BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18114BG\"></sup> are opened,the foundations of the earth shake.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18114BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18114BH\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The earth is broken up,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18115BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18115BI\"></sup>the earth is split asunder,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18115BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18115BJ\"></sup>the earth is violently shaken.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The earth reels like a drunkard,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18116BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18116BK\"></sup>it sways like a hut<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18116BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18116BL\"></sup> in the wind;so heavy upon it is the guilt of its rebellion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18116BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18116BM\"></sup>that it falls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18116BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18116BN\"></sup>—never to rise again.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18116BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18116BO\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18117BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18117BP\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will punish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18117BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18117BQ\"></sup>the powers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18117BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18117BR\"></sup> in the heavens aboveand the kings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18117BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18117BS\"></sup> on the earth below.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>They will be herded togetherlike prisoners<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18118BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18118BT\"></sup> bound in a dungeon;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18118BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18118BU\"></sup>they will be shut up in prisonand be punished after many days.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18118BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18118BV\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The moon will be dismayed,the sun<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18119BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18119BW\"></sup> ashamed;for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty will reign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18119BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18119BX\"></sup>on Mount Zion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18119BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18119BY\"></sup> and in Jerusalem,and before its elders—with great glory.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18119BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18119BZ\"></sup>"
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you are my God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18120A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18120A\"></sup>I will exalt you and praise your name,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18120B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18120B\"></sup>for in perfect faithfulness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18120C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18120C\"></sup>you have done wonderful things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18120D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18120D\"></sup>things planned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18120E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18120E\"></sup> long ago.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>You have made the city a heap of rubble,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18121F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18121F\"></sup>the fortified<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18121G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18121G\"></sup> town a ruin,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18121H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18121H\"></sup>the foreigners’ stronghold<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18121I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18121I\"></sup> a city no more;it will never be rebuilt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18121J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18121J\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore strong peoples will honor you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18122K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18122K\"></sup>cities of ruthless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18122L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18122L\"></sup> nations will revere you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You have been a refuge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18123M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18123M\"></sup> for the poor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18123N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18123N\"></sup>a refuge for the needy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18123O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18123O\"></sup> in their distress,a shelter from the storm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18123P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18123P\"></sup>and a shade from the heat.For the breath of the ruthless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18123Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18123Q\"></sup>is like a storm driving against a wall",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>and like the heat of the desert.You silence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18124R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18124R\"></sup> the uproar of foreigners;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18124S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18124S\"></sup>as heat is reduced by the shadow of a cloud,so the song of the ruthless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18124T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18124T\"></sup> is stilled.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>On this mountain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18125U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18125U\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty will preparea feast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18125V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18125V\"></sup> of rich food for all peoples,a banquet of aged wine—the best of meats and the finest of wines.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18125W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18125W\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>On this mountain he will destroythe shroud<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18126X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18126X\"></sup> that enfolds all peoples,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18126Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18126Y\"></sup>the sheet that covers all nations;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>he will swallow up death<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18127Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18127Z\"></sup> forever.The Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will wipe away the tears<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18127AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18127AA\"></sup>from all faces;he will remove his people’s disgrace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18127AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18127AB\"></sup>from all the earth.The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18127AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18127AC\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18128AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18128AD\"></sup> they will say,“Surely this is our God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18128AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18128AE\"></sup>we trusted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18128AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18128AF\"></sup> in him, and he saved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18128AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18128AG\"></sup> us.This is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, we trusted in him;let us rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18128AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18128AH\"></sup> and be glad in his salvation.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18128AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18128AI\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will rest on this mountain;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18129AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18129AJ\"></sup>but Moab<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18129AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18129AK\"></sup> will be trampled in their landas straw is trampled down in the manure.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They will stretch out their hands in it,as swimmers stretch out their hands to swim.God will bring down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18130AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18130AL\"></sup> their pride<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18130AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18130AM\"></sup>despite the cleverness of their hands.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He will bring down your high fortified walls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18131AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18131AN\"></sup>and lay them low;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18131AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18131AO\"></sup>he will bring them down to the ground,to the very dust."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18132A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18132A\"></sup> this song will be sung<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18132B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18132B\"></sup> in the land of Judah:We have a strong city;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18132C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18132C\"></sup>God makes salvationits walls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18132D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18132D\"></sup> and ramparts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18132E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18132E\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Open the gates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18133F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18133F\"></sup>that the righteous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18133G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18133G\"></sup> nation may enter,the nation that keeps faith.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You will keep in perfect peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18134H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18134H\"></sup>those whose minds are steadfast,because they trust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18134I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18134I\"></sup> in you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Trust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18135J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18135J\"></sup> in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> forever,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18135K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18135K\"></sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> himself, is the Rock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18135L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18135L\"></sup> eternal.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He humbles those who dwell on high,he lays the lofty city low;he levels it to the ground<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18136M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18136M\"></sup>and casts it down to the dust.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18136N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18136N\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Feet trample<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18137O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18137O\"></sup> it down—the feet of the oppressed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18137P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18137P\"></sup>the footsteps of the poor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18137Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18137Q\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The path of the righteous is level;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18138R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18138R\"></sup>you, the Upright One,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18138S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18138S\"></sup> make the way of the righteous smooth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18138T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18138T\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Yes, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, walking in the way of your laws,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18139U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18139U\"></sup>we wait<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18139V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18139V\"></sup> for you;your name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18139W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18139W\"></sup> and renownare the desire of our hearts.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>My soul yearns for you in the night;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18140X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18140X\"></sup>in the morning my spirit longs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18140Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18140Y\"></sup> for you.When your judgments<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18140Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18140Z\"></sup> come upon the earth,the people of the world learn righteousness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18140AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18140AA\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But when grace is shown to the wicked,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18141AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18141AB\"></sup>they do not learn righteousness;even in a land of uprightness they go on doing evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18141AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18141AC\"></sup>and do not regard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18141AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18141AD\"></sup> the majesty of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, your hand is lifted high,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18142AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18142AE\"></sup>but they do not see<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18142AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18142AF\"></sup> it.Let them see your zeal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18142AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18142AG\"></sup> for your people and be put to shame;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18142AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18142AH\"></sup>let the fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18142AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18142AI\"></sup> reserved for your enemies consume them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you establish peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18143AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18143AJ\"></sup> for us;all that we have accomplished you have done<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18143AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18143AK\"></sup> for us.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God, other lords<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18144AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18144AL\"></sup> besides you have ruled over us,but your name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18144AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18144AM\"></sup> alone do we honor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18144AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18144AN\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They are now dead,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18145AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18145AO\"></sup> they live no more;their spirits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18145AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18145AP\"></sup> do not rise.You punished them and brought them to ruin;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18145AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18145AQ\"></sup>you wiped out all memory of them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18145AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18145AR\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>You have enlarged the nation, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;you have enlarged the nation.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18146AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18146AS\"></sup>You have gained glory for yourself;you have extended all the borders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18146AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18146AT\"></sup> of the land.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, they came to you in their distress;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18147AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18147AU\"></sup>when you disciplined<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18147AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18147AV\"></sup> them,they could barely whisper<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18147AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18147AW\"></sup> a prayer.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>As a pregnant woman about to give birth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18148AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18148AX\"></sup>writhes and cries out in her pain,so were we in your presence, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>We were with child, we writhed in labor,but we gave birth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18149AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18149AY\"></sup> to wind.We have not brought salvation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18149AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18149AZ\"></sup> to the earth,and the people of the world have not come to life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18149BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18149BA\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But your dead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18150BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18150BB\"></sup> will live, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;their bodies will rise—let those who dwell in the dust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18150BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18150BC\"></sup>wake up and shout for joy—your dew<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18150BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18150BD\"></sup> is like the dew of the morning;the earth will give birth to her dead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18150BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18150BE\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Go, my people, enter your roomsand shut the doors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18151BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18151BF\"></sup> behind you;hide<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18151BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18151BG\"></sup> yourselves for a little whileuntil his wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18151BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18151BH\"></sup> has passed by.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18151BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18151BI\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>See, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is coming<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18152BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18152BJ\"></sup> out of his dwelling<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18152BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18152BK\"></sup>to punish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18152BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18152BL\"></sup> the people of the earth for their sins.The earth will disclose the blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18152BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18152BM\"></sup> shed on it;the earth will conceal its slain no longer."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span>In that day,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18153A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18153A\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will punish with his sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18153B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18153B\"></sup>—his fierce, great and powerful sword—Leviathan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18153C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18153C\"></sup> the gliding serpent,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18153D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18153D\"></sup>Leviathan the coiling serpent;he will slay the monster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18153E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18153E\"></sup> of the sea.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18154F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18154F\"></sup>—“Sing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18154G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18154G\"></sup> about a fruitful vineyard:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18154H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18154H\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, watch over it;I water<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18155I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18155I\"></sup> it continually.I guard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18155J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18155J\"></sup> it day and nightso that no one may harm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18155K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18155K\"></sup> it.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>I am not angry.If only there were briers and thorns confronting me!I would march against them in battle;I would set them all on fire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18156L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18156L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Or else let them come to me for refuge;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18157M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18157M\"></sup>let them make peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18157N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18157N\"></sup> with me,yes, let them make peace with me.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>In days to come Jacob will take root,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18158O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18158O\"></sup>Israel will bud and blossom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18158P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18158P\"></sup>and fill all the world with fruit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18158Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18158Q\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> struck heras he struck<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18159R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18159R\"></sup> down those who struck her?Has she been killedas those were killed who killed her?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>By warfare and exile<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18160S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18160S\"></sup> you contend with her—with his fierce blast he drives her out,as on a day the east wind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18160T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18160T\"></sup> blows.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>By this, then, will Jacob’s guilt be atoned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18161U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18161U\"></sup> for,and this will be the full fruit of the removal of his sin:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18161V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18161V\"></sup>When he makes all the altar stones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18161W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18161W\"></sup>to be like limestone crushed to pieces,no Asherah poles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18161X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18161X\"></sup> or incense altars<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18161Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18161Y\"></sup>will be left standing.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The fortified city stands desolate,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18162Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18162Z\"></sup>an abandoned settlement, forsaken<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18162AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18162AA\"></sup> like the wilderness;there the calves graze,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18162AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18162AB\"></sup>there they lie down;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18162AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18162AC\"></sup>they strip its branches bare.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When its twigs are dry, they are broken off<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18163AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18163AD\"></sup>and women come and make fires<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18163AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18163AE\"></sup> with them.For this is a people without understanding;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18163AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18163AF\"></sup>so their Maker has no compassion on them,and their Creator<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18163AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18163AG\"></sup> shows them no favor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18163AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18163AH\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>In that day the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will thresh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18164AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18164AI\"></sup> from the flowing Euphrates to the Wadi of Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18164AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18164AJ\"></sup> and you, Israel, will be gathered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18164AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18164AK\"></sup> up one by one.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And in that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18165AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18165AL\"></sup> a great trumpet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18165AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18165AM\"></sup> will sound. Those who were perishing in Assyria and those who were exiled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18165AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18165AN\"></sup> in Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18165AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18165AO\"></sup> will come and worship<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18165AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18165AP\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> on the holy mountain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18165AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18165AQ\"></sup> in Jerusalem."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span>Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18166A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18166A\"></sup> to that wreath, the pride of Ephraim’s<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18166B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18166B\"></sup> drunkards,to the fading flower, his glorious beauty,set on the head of a fertile valley<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18166C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18166C\"></sup>—to that city, the pride of those laid low by wine!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18166D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18166D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>See, the Lord has one who is powerful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18167E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18167E\"></sup> and strong.Like a hailstorm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18167F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18167F\"></sup> and a destructive wind,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18167G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18167G\"></sup>like a driving rain and a flooding<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18167H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18167H\"></sup> downpour,he will throw it forcefully to the ground.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>That wreath, the pride of Ephraim’s<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18168I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18168I\"></sup> drunkards,will be trampled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18168J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18168J\"></sup> underfoot.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>That fading flower, his glorious beauty,set on the head of a fertile valley,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18169K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18169K\"></sup>will be like figs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18169L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18169L\"></sup> ripe before harvest—as soon as people see them and take them in hand,they swallow them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18170M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18170M\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almightywill be a glorious<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18170N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18170N\"></sup> crown,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18170O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18170O\"></sup>a beautiful wreathfor the remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18170P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18170P\"></sup> of his people.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He will be a spirit of justice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18171Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18171Q\"></sup>to the one who sits in judgment,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18171R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18171R\"></sup>a source of strengthto those who turn back the battle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18171S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18171S\"></sup> at the gate.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And these also stagger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18172T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18172T\"></sup> from wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18172U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18172U\"></sup>and reel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18172V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18172V\"></sup> from beer:Priests<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18172W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18172W\"></sup> and prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18172X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18172X\"></sup> stagger from beerand are befuddled with wine;they reel from beer,they stagger when seeing visions,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18172Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18172Y\"></sup>they stumble when rendering decisions.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>All the tables are covered with vomit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18173Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18173Z\"></sup>and there is not a spot without filth.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Who is it he is trying to teach?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18174AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18174AA\"></sup>To whom is he explaining his message?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18174AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18174AB\"></sup>To children weaned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18174AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18174AC\"></sup> from their milk,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18174AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18174AD\"></sup>to those just taken from the breast?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For it is:Do this, do that,a rule for this, a rule for that;a little here, a little there.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18175AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18175AE\"></sup>”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Very well then, with foreign lips and strange tongues<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18176AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18176AF\"></sup>God will speak to this people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18176AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18176AG\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>to whom he said,“This is the resting place, let the weary rest”;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18177AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18177AH\"></sup>and, “This is the place of repose”—but they would not listen.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So then, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to them will become:Do this, do that,a rule for this, a rule for that;a little here, a little there<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18178AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18178AI\"></sup>—so that as they go they will fall backward;they will be injured<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18178AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18178AJ\"></sup> and snared and captured.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18178AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18178AK\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18179AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18179AL\"></sup> you scoffers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18179AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18179AM\"></sup>who rule this people in Jerusalem.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>You boast, “We have entered into a covenant with death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18180AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18180AN\"></sup>with the realm of the dead we have made an agreement.When an overwhelming scourge sweeps by,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18180AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18180AO\"></sup>it cannot touch us,for we have made a lie<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18180AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18180AP\"></sup> our refugeand falsehood our hiding place.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18180AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18180AQ\"></sup>”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“See, I lay a stone in Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18181AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18181AR\"></sup> a tested stone,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18181AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18181AS\"></sup>a precious cornerstone for a sure foundation;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18181AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18181AT\"></sup>the one who relies on itwill never be stricken with panic.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18181AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18181AU\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I will make justice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18182AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18182AV\"></sup> the measuring lineand righteousness the plumb line;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18182AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18182AW\"></sup>hail<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18182AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18182AX\"></sup> will sweep away your refuge, the lie,and water will overflow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18182AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18182AY\"></sup> your hiding place.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Your covenant with death will be annulled;your agreement with the realm of the dead will not stand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18183AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18183AZ\"></sup>When the overwhelming scourge sweeps by,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18183BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18183BA\"></sup>you will be beaten down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18183BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18183BB\"></sup> by it.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>As often as it comes it will carry you away;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18184BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18184BC\"></sup>morning after morning,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18184BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18184BD\"></sup> by day and by night,it will sweep through.”The understanding of this messagewill bring sheer terror.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18184BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18184BE\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The bed is too short to stretch out on,the blanket too narrow to wrap around you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18185BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18185BF\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will rise up as he did at Mount Perazim,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18186BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18186BG\"></sup>he will rouse himself as in the Valley of Gibeon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18186BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18186BH\"></sup>—to do his work,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18186BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18186BI\"></sup> his strange work,and perform his task, his alien task.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Now stop your mocking,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18187BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18187BJ\"></sup>or your chains will become heavier;the Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, has told meof the destruction decreed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18187BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18187BK\"></sup> against the whole land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18187BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18187BL\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18188BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18188BM\"></sup> and hear my voice;pay attention and hear what I say.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>When a farmer plows for planting,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18189BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18189BN\"></sup> does he plow continually?Does he keep on breaking up and working the soil?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When he has leveled the surface,does he not sow caraway and scatter cumin?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18190BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18190BO\"></sup>Does he not plant wheat in its place,barley<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18190BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18190BP\"></sup> in its plot,and spelt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18190BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18190BQ\"></sup> in its field?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>His God instructs himand teaches<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18191BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18191BR\"></sup> him the right way.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Caraway is not threshed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18192BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18192BS\"></sup> with a sledge,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18192BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18192BT\"></sup>nor is the wheel of a cart rolled over cumin;caraway is beaten out with a rod,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18192BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18192BU\"></sup>and cumin with a stick.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Grain must be ground to make bread;so one does not go on threshing it forever.The wheels of a threshing cart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18193BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18193BV\"></sup> may be rolled over it,but one does not use horses to grind grain.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>All this also comes from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty,whose plan is wonderful,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18194BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18194BW\"></sup>whose wisdom is magnificent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18194BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18194BX\"></sup>"
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">29 </span>Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18195A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18195A\"></sup> to you, Ariel, Ariel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18195B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18195B\"></sup>the city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18195C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18195C\"></sup> where David settled!Add year to yearand let your cycle of festivals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18195D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18195D\"></sup> go on.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Yet I will besiege Ariel;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18196E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18196E\"></sup>she will mourn and lament,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18196F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18196F\"></sup>she will be to me like an altar hearth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18196G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18196G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I will encamp against you on all sides;I will encircle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18197H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18197H\"></sup> you with towersand set up my siege works<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18197I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18197I\"></sup> against you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Brought low, you will speak from the ground;your speech will mumble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18198J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18198J\"></sup> out of the dust.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18198K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18198K\"></sup>Your voice will come ghostlike<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18198L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18198L\"></sup> from the earth;out of the dust your speech will whisper.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18198M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18198M\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But your many enemies will become like fine dust,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18199N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18199N\"></sup>the ruthless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18199O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18199O\"></sup> hordes like blown chaff.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18199P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18199P\"></sup>Suddenly,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18199Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18199Q\"></sup> in an instant,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty will come<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18200R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18200R\"></sup>with thunder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18200S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18200S\"></sup> and earthquake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18200T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18200T\"></sup> and great noise,with windstorm and tempest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18200U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18200U\"></sup> and flames of a devouring fire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18200V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18200V\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then the hordes of all the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18201W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18201W\"></sup> that fight against Ariel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18201X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18201X\"></sup>that attack her and her fortress and besiege her,will be as it is with a dream,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18201Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18201Y\"></sup>with a vision in the night—",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>as when a hungry person dreams of eating,but awakens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18202Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18202Z\"></sup> hungry still;as when a thirsty person dreams of drinking,but awakens faint and thirsty still.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18202AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18202AA\"></sup>So will it be with the hordes of all the nationsthat fight against Mount Zion.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18202AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18202AB\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Be stunned and amazed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18203AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18203AC\"></sup>blind yourselves and be sightless;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18203AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18203AD\"></sup>be drunk,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18203AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18203AE\"></sup> but not from wine,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18203AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18203AF\"></sup>stagger,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18203AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18203AG\"></sup> but not from beer.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has brought over you a deep sleep:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18204AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18204AH\"></sup>He has sealed your eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18204AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18204AI\"></sup> (the prophets);<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18204AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18204AJ\"></sup>he has covered your heads (the seers).<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18204AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18204AK\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For you this whole vision<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18205AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18205AL\"></sup> is nothing but words sealed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18205AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18205AM\"></sup> in a scroll. And if you give the scroll to someone who can read, and say, “Read this, please,” they will answer, “I can’t; it is sealed.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Or if you give the scroll to someone who cannot read, and say, “Read this, please,” they will answer, “I don’t know how to read.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The Lord says:“These people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18207AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18207AN\"></sup> come near to me with their mouthand honor me with their lips,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18207AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18207AO\"></sup>but their hearts are far from me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18207AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18207AP\"></sup>Their worship of meis based on merely human rules they have been taught.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18207AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18207AQ\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore once more I will astound these peoplewith wonder upon wonder;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18208AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18208AR\"></sup>the wisdom of the wise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18208AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18208AS\"></sup> will perish,the intelligence of the intelligent will vanish.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18208AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18208AT\"></sup>”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Woe to those who go to great depthsto hide<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18209AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18209AU\"></sup> their plans from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,who do their work in darkness and think,“Who sees us?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18209AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18209AV\"></sup> Who will know?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18209AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18209AW\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You turn things upside down,as if the potter were thought to be like the clay!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18210AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18210AX\"></sup>Shall what is formed say to the one who formed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18210AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18210AY\"></sup> it,“You did not make me”?Can the pot say to the potter,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18210AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18210AZ\"></sup>“You know nothing”?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18210BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18210BA\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>In a very short time,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18211BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18211BB\"></sup> will not Lebanon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18211BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18211BC\"></sup> be turned into a fertile field<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18211BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18211BD\"></sup>and the fertile field seem like a forest?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18211BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18211BE\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18212BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18212BF\"></sup> the deaf<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18212BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18212BG\"></sup> will hear the words of the scroll,and out of gloom and darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18212BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18212BH\"></sup>the eyes of the blind will see.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18212BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18212BI\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Once more the humble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18213BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18213BJ\"></sup> will rejoice in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;the needy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18213BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18213BK\"></sup> will rejoice in the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18213BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18213BL\"></sup> of Israel.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The ruthless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18214BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18214BM\"></sup> will vanish,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18214BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18214BN\"></sup>the mockers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18214BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18214BO\"></sup> will disappear,and all who have an eye for evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18214BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18214BP\"></sup> will be cut down—",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>those who with a word make someone out to be guilty,who ensnare the defender in court<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18215BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18215BQ\"></sup>and with false testimony<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18215BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18215BR\"></sup> deprive the innocent of justice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18215BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18215BS\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, who redeemed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18216BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18216BT\"></sup> Abraham,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18216BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18216BU\"></sup> says to the descendants of Jacob:“No longer will Jacob be ashamed;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18216BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18216BV\"></sup>no longer will their faces grow pale.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18216BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18216BW\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When they see among them their children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18217BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18217BX\"></sup>the work of my hands,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18217BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18217BY\"></sup>they will keep my name holy;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18217BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18217BZ\"></sup>they will acknowledge the holiness of the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18217CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18217CA\"></sup> of Jacob,and will stand in awe of the God of Israel.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Those who are wayward<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18218CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18218CB\"></sup> in spirit will gain understanding;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18218CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18218CC\"></sup>those who complain will accept instruction.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18218CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18218CD\"></sup>"
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">30 </span>“Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18219A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18219A\"></sup> to the obstinate children,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18219B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18219B\"></sup>declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“to those who carry out plans that are not mine,forming an alliance,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18219C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18219C\"></sup> but not by my Spirit,heaping sin upon sin;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>who go down to Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18220D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18220D\"></sup>without consulting<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18220E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18220E\"></sup> me;who look for help to Pharaoh’s protection,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18220F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18220F\"></sup>to Egypt’s shade for refuge.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18220G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18220G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But Pharaoh’s protection will be to your shame,Egypt’s shade<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18221H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18221H\"></sup> will bring you disgrace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18221I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18221I\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Though they have officials in Zoan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18222J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18222J\"></sup>and their envoys have arrived in Hanes,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>everyone will be put to shamebecause of a people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18223K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18223K\"></sup> useless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18223L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18223L\"></sup> to them,who bring neither help<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18223M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18223M\"></sup> nor advantage,but only shame and disgrace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18223N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18223N\"></sup>”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>A prophecy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18224O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18224O\"></sup> concerning the animals of the Negev:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18224P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18224P\"></sup>Through a land of hardship and distress,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18224Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18224Q\"></sup>of lions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18224R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18224R\"></sup> and lionesses,of adders and darting snakes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18224S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18224S\"></sup>the envoys carry their riches on donkeys’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18224T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18224T\"></sup> backs,their treasures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18224U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18224U\"></sup> on the humps of camels,to that unprofitable nation,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>to Egypt, whose help is utterly useless.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18225V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18225V\"></sup>Therefore I call herRahab<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18225W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18225W\"></sup> the Do-Nothing.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Go now, write it on a tablet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18226X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18226X\"></sup> for them,inscribe it on a scroll,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18226Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18226Y\"></sup>that for the days to comeit may be an everlasting witness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18226Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18226Z\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For these are rebellious<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18227AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18227AA\"></sup> people, deceitful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18227AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18227AB\"></sup> children,children unwilling to listen to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s instruction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18227AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18227AC\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They say to the seers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18228AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18228AD\"></sup>“See no more visions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18228AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18228AE\"></sup>!”and to the prophets,“Give us no more visions of what is right!Tell us pleasant things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18228AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18228AF\"></sup>prophesy illusions.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18228AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18228AG\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Leave this way,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18229AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18229AH\"></sup>get off this path,and stop confronting<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18229AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18229AI\"></sup> uswith the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18229AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18229AJ\"></sup> of Israel!”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore this is what the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18230AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18230AK\"></sup> of Israel says:“Because you have rejected this message,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18230AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18230AL\"></sup>relied on oppression<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18230AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18230AM\"></sup>and depended on deceit,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>this sin will become for youlike a high wall,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18231AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18231AN\"></sup> cracked and bulging,that collapses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18231AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18231AO\"></sup> suddenly,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18231AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18231AP\"></sup> in an instant.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>It will break in pieces like pottery,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18232AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18232AQ\"></sup>shattered so mercilesslythat among its pieces not a fragment will be foundfor taking coals from a hearthor scooping water out of a cistern.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>This is what the Sovereign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18233AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18233AR\"></sup> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18233AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18233AS\"></sup> of Israel, says:“In repentance and rest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18233AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18233AT\"></sup> is your salvation,in quietness and trust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18233AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18233AU\"></sup> is your strength,but you would have none of it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18233AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18233AV\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You said, ‘No, we will flee<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18234AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18234AW\"></sup> on horses.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18234AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18234AX\"></sup>Therefore you will flee!You said, ‘We will ride off on swift horses.’Therefore your pursuers will be swift!",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>A thousand will fleeat the threat of one;at the threat of five<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18235AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18235AY\"></sup>you will all flee<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18235AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18235AZ\"></sup> away,till you are left<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18235BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18235BA\"></sup>like a flagstaff on a mountaintop,like a banner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18235BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18235BB\"></sup> on a hill.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Yet the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> longs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18236BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18236BC\"></sup> to be gracious to you;therefore he will rise up to show you compassion.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18236BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18236BD\"></sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is a God of justice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18236BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18236BE\"></sup>Blessed are all who wait for him!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18236BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18236BF\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>People of Zion, who live in Jerusalem, you will weep no more.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18237BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18237BG\"></sup> How gracious he will be when you cry for help!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18237BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18237BH\"></sup> As soon as he hears, he will answer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18237BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18237BI\"></sup> you.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Although the Lord gives you the bread<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18238BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18238BJ\"></sup> of adversity and the water of affliction, your teachers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18238BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18238BK\"></sup> will be hidden<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18238BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18238BL\"></sup> no more; with your own eyes you will see them.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Whether you turn to the right or to the left, your ears will hear a voice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18239BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18239BM\"></sup> behind you, saying, “This is the way;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18239BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18239BN\"></sup> walk in it.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Then you will desecrate your idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18240BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18240BO\"></sup> overlaid with silver and your images covered with gold;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18240BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18240BP\"></sup> you will throw them away like a menstrual<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18240BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18240BQ\"></sup> cloth and say to them, “Away with you!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18240BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18240BR\"></sup>”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He will also send you rain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18241BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18241BS\"></sup> for the seed you sow in the ground, and the food that comes from the land will be rich<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18241BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18241BT\"></sup> and plentiful.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18241BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18241BU\"></sup> In that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18241BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18241BV\"></sup> your cattle will graze in broad meadows.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18241BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18241BW\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The oxen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18242BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18242BX\"></sup> and donkeys that work the soil will eat fodder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18242BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18242BY\"></sup> and mash, spread out with fork<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18242BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18242BZ\"></sup> and shovel.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>In the day of great slaughter,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18243CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18243CA\"></sup> when the towers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18243CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18243CB\"></sup> fall, streams of water will flow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18243CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18243CC\"></sup> on every high mountain and every lofty hill.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The moon will shine like the sun,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18244CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18244CD\"></sup> and the sunlight will be seven times brighter, like the light of seven full days, when the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> binds up the bruises of his people and heals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18244CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18244CE\"></sup> the wounds he inflicted.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>See, the Name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18245CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18245CF\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> comes from afar,with burning anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18245CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18245CG\"></sup> and dense clouds of smoke;his lips are full of wrath,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18245CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18245CH\"></sup>and his tongue is a consuming fire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18245CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18245CI\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>His breath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18246CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18246CJ\"></sup> is like a rushing torrent,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18246CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18246CK\"></sup>rising up to the neck.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18246CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18246CL\"></sup>He shakes the nations in the sieve<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18246CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18246CM\"></sup> of destruction;he places in the jaws of the peoplesa bit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18246CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18246CN\"></sup> that leads them astray.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And you will singas on the night you celebrate a holy festival;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18247CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18247CO\"></sup>your hearts will rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18247CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18247CP\"></sup>as when people playing pipes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18247CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18247CQ\"></sup> go upto the mountain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18247CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18247CR\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,to the Rock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18247CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18247CS\"></sup> of Israel.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will cause people to hear his majestic voice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18248CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18248CT\"></sup>and will make them see his arm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18248CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18248CU\"></sup> coming downwith raging anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18248CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18248CV\"></sup> and consuming fire,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18248CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18248CW\"></sup>with cloudburst, thunderstorm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18248CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18248CX\"></sup> and hail.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18248CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18248CY\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will shatter Assyria;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18249CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18249CZ\"></sup>with his rod he will strike<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18249DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18249DA\"></sup> them down.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Every stroke the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lays on themwith his punishing club<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18250DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18250DB\"></sup>will be to the music of timbrels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18250DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18250DC\"></sup> and harps,as he fights them in battle with the blows of his arm.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18250DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18250DD\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Topheth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18251DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18251DE\"></sup> has long been prepared;it has been made ready for the king.Its fire pit has been made deep and wide,with an abundance of fire and wood;the breath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18251DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18251DF\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,like a stream of burning sulfur,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18251DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18251DG\"></sup>sets it ablaze.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18251DH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DH&quot;&gt;DH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18251DH\"></sup>"
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">31 </span>Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18252A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18252A\"></sup> to those who go down to Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18252B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18252B\"></sup> for help,who rely on horses,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18252C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18252C\"></sup>who trust in the multitude of their chariots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18252D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18252D\"></sup>and in the great strength of their horsemen,but do not look to the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18252E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18252E\"></sup> of Israel,or seek help from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18252F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18252F\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Yet he too is wise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18253G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18253G\"></sup> and can bring disaster;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18253H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18253H\"></sup>he does not take back his words.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18253I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18253I\"></sup>He will rise up against that wicked nation,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18253J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18253J\"></sup>against those who help evildoers.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But the Egyptians<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18254K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18254K\"></sup> are mere mortals and not God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18254L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18254L\"></sup>their horses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18254M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18254M\"></sup> are flesh and not spirit.When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> stretches out his hand,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18254N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18254N\"></sup>those who help will stumble,those who are helped<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18254O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18254O\"></sup> will fall;all will perish together.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18254P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18254P\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says to me:“As a lion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18255Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18255Q\"></sup> growls,a great lion over its prey—and though a whole band of shepherds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18255R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18255R\"></sup>is called together against it,it is not frightened by their shoutsor disturbed by their clamor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18255S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18255S\"></sup>—so the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty will come down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18255T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18255T\"></sup>to do battle on Mount Zion and on its heights.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Like birds hovering<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18256U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18256U\"></sup> overhead,the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty will shield<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18256V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18256V\"></sup> Jerusalem;he will shield it and deliver<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18256W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18256W\"></sup> it,he will ‘pass over’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18256X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18256X\"></sup> it and will rescue it.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Return,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18257Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18257Y\"></sup> you Israelites, to the One you have so greatly revolted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18257Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18257Z\"></sup> against.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For in that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18258AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18258AA\"></sup> every one of you will reject the idols of silver and gold<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18258AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18258AB\"></sup> your sinful hands have made.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18258AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18258AC\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Assyria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18259AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18259AD\"></sup> will fall by no human sword;a sword, not of mortals, will devour<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18259AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18259AE\"></sup> them.They will flee before the swordand their young men will be put to forced labor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18259AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18259AF\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Their stronghold<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18260AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18260AG\"></sup> will fall because of terror;at the sight of the battle standard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18260AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18260AH\"></sup> their commanders will panic,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18260AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18260AI\"></sup>”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,whose fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18260AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18260AJ\"></sup> is in Zion,whose furnace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18260AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18260AK\"></sup> is in Jerusalem."
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">32 </span>See, a king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18261A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18261A\"></sup> will reign in righteousnessand rulers will rule with justice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18261B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18261B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Each one will be like a shelter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18262C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18262C\"></sup> from the windand a refuge from the storm,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18262D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18262D\"></sup>like streams of water<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18262E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18262E\"></sup> in the desert<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18262F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18262F\"></sup>and the shadow of a great rock in a thirsty land.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then the eyes of those who see will no longer be closed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18263G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18263G\"></sup>and the ears<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18263H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18263H\"></sup> of those who hear will listen.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The fearful heart will know and understand,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18264I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18264I\"></sup>and the stammering tongue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18264J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18264J\"></sup> will be fluent and clear.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>No longer will the fool<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18265K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18265K\"></sup> be called noblenor the scoundrel be highly respected.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For fools speak folly,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18266L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18266L\"></sup>their hearts are bent on evil:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18266M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18266M\"></sup>They practice ungodliness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18266N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18266N\"></sup>and spread error<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18266O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18266O\"></sup> concerning the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;the hungry they leave empty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18266P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18266P\"></sup>and from the thirsty they withhold water.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Scoundrels use wicked methods,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18267Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18267Q\"></sup>they make up evil schemes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18267R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18267R\"></sup>to destroy the poor with lies,even when the plea of the needy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18267S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18267S\"></sup> is just.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18267T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18267T\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But the noble make noble plans,and by noble deeds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18268U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18268U\"></sup> they stand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18268V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18268V\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>You women<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18269W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18269W\"></sup> who are so complacent,rise up and listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18269X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18269X\"></sup> to me;you daughters who feel secure,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18269Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18269Y\"></sup>hear what I have to say!",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>In little more than a year<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18270Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18270Z\"></sup>you who feel secure will tremble;the grape harvest will fail,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18270AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18270AA\"></sup>and the harvest of fruit will not come.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Tremble,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18271AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18271AB\"></sup> you complacent women;shudder, you daughters who feel secure!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18271AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18271AC\"></sup>Strip off your fine clothes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18271AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18271AD\"></sup>and wrap yourselves in rags.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18271AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18271AE\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Beat your breasts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18272AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18272AF\"></sup> for the pleasant fields,for the fruitful vines<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18272AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18272AG\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and for the land of my people,a land overgrown with thorns and briers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18273AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18273AH\"></sup>—yes, mourn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18273AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18273AI\"></sup> for all houses of merrimentand for this city of revelry.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18273AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18273AJ\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The fortress<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18274AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18274AK\"></sup> will be abandoned,the noisy city deserted;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18274AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18274AL\"></sup>citadel and watchtower<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18274AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18274AM\"></sup> will become a wasteland forever,the delight of donkeys,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18274AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18274AN\"></sup> a pasture for flocks,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18274AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18274AO\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>till the Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18275AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18275AP\"></sup> is poured on us from on high,and the desert becomes a fertile field,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18275AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18275AQ\"></sup>and the fertile field seems like a forest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18275AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18275AR\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s justice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18276AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18276AS\"></sup> will dwell in the desert,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18276AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18276AT\"></sup>his righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18276AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18276AU\"></sup> live in the fertile field.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The fruit of that righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18277AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18277AV\"></sup> will be peace;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18277AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18277AW\"></sup>its effect will be quietness and confidence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18277AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18277AX\"></sup> forever.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>My people will live in peaceful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18278AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18278AY\"></sup> dwelling places,in secure homes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18278AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18278AZ\"></sup>in undisturbed places of rest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18278BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18278BA\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Though hail<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18279BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18279BB\"></sup> flattens the forest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18279BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18279BC\"></sup>and the city is leveled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18279BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18279BD\"></sup> completely,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>how blessed you will be,sowing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18280BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18280BE\"></sup> your seed by every stream,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18280BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18280BF\"></sup>and letting your cattle and donkeys range free.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18280BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18280BG\"></sup>"
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">33 </span>Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18281A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18281A\"></sup> to you, destroyer,you who have not been destroyed!Woe to you, betrayer,you who have not been betrayed!When you stop destroying,you will be destroyed;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18281B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18281B\"></sup>when you stop betraying,you will be betrayed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18281C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18281C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, be gracious<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18282D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18282D\"></sup> to us;we long for you.Be our strength<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18282E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18282E\"></sup> every morning,our salvation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18282F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18282F\"></sup> in time of distress.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18282G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18282G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>At the uproar of your army,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18283H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18283H\"></sup> the peoples flee;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18283I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18283I\"></sup>when you rise up,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18283J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18283J\"></sup> the nations scatter.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Your plunder,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18284K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18284K\"></sup> O nations, is harvested<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18284L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18284L\"></sup> as by young locusts;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18284M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18284M\"></sup>like a swarm of locusts people pounce on it.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is exalted,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18285N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18285N\"></sup> for he dwells on high;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18285O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18285O\"></sup>he will fill Zion with his justice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18285P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18285P\"></sup> and righteousness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18285Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18285Q\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He will be the sure foundation for your times,a rich store of salvation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18286R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18286R\"></sup> and wisdom and knowledge;the fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18286S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18286S\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is the key to this treasure.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18286T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18286T\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Look, their brave men<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18287U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18287U\"></sup> cry aloud in the streets;the envoys<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18287V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18287V\"></sup> of peace weep bitterly.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The highways are deserted,no travelers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18288W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18288W\"></sup> are on the roads.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18288X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18288X\"></sup>The treaty is broken,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18288Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18288Y\"></sup>its witnesses are despised,no one is respected.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The land dries up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18289Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18289Z\"></sup> and wastes away,Lebanon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18289AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18289AA\"></sup> is ashamed and withers;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18289AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18289AB\"></sup>Sharon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18289AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18289AC\"></sup> is like the Arabah,and Bashan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18289AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18289AD\"></sup> and Carmel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18289AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18289AE\"></sup> drop their leaves.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Now will I arise,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18290AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18290AF\"></sup>” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“Now will I be exalted;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18290AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18290AG\"></sup>now will I be lifted up.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>You conceive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18291AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18291AH\"></sup> chaff,you give birth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18291AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18291AI\"></sup> to straw;your breath is a fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18291AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18291AJ\"></sup> that consumes you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The peoples will be burned to ashes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18292AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18292AK\"></sup>like cut thornbushes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18292AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18292AL\"></sup> they will be set ablaze.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18292AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18292AM\"></sup>”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>You who are far away,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18293AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18293AN\"></sup> hear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18293AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18293AO\"></sup> what I have done;you who are near, acknowledge my power!",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The sinners<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18294AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18294AP\"></sup> in Zion are terrified;trembling<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18294AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18294AQ\"></sup> grips the godless:“Who of us can dwell with the consuming fire?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18294AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18294AR\"></sup>Who of us can dwell with everlasting burning?”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Those who walk righteously<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18295AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18295AS\"></sup>and speak what is right,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18295AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18295AT\"></sup>who reject gain from extortion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18295AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18295AU\"></sup>and keep their hands from accepting bribes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18295AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18295AV\"></sup>who stop their ears against plots of murderand shut their eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18295AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18295AW\"></sup> against contemplating evil—",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>they are the ones who will dwell on the heights,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18296AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18296AX\"></sup>whose refuge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18296AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18296AY\"></sup> will be the mountain fortress.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18296AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18296AZ\"></sup>Their bread will be supplied,and water will not fail<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18296BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18296BA\"></sup> them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Your eyes will see the king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18297BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18297BB\"></sup> in his beauty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18297BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18297BC\"></sup>and view a land that stretches afar.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18297BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18297BD\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>In your thoughts you will ponder the former terror:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18298BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18298BE\"></sup>“Where is that chief officer?Where is the one who took the revenue?Where is the officer in charge of the towers?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18298BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18298BF\"></sup>”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>You will see those arrogant people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18299BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18299BG\"></sup> no more,people whose speech is obscure,whose language is strange and incomprehensible.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18299BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18299BH\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Look on Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18300BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18300BI\"></sup> the city of our festivals;your eyes will see Jerusalem,a peaceful abode,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18300BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18300BJ\"></sup> a tent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18300BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18300BK\"></sup> that will not be moved;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18300BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18300BL\"></sup>its stakes will never be pulled up,nor any of its ropes broken.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>There the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be our Mighty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18301BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18301BM\"></sup> One.It will be like a place of broad rivers and streams.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18301BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18301BN\"></sup>No galley with oars will ride them,no mighty ship<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18301BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18301BO\"></sup> will sail them.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is our judge,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18302BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18302BP\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is our lawgiver,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18302BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18302BQ\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is our king;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18302BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18302BR\"></sup>it is he who will save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18302BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18302BS\"></sup> us.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Your rigging hangs loose:The mast is not held secure,the sail is not spread.Then an abundance of spoils will be dividedand even the lame<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18303BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18303BT\"></sup> will carry off plunder.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18303BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18303BU\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>No one living in Zion will say, “I am ill”;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18304BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18304BV\"></sup>and the sins of those who dwell there will be forgiven.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18304BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18304BW\"></sup>"
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">34 </span>Come near, you nations, and listen;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18305A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18305A\"></sup>pay attention, you peoples!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18305B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18305B\"></sup>Let the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18305C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18305C\"></sup> hear, and all that is in it,the world, and all that comes out of it!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18305D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18305D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is angry with all nations;his wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18306E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18306E\"></sup> is on all their armies.He will totally destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18306F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18306F\"></sup> them,he will give them over to slaughter.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18306G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18306G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Their slain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18307H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18307H\"></sup> will be thrown out,their dead bodies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18307I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18307I\"></sup> will stink;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18307J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18307J\"></sup>the mountains will be soaked with their blood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18307K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18307K\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>All the stars in the sky will be dissolved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18308L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18308L\"></sup>and the heavens rolled up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18308M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18308M\"></sup> like a scroll;all the starry host will fall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18308N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18308N\"></sup>like withered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18308O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18308O\"></sup> leaves from the vine,like shriveled figs from the fig tree.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>My sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18309P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18309P\"></sup> has drunk its fill in the heavens;see, it descends in judgment on Edom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18309Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18309Q\"></sup>the people I have totally destroyed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18309R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18309R\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18310S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18310S\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is bathed in blood,it is covered with fat—the blood of lambs and goats,fat from the kidneys of rams.For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has a sacrifice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18310T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18310T\"></sup> in Bozrah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18310U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18310U\"></sup>and a great slaughter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18310V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18310V\"></sup> in the land of Edom.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And the wild oxen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18311W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18311W\"></sup> will fall with them,the bull calves and the great bulls.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18311X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18311X\"></sup>Their land will be drenched with blood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18311Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18311Y\"></sup>and the dust will be soaked with fat.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has a day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18312Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18312Z\"></sup> of vengeance,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18312AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18312AA\"></sup>a year of retribution,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18312AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18312AB\"></sup> to uphold Zion’s cause.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Edom’s streams will be turned into pitch,her dust into burning sulfur;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18313AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18313AC\"></sup>her land will become blazing pitch!",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>It will not be quenched<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18314AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18314AD\"></sup> night or day;its smoke will rise forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18314AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18314AE\"></sup>From generation to generation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18314AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18314AF\"></sup> it will lie desolate;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18314AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18314AG\"></sup>no one will ever pass through it again.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The desert owl<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18315AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18315AH\"></sup> and screech owl will possess it;the great owl and the raven<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18315AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18315AI\"></sup> will nest there.God will stretch out over Edom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18315AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18315AJ\"></sup>the measuring line of chaos<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18315AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18315AK\"></sup>and the plumb line<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18315AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18315AL\"></sup> of desolation.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Her nobles will have nothing there to be called a kingdom,all her princes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18316AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18316AM\"></sup> will vanish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18316AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18316AN\"></sup> away.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Thorns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18317AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18317AO\"></sup> will overrun her citadels,nettles and brambles her strongholds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18317AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18317AP\"></sup>She will become a haunt for jackals,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18317AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18317AQ\"></sup>a home for owls.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18317AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18317AR\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Desert creatures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18318AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18318AS\"></sup> will meet with hyenas,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18318AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18318AT\"></sup>and wild goats will bleat to each other;there the night creatures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18318AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18318AU\"></sup> will also lie downand find for themselves places of rest.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The owl will nest there and lay eggs,she will hatch them, and care for her youngunder the shadow of her wings;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18319AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18319AV\"></sup>there also the falcons<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18319AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18319AW\"></sup> will gather,each with its mate.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Look in the scroll<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18320AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18320AX\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and read:None of these will be missing,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18320AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18320AY\"></sup>not one will lack her mate.For it is his mouth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18320AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18320AZ\"></sup> that has given the order,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18320BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18320BA\"></sup>and his Spirit will gather them together.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He allots their portions;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18321BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18321BB\"></sup>his hand distributes them by measure.They will possess it foreverand dwell there from generation to generation.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18321BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18321BC\"></sup>"
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">35 </span>The desert<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18322A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18322A\"></sup> and the parched land will be glad;the wilderness will rejoice and blossom.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18322B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18322B\"></sup>Like the crocus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18322C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18322C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum mid-line\">2 </sup>it will burst into bloom;it will rejoice greatly and shout for joy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18323D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18323D\"></sup>The glory of Lebanon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18323E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18323E\"></sup> will be given to it,the splendor of Carmel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18323F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18323F\"></sup> and Sharon;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18323G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18323G\"></sup>they will see the glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18323H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18323H\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,the splendor of our God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18323I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18323I\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Strengthen the feeble hands,steady the knees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18324J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18324J\"></sup> that give way;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>say<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18325K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18325K\"></sup> to those with fearful hearts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18325L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18325L\"></sup>“Be strong, do not fear;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18325M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18325M\"></sup>your God will come,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18325N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18325N\"></sup>he will come with vengeance;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18325O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18325O\"></sup>with divine retributionhe will come to save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18325P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18325P\"></sup> you.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then will the eyes of the blind be opened<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18326Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18326Q\"></sup>and the ears of the deaf<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18326R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18326R\"></sup> unstopped.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then will the lame<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18327S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18327S\"></sup> leap like a deer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18327T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18327T\"></sup>and the mute tongue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18327U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18327U\"></sup> shout for joy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18327V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18327V\"></sup>Water will gush forth in the wildernessand streams<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18327W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18327W\"></sup> in the desert.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The burning sand will become a pool,the thirsty ground<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18328X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18328X\"></sup> bubbling springs.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18328Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18328Y\"></sup>In the haunts where jackals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18328Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18328Z\"></sup> once lay,grass and reeds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18328AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18328AA\"></sup> and papyrus will grow.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And a highway<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18329AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18329AB\"></sup> will be there;it will be called the Way of Holiness;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18329AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18329AC\"></sup>it will be for those who walk on that Way.The unclean<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18329AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18329AD\"></sup> will not journey on it;wicked fools will not go about on it.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>No lion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18330AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18330AE\"></sup> will be there,nor any ravenous beast;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18330AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18330AF\"></sup>they will not be found there.But only the redeemed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18330AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18330AG\"></sup> will walk there,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>and those the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has rescued<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18331AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18331AH\"></sup> will return.They will enter Zion with singing;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18331AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18331AI\"></sup>everlasting joy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18331AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18331AJ\"></sup> will crown their heads.Gladness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18331AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18331AK\"></sup> and joy will overtake them,and sorrow and sighing will flee away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18331AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18331AL\"></sup>"
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">36 </span>In the fourteenth year of King Hezekiah’s<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18332B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18332B\"></sup> reign, Sennacherib<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18332C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18332C\"></sup> king of Assyria attacked all the fortified cities of Judah and captured them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18332D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18332D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then the king of Assyria sent his field commander with a large army from Lachish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18333E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18333E\"></sup> to King Hezekiah at Jerusalem. When the commander stopped at the aqueduct of the Upper Pool, on the road to the Launderer’s Field,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18333F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18333F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Eliakim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18334G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18334G\"></sup> son of Hilkiah the palace administrator,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18334H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18334H\"></sup> Shebna<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18334I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18334I\"></sup> the secretary,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18334J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18334J\"></sup> and Joah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18334K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18334K\"></sup> son of Asaph the recorder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18334L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18334L\"></sup> went out to him.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The field commander said to them, “Tell Hezekiah:“‘This is what the great king, the king of Assyria, says: On what are you basing this confidence of yours?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You say you have counsel and might for war—but you speak only empty words. On whom are you depending, that you rebel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18336M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18336M\"></sup> against me?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Look, I know you are depending<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18337N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18337N\"></sup> on Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18337O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18337O\"></sup> that splintered reed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18337P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18337P\"></sup> of a staff, which pierces the hand of anyone who leans on it! Such is Pharaoh king of Egypt to all who depend on him.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But if you say to me, “We are depending<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18338Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18338Q\"></sup> on the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God”—isn’t he the one whose high places and altars Hezekiah removed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18338R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18338R\"></sup> saying to Judah and Jerusalem, “You must worship before this altar”?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18338S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18338S\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“‘Come now, make a bargain with my master, the king of Assyria: I will give you two thousand horses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18339T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18339T\"></sup>—if you can put riders on them!",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>How then can you repulse one officer of the least of my master’s officials, even though you are depending on Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18340U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18340U\"></sup> for chariots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18340V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18340V\"></sup> and horsemen?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18340W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18340W\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Furthermore, have I come to attack and destroy this land without the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>? The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> himself told<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18341X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18341X\"></sup> me to march against this country and destroy it.’”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then Eliakim, Shebna and Joah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18342Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18342Y\"></sup> said to the field commander, “Please speak to your servants in Aramaic,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18342Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18342Z\"></sup> since we understand it. Don’t speak to us in Hebrew in the hearing of the people on the wall.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But the commander replied, “Was it only to your master and you that my master sent me to say these things, and not to the people sitting on the wall—who, like you, will have to eat their own excrement and drink their own urine?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18343AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18343AA\"></sup>”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then the commander stood and called out in Hebrew,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18344AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18344AB\"></sup> “Hear the words of the great king, the king of Assyria!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18344AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18344AC\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>This is what the king says: Do not let Hezekiah deceive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18345AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18345AD\"></sup> you. He cannot deliver you!",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Do not let Hezekiah persuade you to trust in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> when he says, ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will surely deliver<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18346AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18346AE\"></sup> us; this city will not be given into the hand of the king of Assyria.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18346AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18346AF\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Do not listen to Hezekiah. This is what the king of Assyria says: Make peace with me and come out to me. Then each of you will eat fruit from your own vine and fig tree<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18347AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18347AG\"></sup> and drink water from your own cistern,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18347AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18347AH\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>until I come and take you to a land like your own<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18348AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18348AI\"></sup>—a land of grain and new wine,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18348AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18348AJ\"></sup> a land of bread and vineyards.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Do not let Hezekiah mislead you when he says, ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will deliver us.’ Have the gods of any nations ever delivered their lands from the hand of the king of Assyria?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Where are the gods of Hamath and Arpad?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18350AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18350AK\"></sup> Where are the gods of Sepharvaim?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18350AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18350AL\"></sup> Have they rescued Samaria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18350AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18350AM\"></sup> from my hand?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Who of all the gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18351AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18351AN\"></sup> of these countries have been able to save their lands from me? How then can the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> deliver Jerusalem from my hand?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18351AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18351AO\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But the people remained silent and said nothing in reply, because the king had commanded, “Do not answer him.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18352AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18352AP\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Then Eliakim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18353AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18353AQ\"></sup> son of Hilkiah the palace administrator, Shebna the secretary and Joah son of Asaph the recorder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18353AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18353AR\"></sup> went to Hezekiah, with their clothes torn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18353AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18353AS\"></sup> and told him what the field commander had said."
		},
		"37": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">37 </span>When King Hezekiah heard this, he tore his clothes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18354B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18354B\"></sup> and put on sackcloth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18354C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18354C\"></sup> and went into the temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18354D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18354D\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He sent Eliakim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18355E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18355E\"></sup> the palace administrator, Shebna<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18355F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18355F\"></sup> the secretary, and the leading priests, all wearing sackcloth, to the prophet Isaiah son of Amoz.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18355G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18355G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>They told him, “This is what Hezekiah says: This day is a day of distress<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18356H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18356H\"></sup> and rebuke and disgrace, as when children come to the moment of birth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18356I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18356I\"></sup> and there is no strength to deliver them.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>It may be that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will hear the words of the field commander, whom his master, the king of Assyria, has sent to ridicule<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18357J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18357J\"></sup> the living God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18357K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18357K\"></sup> and that he will rebuke him for the words the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has heard.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18357L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18357L\"></sup> Therefore pray<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18357M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18357M\"></sup> for the remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18357N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18357N\"></sup> that still survives.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When King Hezekiah’s officials came to Isaiah,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Isaiah said to them, “Tell your master, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Do not be afraid<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18359O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18359O\"></sup> of what you have heard—those words with which the underlings of the king of Assyria have blasphemed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18359P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18359P\"></sup> me.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Listen! When he hears a certain report,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18360Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18360Q\"></sup> I will make him want<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18360R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18360R\"></sup> to return to his own country, and there I will have him cut down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18360S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18360S\"></sup> with the sword.’”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>When the field commander heard that the king of Assyria had left Lachish,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18361T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18361T\"></sup> he withdrew and found the king fighting against Libnah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18361U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18361U\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Now Sennacherib<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18362V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18362V\"></sup> received a report<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18362W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18362W\"></sup> that Tirhakah, the king of Cush,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18362X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18362X\"></sup> was marching out to fight against him. When he heard it, he sent messengers to Hezekiah with this word:",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Say to Hezekiah king of Judah: Do not let the god you depend on deceive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18363Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18363Y\"></sup> you when he says, ‘Jerusalem will not be given into the hands of the king of Assyria.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18363Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18363Z\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Surely you have heard what the kings of Assyria have done to all the countries, destroying them completely. And will you be delivered?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18364AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18364AA\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Did the gods of the nations that were destroyed by my predecessors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18365AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18365AB\"></sup> deliver them—the gods of Gozan, Harran,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18365AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18365AC\"></sup> Rezeph and the people of Eden<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18365AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18365AD\"></sup> who were in Tel Assar?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Where is the king of Hamath or the king of Arpad?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18366AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18366AE\"></sup> Where are the kings of Lair, Sepharvaim,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18366AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18366AF\"></sup> Hena and Ivvah?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18366AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18366AG\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Hezekiah received the letter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18367AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18367AI\"></sup> from the messengers and read it. Then he went up to the temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18367AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18367AJ\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and spread it out before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And Hezekiah prayed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18368AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18368AK\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, enthroned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18369AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18369AL\"></sup> between the cherubim,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18369AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18369AM\"></sup> you alone are God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18369AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18369AN\"></sup> over all the kingdoms<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18369AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18369AO\"></sup> of the earth. You have made heaven and earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18369AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18369AP\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Give ear, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and hear;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18370AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18370AQ\"></sup> open your eyes, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and see;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18370AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18370AR\"></sup> listen to all the words Sennacherib<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18370AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18370AS\"></sup> has sent to ridicule<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18370AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18370AT\"></sup> the living God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18370AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18370AU\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“It is true, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, that the Assyrian kings have laid waste all these peoples and their lands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18371AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18371AV\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>They have thrown their gods into the fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18372AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18372AW\"></sup> and destroyed them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18372AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18372AX\"></sup> for they were not gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18372AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18372AY\"></sup> but only wood and stone, fashioned by human hands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18372AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18372AZ\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Now, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God, deliver<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18373BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18373BA\"></sup> us from his hand, so that all the kingdoms of the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18373BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18373BB\"></sup> may know that you, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, are the only God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18373BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18373BC\"></sup>”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then Isaiah son of Amoz<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18374BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18374BE\"></sup> sent a message to Hezekiah: “This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, says: Because you have prayed to me concerning Sennacherib king of Assyria,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>this is the word the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken against him:“Virgin Daughter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18375BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18375BF\"></sup> Zion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18375BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18375BG\"></sup>despises and mocks you.Daughter Jerusalemtosses her head<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18375BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18375BH\"></sup> as you flee.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Who is it you have ridiculed and blasphemed?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18376BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18376BI\"></sup>Against whom have you raised your voice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18376BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18376BJ\"></sup>and lifted your eyes in pride?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18376BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18376BK\"></sup>Against the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18376BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18376BL\"></sup> of Israel!",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>By your messengersyou have ridiculed the Lord.And you have said,‘With my many chariots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18377BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18377BM\"></sup>I have ascended the heights of the mountains,the utmost heights<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18377BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18377BN\"></sup> of Lebanon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18377BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18377BO\"></sup>I have cut down its tallest cedars,the choicest of its junipers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18377BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18377BP\"></sup>I have reached its remotest heights,the finest of its forests.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I have dug wells in foreign landsand drunk the water there.With the soles of my feetI have dried up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18378BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18378BQ\"></sup> all the streams of Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18378BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18378BR\"></sup>’",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Have you not heard?Long ago I ordained<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18379BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18379BS\"></sup> it.In days of old I planned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18379BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18379BT\"></sup> it;now I have brought it to pass,that you have turned fortified citiesinto piles of stone.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18379BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18379BU\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Their people, drained of power,are dismayed and put to shame.They are like plants in the field,like tender green shoots,like grass<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18380BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18380BV\"></sup> sprouting on the roof,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18380BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18380BW\"></sup>scorched before it grows up.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“But I know where you areand when you come and go<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18381BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18381BX\"></sup>and how you rage<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18381BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18381BY\"></sup> against me.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Because you rage against meand because your insolence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18382BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18382BZ\"></sup> has reached my ears,I will put my hook<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18382CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18382CA\"></sup> in your nose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18382CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18382CB\"></sup>and my bit in your mouth,and I will make you returnby the way you came.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18382CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18382CC\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“This will be the sign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18383CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18383CD\"></sup> for you, Hezekiah:“This year<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18383CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18383CE\"></sup> you will eat what grows by itself,and the second year what springs from that.But in the third year<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18383CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18383CF\"></sup> sow and reap,plant vineyards<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18383CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18383CG\"></sup> and eat their fruit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18383CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18383CH\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Once more a remnant of the kingdom of Judahwill take root<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18384CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18384CI\"></sup> below and bear fruit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18384CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18384CJ\"></sup> above.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>For out of Jerusalem will come a remnant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18385CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18385CK\"></sup>and out of Mount Zion a band of survivors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18385CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18385CL\"></sup>The zeal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18385CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18385CM\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almightywill accomplish this.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says concerning the king of Assyria:“He will not enter this city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18386CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18386CN\"></sup>or shoot an arrow here.He will not come before it with shieldor build a siege ramp<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18386CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18386CO\"></sup> against it.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>By the way that he came he will return;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18387CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18387CP\"></sup>he will not enter this city,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“I will defend<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18388CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18388CQ\"></sup> this city and save it,for my sake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18388CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18388CR\"></sup> and for the sake of David<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18388CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18388CS\"></sup> my servant!”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Then the angel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18389CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18389CT\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> went out and put to death<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18389CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18389CU\"></sup> a hundred and eighty-five thousand in the Assyrian<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18389CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18389CV\"></sup> camp. When the people got up the next morning—there were all the dead bodies!",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>So Sennacherib<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18390CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18390CW\"></sup> king of Assyria broke camp and withdrew. He returned to Nineveh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18390CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18390CX\"></sup> and stayed there.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>One day, while he was worshiping in the temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18391CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18391CY\"></sup> of his god Nisrok, his sons Adrammelek and Sharezer killed him with the sword, and they escaped to the land of Ararat.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18391CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18391CZ\"></sup> And Esarhaddon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18391DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18391DA\"></sup> his son succeeded him as king.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18391DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18391DB\"></sup>"
		},
		"38": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">38 </span>In those days Hezekiah became ill and was at the point of death. The prophet Isaiah son of Amoz<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18392B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18392B\"></sup> went to him and said, “This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Put your house in order,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18392C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18392C\"></sup> because you are going to die; you will not recover.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18392D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18392D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Hezekiah turned his face to the wall and prayed to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Remember, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, how I have walked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18394E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18394E\"></sup> before you faithfully and with wholehearted devotion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18394F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18394F\"></sup> and have done what is good in your eyes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18394G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18394G\"></sup>” And Hezekiah wept<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18394H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18394H\"></sup> bitterly.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then the word<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18395I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18395I\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Isaiah:",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Go and tell Hezekiah, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of your father David,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18396J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18396J\"></sup> says: I have heard your prayer and seen your tears;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18396K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18396K\"></sup> I will add fifteen years<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18396L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18396L\"></sup> to your life.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And I will deliver you and this city from the hand of the king of Assyria. I will defend<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18397M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18397M\"></sup> this city.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“‘This is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s sign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18398N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18398N\"></sup> to you that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will do what he has promised:",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will make the shadow cast by the sun go back the ten steps it has gone down on the stairway of Ahaz.’” So the sunlight went back the ten steps it had gone down.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18399O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18399O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>A writing of Hezekiah king of Judah after his illness and recovery:",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I said, “In the prime of my life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18401P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18401P\"></sup>must I go through the gates of death<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18401Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18401Q\"></sup>and be robbed of the rest of my years?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18401R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18401R\"></sup>”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I said, “I will not again see the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> himself<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18402S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18402S\"></sup>in the land of the living;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18402T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18402T\"></sup>no longer will I look on my fellow man,or be with those who now dwell in this world.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Like a shepherd’s tent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18403U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18403U\"></sup> my househas been pulled down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18403V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18403V\"></sup> and taken from me.Like a weaver I have rolled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18403W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18403W\"></sup> up my life,and he has cut me off from the loom;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18403X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18403X\"></sup>day and night<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18403Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18403Y\"></sup> you made an end of me.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I waited patiently<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18404Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18404Z\"></sup> till dawn,but like a lion he broke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18404AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18404AA\"></sup> all my bones;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18404AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18404AB\"></sup>day and night<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18404AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18404AC\"></sup> you made an end of me.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I cried like a swift or thrush,I moaned like a mourning dove.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18405AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18405AD\"></sup>My eyes grew weak<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18405AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18405AE\"></sup> as I looked to the heavens.I am being threatened; Lord, come to my aid!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18405AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18405AF\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But what can I say?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18406AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18406AG\"></sup>He has spoken to me, and he himself has done this.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18406AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18406AH\"></sup>I will walk humbly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18406AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18406AI\"></sup> all my yearsbecause of this anguish of my soul.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18406AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18406AJ\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Lord, by such things people live;and my spirit finds life in them too.You restored me to healthand let me live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18407AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18407AK\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Surely it was for my benefit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18408AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18408AL\"></sup>that I suffered such anguish.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18408AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18408AM\"></sup>In your love you kept mefrom the pit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18408AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18408AN\"></sup> of destruction;you have put all my sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18408AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18408AO\"></sup>behind your back.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18408AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18408AP\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For the grave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18409AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18409AQ\"></sup> cannot praise you,death cannot sing your praise;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18409AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18409AR\"></sup>those who go down to the pit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18409AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18409AS\"></sup>cannot hope for your faithfulness.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The living, the living—they praise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18410AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18410AT\"></sup> you,as I am doing today;parents tell their children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18410AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18410AU\"></sup>about your faithfulness.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will save me,and we will sing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18411AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18411AV\"></sup> with stringed instruments<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18411AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18411AW\"></sup>all the days of our lives<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18411AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18411AX\"></sup>in the temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18411AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18411AY\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Isaiah had said, “Prepare a poultice of figs and apply it to the boil, and he will recover.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Hezekiah had asked, “What will be the sign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18413AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18413AZ\"></sup> that I will go up to the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?”"
		},
		"39": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">39 </span>At that time Marduk-Baladan son of Baladan king of Babylon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18414B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18414B\"></sup> sent Hezekiah letters and a gift, because he had heard of his illness and recovery.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Hezekiah received the envoys<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18415C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18415C\"></sup> gladly and showed them what was in his storehouses—the silver, the gold,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18415D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18415D\"></sup> the spices, the fine olive oil—his entire armory and everything found among his treasures.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18415E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18415E\"></sup> There was nothing in his palace or in all his kingdom that Hezekiah did not show them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then Isaiah the prophet went to King Hezekiah and asked, “What did those men say, and where did they come from?”“From a distant land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18416F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18416F\"></sup>” Hezekiah replied. “They came to me from Babylon.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The prophet asked, “What did they see in your palace?”“They saw everything in my palace,” Hezekiah said. “There is nothing among my treasures that I did not show them.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then Isaiah said to Hezekiah, “Hear the word<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18418G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18418G\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty:",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The time will surely come when everything in your palace, and all that your predecessors have stored up until this day, will be carried off to Babylon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18419H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18419H\"></sup> Nothing will be left, says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And some of your descendants, your own flesh and blood who will be born to you, will be taken away, and they will become eunuchs in the palace of the king of Babylon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18420I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18420I\"></sup>”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> you have spoken is good,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18421J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18421J\"></sup>” Hezekiah replied. For he thought, “There will be peace and security in my lifetime.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18421K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18421K\"></sup>”"
		},
		"40": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">40 </span>Comfort, comfort<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18422A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18422A\"></sup> my people,says your God.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Speak tenderly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18423B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18423B\"></sup> to Jerusalem,and proclaim to herthat her hard service<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18423C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18423C\"></sup> has been completed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18423D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18423D\"></sup>that her sin has been paid for,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18423E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18423E\"></sup>that she has received from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s handdouble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18423F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18423F\"></sup> for all her sins.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>A voice of one calling:“In the wilderness preparethe way<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18424G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18424G\"></sup> for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;make straight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18424H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18424H\"></sup> in the deserta highway for our God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18424I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18424I\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Every valley shall be raised up,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18425J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18425J\"></sup>every mountain and hill<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18425K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18425K\"></sup> made low;the rough ground shall become level,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18425L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18425L\"></sup>the rugged places a plain.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And the glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18426M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18426M\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be revealed,and all people will see it together.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18426N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18426N\"></sup>For the mouth of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18426O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18426O\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>A voice says, “Cry out.”And I said, “What shall I cry?”“All people are like grass,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18427P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18427P\"></sup>and all their faithfulness is like the flowers of the field.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The grass withers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18428Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18428Q\"></sup> and the flowers fall,because the breath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18428R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18428R\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> blows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18428S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18428S\"></sup> on them.Surely the people are grass.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The grass withers and the flowers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18429T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18429T\"></sup> fall,but the word<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18429U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18429U\"></sup> of our God endures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18429V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18429V\"></sup> forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18429W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18429W\"></sup>”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>You who bring good news<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18430X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18430X\"></sup> to Zion,go up on a high mountain.You who bring good news to Jerusalem,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18430Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18430Y\"></sup>lift up your voice with a shout,lift it up, do not be afraid;say to the towns of Judah,“Here is your God!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18430Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18430Z\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>See, the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> comes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18431AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18431AA\"></sup> with power,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18431AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18431AB\"></sup>and he rules<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18431AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18431AC\"></sup> with a mighty arm.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18431AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18431AD\"></sup>See, his reward<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18431AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18431AE\"></sup> is with him,and his recompense accompanies him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He tends his flock like a shepherd:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18432AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18432AF\"></sup>He gathers the lambs in his arms<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18432AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18432AG\"></sup>and carries them close to his heart;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18432AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18432AH\"></sup>he gently leads<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18432AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18432AI\"></sup> those that have young.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18432AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18432AJ\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Who has measured the waters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18433AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18433AK\"></sup> in the hollow of his hand,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18433AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18433AL\"></sup>or with the breadth of his hand marked off the heavens?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18433AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18433AM\"></sup>Who has held the dust of the earth in a basket,or weighed the mountains on the scalesand the hills in a balance?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18433AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18433AN\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Who can fathom the Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18434AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18434AO\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,or instruct the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> as his counselor?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18434AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18434AP\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Whom did the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> consult to enlighten him,and who taught him the right way?Who was it that taught him knowledge,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18435AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18435AQ\"></sup>or showed him the path of understanding?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18435AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18435AR\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Surely the nations are like a drop in a bucket;they are regarded as dust on the scales;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18436AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18436AS\"></sup>he weighs the islands as though they were fine dust.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18436AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18436AT\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Lebanon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18437AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18437AU\"></sup> is not sufficient for altar fires,nor its animals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18437AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18437AV\"></sup> enough for burnt offerings.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Before him all the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18438AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18438AW\"></sup> are as nothing;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18438AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18438AX\"></sup>they are regarded by him as worthlessand less than nothing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18438AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18438AY\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>With whom, then, will you compare God?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18439AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18439AZ\"></sup>To what image<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18439BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18439BA\"></sup> will you liken him?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>As for an idol,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18440BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18440BB\"></sup> a metalworker casts it,and a goldsmith<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18440BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18440BC\"></sup> overlays it with gold<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18440BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18440BD\"></sup>and fashions silver chains for it.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>A person too poor to present such an offeringselects wood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18441BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18441BE\"></sup> that will not rot;they look for a skilled workerto set up an idol<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18441BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18441BF\"></sup> that will not topple.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18441BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18441BG\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Do you not know?Have you not heard?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18442BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18442BH\"></sup>Has it not been told<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18442BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18442BI\"></sup> you from the beginning?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18442BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18442BJ\"></sup>Have you not understood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18442BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18442BK\"></sup> since the earth was founded?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18442BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18442BL\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>He sits enthroned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18443BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18443BM\"></sup> above the circle of the earth,and its people are like grasshoppers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18443BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18443BN\"></sup>He stretches out the heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18443BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18443BO\"></sup> like a canopy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18443BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18443BP\"></sup>and spreads them out like a tent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18443BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18443BQ\"></sup> to live in.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18443BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18443BR\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He brings princes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18444BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18444BS\"></sup> to naughtand reduces the rulers of this world to nothing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18444BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18444BT\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>No sooner are they planted,no sooner are they sown,no sooner do they take root<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18445BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18445BU\"></sup> in the ground,than he blows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18445BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18445BV\"></sup> on them and they wither,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18445BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18445BW\"></sup>and a whirlwind sweeps them away like chaff.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18445BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18445BX\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“To whom will you compare me?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18446BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18446BY\"></sup>Or who is my equal?” says the Holy One.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18446BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18446BZ\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Lift up your eyes and look to the heavens:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18447CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18447CA\"></sup>Who created<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18447CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18447CB\"></sup> all these?He who brings out the starry host<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18447CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18447CC\"></sup> one by oneand calls forth each of them by name.Because of his great power and mighty strength,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18447CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18447CD\"></sup>not one of them is missing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18447CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18447CE\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Why do you complain, Jacob?Why do you say, Israel,“My way is hidden from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;my cause is disregarded by my God”?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18448CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18448CF\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Do you not know?Have you not heard?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18449CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18449CG\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is the everlasting<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18449CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18449CH\"></sup> God,the Creator<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18449CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18449CI\"></sup> of the ends of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18449CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18449CJ\"></sup>He will not grow tired or weary,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18449CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18449CK\"></sup>and his understanding no one can fathom.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18449CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18449CL\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>He gives strength<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18450CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18450CM\"></sup> to the weary<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18450CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18450CN\"></sup>and increases the power of the weak.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Even youths grow tired and weary,and young men<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18451CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18451CO\"></sup> stumble and fall;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18451CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18451CP\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>but those who hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18452CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18452CQ\"></sup> in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>will renew their strength.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18452CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18452CR\"></sup>They will soar on wings like eagles;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18452CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18452CS\"></sup>they will run and not grow weary,they will walk and not be faint.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18452CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18452CT\"></sup>"
		},
		"41": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">41 </span>“Be silent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18453A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18453A\"></sup> before me, you islands!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18453B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18453B\"></sup>Let the nations renew their strength!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18453C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18453C\"></sup>Let them come forward<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18453D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18453D\"></sup> and speak;let us meet together<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18453E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18453E\"></sup> at the place of judgment.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Who has stirred<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18454F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18454F\"></sup> up one from the east,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18454G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18454G\"></sup>calling him in righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18454H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18454H\"></sup> to his service?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18454I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18454I\"></sup>He hands nations over to himand subdues kings before him.He turns them to dust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18454J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18454J\"></sup> with his sword,to windblown chaff<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18454K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18454K\"></sup> with his bow.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18454L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18454L\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He pursues them and moves on unscathed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18455M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18455M\"></sup>by a path his feet have not traveled before.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Who has done this and carried it through,calling<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18456N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18456N\"></sup> forth the generations from the beginning?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18456O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18456O\"></sup>I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>—with the first of themand with the last<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18456P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18456P\"></sup>—I am he.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18456Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18456Q\"></sup>”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The islands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18457R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18457R\"></sup> have seen it and fear;the ends of the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18457S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18457S\"></sup> tremble.They approach and come forward;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>they help each otherand say to their companions, “Be strong!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18458T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18458T\"></sup>”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The metalworker<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18459U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18459U\"></sup> encourages the goldsmith,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18459V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18459V\"></sup>and the one who smooths with the hammerspurs on the one who strikes the anvil.One says of the welding, “It is good.”The other nails down the idol so it will not topple.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18459W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18459W\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“But you, Israel, my servant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18460X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18460X\"></sup>Jacob, whom I have chosen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18460Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18460Y\"></sup>you descendants of Abraham<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18460Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18460Z\"></sup> my friend,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18460AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18460AA\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I took you from the ends of the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18461AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18461AB\"></sup>from its farthest corners I called<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18461AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18461AC\"></sup> you.I said, ‘You are my servant’;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18461AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18461AD\"></sup>I have chosen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18461AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18461AE\"></sup> you and have not rejected you.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So do not fear,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18462AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18462AF\"></sup> for I am with you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18462AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18462AG\"></sup>do not be dismayed, for I am your God.I will strengthen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18462AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18462AH\"></sup> you and help<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18462AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18462AI\"></sup> you;I will uphold you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18462AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18462AJ\"></sup> with my righteous right hand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18462AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18462AK\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“All who rage<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18463AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18463AL\"></sup> against youwill surely be ashamed and disgraced;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18463AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18463AM\"></sup>those who oppose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18463AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18463AN\"></sup> youwill be as nothing and perish.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18463AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18463AO\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Though you search for your enemies,you will not find them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18464AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18464AP\"></sup>Those who wage war against youwill be as nothing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18464AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18464AQ\"></sup> at all.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your Godwho takes hold of your right hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18465AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18465AR\"></sup>and says to you, Do not fear;I will help<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18465AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18465AS\"></sup> you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Do not be afraid,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18466AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18466AT\"></sup> you worm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18466AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18466AU\"></sup> Jacob,little Israel, do not fear,for I myself will help<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18466AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18466AV\"></sup> you,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,your Redeemer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18466AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18466AW\"></sup> the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18466AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18466AX\"></sup> of Israel.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“See, I will make you into a threshing sledge,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18467AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18467AY\"></sup>new and sharp, with many teeth.You will thresh the mountains<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18467AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18467AZ\"></sup> and crush them,and reduce the hills to chaff.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18467BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18467BA\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You will winnow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18468BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18468BB\"></sup> them, the wind will pick them up,and a gale<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18468BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18468BC\"></sup> will blow them away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18468BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18468BD\"></sup>But you will rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18468BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18468BE\"></sup> in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18468BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18468BF\"></sup> in the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18468BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18468BG\"></sup> of Israel.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“The poor and needy search for water,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18469BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18469BH\"></sup>but there is none;their tongues are parched with thirst.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18469BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18469BI\"></sup>But I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will answer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18469BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18469BJ\"></sup> them;I, the God of Israel, will not forsake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18469BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18469BK\"></sup> them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I will make rivers flow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18470BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18470BL\"></sup> on barren heights,and springs within the valleys.I will turn the desert<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18470BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18470BM\"></sup> into pools of water,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18470BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18470BN\"></sup>and the parched ground into springs.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18470BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18470BO\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I will put in the desert<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18471BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18471BP\"></sup>the cedar and the acacia,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18471BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18471BQ\"></sup> the myrtle and the olive.I will set junipers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18471BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18471BR\"></sup> in the wasteland,the fir and the cypress<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18471BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18471BS\"></sup> together,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18471BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18471BT\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>so that people may see and know,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18472BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18472BU\"></sup>may consider and understand,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18472BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18472BV\"></sup>that the hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18472BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18472BW\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has done this,that the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18472BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18472BX\"></sup> of Israel has created<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18472BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18472BY\"></sup> it.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Present your case,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18473BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18473BZ\"></sup>” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“Set forth your arguments,” says Jacob’s King.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18473CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18473CA\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Tell us, you idols,what is going to happen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18474CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18474CB\"></sup>Tell us what the former things<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18474CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18474CC\"></sup> were,so that we may consider themand know their final outcome.Or declare to us the things to come,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18474CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18474CD\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>tell us what the future holds,so we may know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18475CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18475CE\"></sup> that you are gods.Do something, whether good or bad,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18475CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18475CF\"></sup>so that we will be dismayed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18475CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18475CG\"></sup> and filled with fear.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But you are less than nothing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18476CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18476CH\"></sup>and your works are utterly worthless;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18476CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18476CI\"></sup>whoever chooses you is detestable.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18476CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18476CJ\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“I have stirred<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18477CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18477CK\"></sup> up one from the north,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18477CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18477CL\"></sup> and he comes—one from the rising sun who calls on my name.He treads<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18477CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18477CM\"></sup> on rulers as if they were mortar,as if he were a potter treading the clay.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Who told of this from the beginning,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18478CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18478CN\"></sup> so we could know,or beforehand, so we could say, ‘He was right’?No one told of this,no one foretold<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18478CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18478CO\"></sup> it,no one heard any words<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18478CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18478CP\"></sup> from you.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>I was the first to tell<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18479CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18479CQ\"></sup> Zion, ‘Look, here they are!’I gave to Jerusalem a messenger of good news.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18479CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18479CR\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>I look but there is no one<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18480CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18480CS\"></sup>—no one among the gods to give counsel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18480CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18480CT\"></sup>no one to give answer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18480CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18480CU\"></sup> when I ask them.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>See, they are all false!Their deeds amount to nothing;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18481CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18481CV\"></sup>their images<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18481CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18481CW\"></sup> are but wind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18481CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18481CX\"></sup> and confusion."
		},
		"42": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">42 </span>“Here is my servant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18482A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18482A\"></sup> whom I uphold,my chosen one<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18482B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18482B\"></sup> in whom I delight;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18482C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18482C\"></sup>I will put my Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18482D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18482D\"></sup> on him,and he will bring justice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18482E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18482E\"></sup> to the nations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18482F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18482F\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He will not shout or cry out,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18483G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18483G\"></sup>or raise his voice in the streets.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>A bruised reed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18484H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18484H\"></sup> he will not break,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18484I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18484I\"></sup>and a smoldering wick he will not snuff out.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18484J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18484J\"></sup>In faithfulness he will bring forth justice;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18484K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18484K\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>he will not falter or be discouragedtill he establishes justice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18485L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18485L\"></sup> on earth.In his teaching<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18485M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18485M\"></sup> the islands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18485N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18485N\"></sup> will put their hope.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18485O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18485O\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>This is what God the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says—the Creator of the heavens,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18486P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18486P\"></sup> who stretches them out,who spreads out the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18486Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18486Q\"></sup> with all that springs from it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18486R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18486R\"></sup>who gives breath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18486S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18486S\"></sup> to its people,and life to those who walk on it:",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have called<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18487T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18487T\"></sup> you in righteousness;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18487U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18487U\"></sup>I will take hold of your hand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18487V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18487V\"></sup>I will keep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18487W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18487W\"></sup> you and will make youto be a covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18487X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18487X\"></sup> for the peopleand a light<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18487Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18487Y\"></sup> for the Gentiles,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18487Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18487Z\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>to open eyes that are blind,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18488AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18488AA\"></sup>to free<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18488AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18488AB\"></sup> captives from prison<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18488AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18488AC\"></sup>and to release from the dungeon those who sit in darkness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18488AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18488AD\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18489AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18489AE\"></sup> that is my name!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18489AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18489AF\"></sup>I will not yield my glory to another<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18489AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18489AG\"></sup>or my praise to idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18489AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18489AH\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>See, the former things<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18490AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18490AI\"></sup> have taken place,and new things I declare;before they spring into beingI announce<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18490AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18490AJ\"></sup> them to you.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Sing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18491AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18491AK\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> a new song,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18491AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18491AL\"></sup>his praise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18491AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18491AM\"></sup> from the ends of the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18491AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18491AN\"></sup>you who go down to the sea, and all that is in it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18491AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18491AO\"></sup>you islands,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18491AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18491AP\"></sup> and all who live in them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Let the wilderness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18492AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18492AQ\"></sup> and its towns raise their voices;let the settlements where Kedar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18492AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18492AR\"></sup> lives rejoice.Let the people of Sela<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18492AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18492AS\"></sup> sing for joy;let them shout from the mountaintops.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18492AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18492AT\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Let them give glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18493AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18493AU\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and proclaim his praise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18493AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18493AV\"></sup> in the islands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18493AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18493AW\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will march out like a champion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18494AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18494AX\"></sup>like a warrior<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18494AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18494AY\"></sup> he will stir up his zeal;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18494AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18494AZ\"></sup>with a shout<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18494BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18494BA\"></sup> he will raise the battle cryand will triumph over his enemies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18494BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18494BB\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“For a long time I have kept silent,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18495BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18495BC\"></sup>I have been quiet and held myself back.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18495BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18495BD\"></sup>But now, like a woman in childbirth,I cry out, I gasp and pant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18495BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18495BE\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I will lay waste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18496BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18496BF\"></sup> the mountains<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18496BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18496BG\"></sup> and hillsand dry up all their vegetation;I will turn rivers into islandsand dry up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18496BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18496BH\"></sup> the pools.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I will lead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18497BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18497BI\"></sup> the blind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18497BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18497BJ\"></sup> by ways they have not known,along unfamiliar paths I will guide them;I will turn the darkness into light<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18497BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18497BK\"></sup> before themand make the rough places smooth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18497BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18497BL\"></sup>These are the things I will do;I will not forsake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18497BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18497BM\"></sup> them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But those who trust in idols,who say to images, ‘You are our gods,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18498BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18498BN\"></sup>will be turned back in utter shame.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18498BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18498BO\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Hear, you deaf;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18499BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18499BP\"></sup>look, you blind, and see!",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Who is blind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18500BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18500BQ\"></sup> but my servant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18500BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18500BR\"></sup>and deaf like the messenger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18500BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18500BS\"></sup> I send?Who is blind like the one in covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18500BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18500BT\"></sup> with me,blind like the servant of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>You have seen many things, but you pay no attention;your ears are open, but you do not listen.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18501BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18501BU\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>It pleased the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>for the sake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18502BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18502BV\"></sup> of his righteousnessto make his law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18502BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18502BW\"></sup> great and glorious.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But this is a people plundered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18503BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18503BX\"></sup> and looted,all of them trapped in pits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18503BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18503BY\"></sup>or hidden away in prisons.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18503BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18503BZ\"></sup>They have become plunder,with no one to rescue them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18503CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18503CA\"></sup>they have been made loot,with no one to say, “Send them back.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Which of you will listen to thisor pay close attention<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18504CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18504CB\"></sup> in time to come?",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Who handed Jacob over to become loot,and Israel to the plunderers?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18505CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18505CC\"></sup>Was it not the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18505CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18505CD\"></sup>against whom we have sinned?For they would not follow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18505CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18505CE\"></sup> his ways;they did not obey his law.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18505CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18505CF\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>So he poured out on them his burning anger,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18506CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18506CG\"></sup>the violence of war.It enveloped them in flames,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18506CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18506CH\"></sup> yet they did not understand;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18506CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18506CI\"></sup>it consumed them, but they did not take it to heart.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18506CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18506CJ\"></sup>"
		},
		"43": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">43 </span>But now, this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says—he who created<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18507A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18507A\"></sup> you, Jacob,he who formed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18507B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18507B\"></sup> you, Israel:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18507C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18507C\"></sup>“Do not fear, for I have redeemed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18507D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18507D\"></sup> you;I have summoned you by name;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18507E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18507E\"></sup> you are mine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18507F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18507F\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When you pass through the waters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18508G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18508G\"></sup>I will be with you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18508H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18508H\"></sup>and when you pass through the rivers,they will not sweep over you.When you walk through the fire,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18508I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18508I\"></sup>you will not be burned;the flames will not set you ablaze.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18508J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18508J\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18509K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18509K\"></sup>the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18509L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18509L\"></sup> of Israel, your Savior;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18509M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18509M\"></sup>I give Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18509N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18509N\"></sup> for your ransom,Cush<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18509O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18509O\"></sup> and Seba<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18509P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18509P\"></sup> in your stead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18509Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18509Q\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Since you are precious and honored<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18510R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18510R\"></sup> in my sight,and because I love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18510S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18510S\"></sup> you,I will give people in exchange for you,nations in exchange for your life.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Do not be afraid,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18511T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18511T\"></sup> for I am with you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18511U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18511U\"></sup>I will bring your children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18511V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18511V\"></sup> from the eastand gather<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18511W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18511W\"></sup> you from the west.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18511X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18511X\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I will say to the north, ‘Give them up!’and to the south,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18512Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18512Y\"></sup> ‘Do not hold them back.’Bring my sons from afarand my daughters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18512Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18512Z\"></sup> from the ends of the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18512AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18512AA\"></sup>—",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>everyone who is called by my name,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18513AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18513AB\"></sup>whom I created<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18513AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18513AC\"></sup> for my glory,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18513AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18513AD\"></sup>whom I formed and made.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18513AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18513AE\"></sup>”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Lead out those who have eyes but are blind,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18514AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18514AF\"></sup>who have ears but are deaf.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18514AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18514AG\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>All the nations gather together<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18515AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18515AH\"></sup>and the peoples assemble.Which of their gods foretold<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18515AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18515AI\"></sup> thisand proclaimed to us the former things?Let them bring in their witnesses to prove they were right,so that others may hear and say, “It is true.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“You are my witnesses,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18516AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18516AJ\"></sup>” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“and my servant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18516AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18516AK\"></sup> whom I have chosen,so that you may know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18516AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18516AL\"></sup> and believe meand understand that I am he.Before me no god<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18516AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18516AM\"></sup> was formed,nor will there be one after me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18516AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18516AN\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I, even I, am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18517AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18517AO\"></sup>and apart from me there is no savior.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18517AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18517AP\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I have revealed and saved and proclaimed—I, and not some foreign god<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18518AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18518AQ\"></sup> among you.You are my witnesses,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18518AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18518AR\"></sup>” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “that I am God.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Yes, and from ancient days<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18519AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18519AS\"></sup> I am he.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18519AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18519AT\"></sup>No one can deliver out of my hand.When I act, who can reverse it?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18519AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18519AU\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says—your Redeemer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18520AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18520AV\"></sup> the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18520AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18520AW\"></sup> of Israel:“For your sake I will send to Babylonand bring down as fugitives<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18520AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18520AX\"></sup> all the Babylonians,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18520AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18520AY\"></sup>in the ships in which they took pride.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18521AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18521AZ\"></sup> your Holy One,Israel’s Creator,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18521BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18521BA\"></sup> your King.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18521BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18521BB\"></sup>”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says—he who made a way through the sea,a path through the mighty waters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18522BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18522BC\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>who drew out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18523BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18523BD\"></sup> the chariots and horses,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18523BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18523BE\"></sup>the army and reinforcements together,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18523BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18523BF\"></sup>and they lay<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18523BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18523BG\"></sup> there, never to rise again,extinguished, snuffed out like a wick:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18523BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18523BH\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Forget the former things;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18524BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18524BI\"></sup>do not dwell on the past.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>See, I am doing a new thing!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18525BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18525BJ\"></sup>Now it springs up; do you not perceive it?I am making a way in the wilderness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18525BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18525BK\"></sup>and streams in the wasteland.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18525BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18525BL\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The wild animals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18526BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18526BM\"></sup> honor me,the jackals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18526BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18526BN\"></sup> and the owls,because I provide water<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18526BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18526BO\"></sup> in the wildernessand streams in the wasteland,to give drink to my people, my chosen,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>the people I formed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18527BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18527BP\"></sup> for myself<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18527BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18527BQ\"></sup>that they may proclaim my praise.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18527BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18527BR\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Yet you have not called on me, Jacob,you have not wearied<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18528BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18528BS\"></sup> yourselves for me, Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18528BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18528BT\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>You have not brought me sheep for burnt offerings,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18529BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18529BU\"></sup>nor honored<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18529BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18529BV\"></sup> me with your sacrifices.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18529BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18529BW\"></sup>I have not burdened<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18529BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18529BX\"></sup> you with grain offeringsnor wearied you with demands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18529BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18529BY\"></sup> for incense.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18529BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18529BZ\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>You have not bought any fragrant calamus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18530CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18530CA\"></sup> for me,or lavished on me the fat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18530CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18530CB\"></sup> of your sacrifices.But you have burdened me with your sinsand wearied<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18530CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18530CC\"></sup> me with your offenses.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18530CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18530CD\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“I, even I, am he who blots outyour transgressions,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18531CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18531CE\"></sup> for my own sake,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18531CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18531CF\"></sup>and remembers your sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18531CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18531CG\"></sup> no more.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18531CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18531CH\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Review the past for me,let us argue the matter together;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18532CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18532CI\"></sup>state the case<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18532CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18532CJ\"></sup> for your innocence.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Your first father<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18533CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18533CK\"></sup> sinned;those I sent to teach<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18533CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18533CL\"></sup> you rebelled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18533CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18533CM\"></sup> against me.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So I disgraced the dignitaries of your temple;I consigned Jacob to destruction<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18534CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18534CN\"></sup>and Israel to scorn.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18534CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18534CO\"></sup>"
		},
		"44": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">44 </span>“But now listen, Jacob, my servant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18535A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18535A\"></sup>Israel, whom I have chosen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18535B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18535B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says—he who made<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18536C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18536C\"></sup> you, who formed you in the womb,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18536D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18536D\"></sup>and who will help<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18536E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18536E\"></sup> you:Do not be afraid,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18536F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18536F\"></sup> Jacob, my servant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18536G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18536G\"></sup>Jeshurun,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18536H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18536H\"></sup> whom I have chosen.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For I will pour water<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18537I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18537I\"></sup> on the thirsty land,and streams on the dry ground;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18537J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18537J\"></sup>I will pour out my Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18537K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18537K\"></sup> on your offspring,and my blessing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18537L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18537L\"></sup> on your descendants.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18537M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18537M\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They will spring up like grass<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18538N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18538N\"></sup> in a meadow,like poplar trees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18538O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18538O\"></sup> by flowing streams.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18538P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18538P\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Some will say, ‘I belong<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18539Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18539Q\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’;others will call themselves by the name of Jacob;still others will write on their hand,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18539R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18539R\"></sup> ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18539S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18539S\"></sup>and will take the name Israel.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says—Israel’s King<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18540T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18540T\"></sup> and Redeemer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18540U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18540U\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty:I am the first and I am the last;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18540V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18540V\"></sup>apart from me there is no God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18540W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18540W\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Who then is like me?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18541X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18541X\"></sup> Let him proclaim it.Let him declare and lay out before mewhat has happened since I established my ancient people,and what is yet to come—yes, let them foretell<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18541Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18541Y\"></sup> what will come.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Do not tremble, do not be afraid.Did I not proclaim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18542Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18542Z\"></sup> this and foretell it long ago?You are my witnesses. Is there any God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18542AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18542AA\"></sup> besides me?No, there is no other Rock;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18542AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18542AB\"></sup> I know not one.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>All who make idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18543AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18543AC\"></sup> are nothing,and the things they treasure are worthless.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18543AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18543AD\"></sup>Those who would speak up for them are blind;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18543AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18543AE\"></sup>they are ignorant, to their own shame.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18543AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18543AF\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Who shapes a god and casts an idol,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18544AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18544AG\"></sup>which can profit nothing?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18544AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18544AH\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>People who do that will be put to shame;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18545AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18545AI\"></sup>such craftsmen are only human beings.Let them all come together and take their stand;they will be brought down to terror and shame.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18545AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18545AJ\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The blacksmith<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18546AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18546AK\"></sup> takes a tooland works with it in the coals;he shapes an idol with hammers,he forges it with the might of his arm.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18546AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18546AL\"></sup>He gets hungry and loses his strength;he drinks no water and grows faint.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18546AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18546AM\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The carpenter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18547AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18547AN\"></sup> measures with a lineand makes an outline with a marker;he roughs it out with chiselsand marks it with compasses.He shapes it in human form,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18547AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18547AO\"></sup>human form in all its glory,that it may dwell in a shrine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18547AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18547AP\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>He cut down cedars,or perhaps took a cypress or oak.He let it grow among the trees of the forest,or planted a pine,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18548AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18548AQ\"></sup> and the rain made it grow.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>It is used as fuel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18549AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18549AR\"></sup> for burning;some of it he takes and warms himself,he kindles a fire and bakes bread.But he also fashions a god and worships<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18549AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18549AS\"></sup> it;he makes an idol and bows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18549AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18549AT\"></sup> down to it.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Half of the wood he burns in the fire;over it he prepares his meal,he roasts his meat and eats his fill.He also warms himself and says,“Ah! I am warm; I see the fire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18550AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18550AU\"></sup>”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>From the rest he makes a god, his idol;he bows down to it and worships.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18551AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18551AV\"></sup>He prays<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18551AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18551AW\"></sup> to it and says,“Save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18551AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18551AX\"></sup> me! You are my god!”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>They know nothing, they understand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18552AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18552AY\"></sup> nothing;their eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18552AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18552AZ\"></sup> are plastered over so they cannot see,and their minds closed so they cannot understand.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>No one stops to think,no one has the knowledge or understanding<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18553BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18553BA\"></sup> to say,“Half of it I used for fuel;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18553BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18553BB\"></sup>I even baked bread over its coals,I roasted meat and I ate.Shall I make a detestable<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18553BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18553BC\"></sup> thing from what is left?Shall I bow down to a block of wood?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18553BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18553BD\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Such a person feeds on ashes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18554BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18554BE\"></sup> a deluded<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18554BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18554BF\"></sup> heart misleads him;he cannot save himself, or say,“Is not this thing in my right hand a lie?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18554BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18554BG\"></sup>”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Remember<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18555BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18555BH\"></sup> these things, Jacob,for you, Israel, are my servant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18555BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18555BI\"></sup>I have made you, you are my servant;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18555BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18555BJ\"></sup>Israel, I will not forget you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18555BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18555BK\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>I have swept away<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18556BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18556BL\"></sup> your offenses like a cloud,your sins like the morning mist.Return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18556BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18556BM\"></sup> to me,for I have redeemed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18556BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18556BN\"></sup> you.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Sing for joy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18557BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18557BO\"></sup> you heavens, for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has done this;shout aloud, you earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18557BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18557BP\"></sup> beneath.Burst into song, you mountains,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18557BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18557BQ\"></sup>you forests and all your trees,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18557BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18557BR\"></sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has redeemed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18557BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18557BS\"></sup> Jacob,he displays his glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18557BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18557BT\"></sup> in Israel.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says—your Redeemer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18558BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18558BU\"></sup> who formed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18558BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18558BV\"></sup> you in the womb:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18558BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18558BW\"></sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,the Maker of all things,who stretches out the heavens,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18558BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18558BX\"></sup>who spreads out the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18558BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18558BY\"></sup> by myself,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>who foils<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18559BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18559BZ\"></sup> the signs of false prophetsand makes fools of diviners,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18559CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18559CA\"></sup>who overthrows the learning of the wise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18559CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18559CB\"></sup>and turns it into nonsense,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18559CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18559CC\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>who carries out the words<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18560CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18560CD\"></sup> of his servantsand fulfills<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18560CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18560CE\"></sup> the predictions of his messengers,who says of Jerusalem,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18560CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18560CF\"></sup> ‘It shall be inhabited,’of the towns of Judah, ‘They shall be rebuilt,’and of their ruins,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18560CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18560CG\"></sup> ‘I will restore them,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18560CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18560CH\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>who says to the watery deep, ‘Be dry,and I will dry up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18561CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18561CI\"></sup> your streams,’",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>who says of Cyrus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18562CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18562CJ\"></sup> ‘He is my shepherdand will accomplish all that I please;he will say of Jerusalem,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18562CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18562CK\"></sup> “Let it be rebuilt,”and of the temple,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18562CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18562CL\"></sup> “Let its foundations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18562CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18562CM\"></sup> be laid.”’"
		},
		"45": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">45 </span>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says to his anointed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18563A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18563A\"></sup>to Cyrus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18563B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18563B\"></sup> whose right hand I take hold<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18563C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18563C\"></sup> ofto subdue nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18563D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18563D\"></sup> before himand to strip kings of their armor,to open doors before himso that gates will not be shut:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I will go before you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18564E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18564E\"></sup>and will level<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18564F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18564F\"></sup> the mountains;I will break down gates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18564G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18564G\"></sup> of bronzeand cut through bars of iron.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18564H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18564H\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I will give you hidden treasures,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18565I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18565I\"></sup>riches stored in secret places,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18565J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18565J\"></sup>so that you may know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18565K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18565K\"></sup> that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,the God of Israel, who summons you by name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18565L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18565L\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For the sake of Jacob my servant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18566M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18566M\"></sup>of Israel my chosen,I summon you by nameand bestow on you a title of honor,though you do not acknowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18566N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18566N\"></sup> me.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and there is no other;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18567O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18567O\"></sup>apart from me there is no God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18567P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18567P\"></sup>I will strengthen you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18567Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18567Q\"></sup>though you have not acknowledged me,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>so that from the rising of the sunto the place of its setting<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18568R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18568R\"></sup>people may know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18568S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18568S\"></sup> there is none besides me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18568T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18568T\"></sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and there is no other.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I form the light and create darkness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18569U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18569U\"></sup>I bring prosperity and create disaster;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18569V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18569V\"></sup>I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, do all these things.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“You heavens above, rain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18570W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18570W\"></sup> down my righteousness;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18570X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18570X\"></sup>let the clouds shower it down.Let the earth open wide,let salvation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18570Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18570Y\"></sup> spring up,let righteousness flourish with it;I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have created it.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Woe to those who quarrel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18571Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18571Z\"></sup> with their Maker,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18571AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18571AA\"></sup>those who are nothing but potsherds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18571AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18571AB\"></sup>among the potsherds on the ground.Does the clay say to the potter,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18571AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18571AC\"></sup>‘What are you making?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18571AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18571AD\"></sup>Does your work say,‘The potter has no hands’?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18571AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18571AE\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Woe to the one who says to a father,‘What have you begotten?’or to a mother,‘What have you brought to birth?’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says—the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18573AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18573AF\"></sup> of Israel, and its Maker:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18573AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18573AG\"></sup>Concerning things to come,do you question me about my children,or give me orders about the work of my hands?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18573AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18573AH\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>It is I who made the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18574AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18574AI\"></sup>and created mankind on it.My own hands stretched out the heavens;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18574AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18574AJ\"></sup>I marshaled their starry hosts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18574AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18574AK\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I will raise up Cyrus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18575AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18575AL\"></sup> in my righteousness:I will make all his ways straight.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18575AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18575AM\"></sup>He will rebuild my city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18575AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18575AN\"></sup>and set my exiles free,but not for a price or reward,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18575AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18575AO\"></sup>says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“The products<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18576AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18576AP\"></sup> of Egypt and the merchandise of Cush,and those tall Sabeans<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18576AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18576AQ\"></sup>—they will come over to you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18576AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18576AR\"></sup>and will be yours;they will trudge behind you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18576AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18576AS\"></sup>coming over to you in chains.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18576AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18576AT\"></sup>They will bow down before youand plead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18576AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18576AU\"></sup> with you, saying,‘Surely God is with you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18576AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18576AV\"></sup> and there is no other;there is no other god.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18576AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18576AW\"></sup>’”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Truly you are a God who has been hiding<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18577AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18577AX\"></sup> himself,the God and Savior<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18577AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18577AY\"></sup> of Israel.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>All the makers of idols will be put to shame and disgraced;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18578AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18578AZ\"></sup>they will go off into disgrace together.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But Israel will be saved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18579BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18579BA\"></sup> by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>with an everlasting salvation;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18579BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18579BB\"></sup>you will never be put to shame or disgraced,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18579BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18579BC\"></sup>to ages everlasting.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says—he who created the heavens,he is God;he who fashioned and made the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18580BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18580BD\"></sup>he founded it;he did not create it to be empty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18580BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18580BE\"></sup>but formed it to be inhabited<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18580BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18580BF\"></sup>—he says:“I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and there is no other.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18580BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18580BG\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I have not spoken in secret,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18581BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18581BH\"></sup>from somewhere in a land of darkness;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18581BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18581BI\"></sup>I have not said to Jacob’s descendants,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18581BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18581BJ\"></sup>‘Seek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18581BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18581BK\"></sup> me in vain.’I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, speak the truth;I declare what is right.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18581BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18581BL\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Gather together<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18582BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18582BM\"></sup> and come;assemble, you fugitives from the nations.Ignorant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18582BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18582BN\"></sup> are those who carry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18582BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18582BO\"></sup> about idols of wood,who pray to gods that cannot save.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18582BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18582BP\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Declare what is to be, present it—let them take counsel together.Who foretold<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18583BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18583BQ\"></sup> this long ago,who declared it from the distant past?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18583BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18583BR\"></sup>Was it not I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?And there is no God apart from me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18583BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18583BS\"></sup>a righteous God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18583BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18583BT\"></sup> and a Savior;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18583BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18583BU\"></sup>there is none but me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Turn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18584BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18584BV\"></sup> to me and be saved,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18584BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18584BW\"></sup>all you ends of the earth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18584BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18584BX\"></sup>for I am God, and there is no other.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18584BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18584BY\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>By myself I have sworn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18585BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18585BZ\"></sup>my mouth has uttered in all integrity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18585CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18585CA\"></sup>a word that will not be revoked:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18585CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18585CB\"></sup>Before me every knee will bow;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18585CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18585CC\"></sup>by me every tongue will swear.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18585CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18585CD\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>They will say of me, ‘In the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> aloneare deliverance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18586CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18586CE\"></sup> and strength.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18586CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18586CF\"></sup>’”All who have raged against himwill come to him and be put to shame.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18586CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18586CG\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But all the descendants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18587CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18587CH\"></sup> of Israelwill find deliverance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18587CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18587CI\"></sup> in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and will make their boast in him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18587CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18587CJ\"></sup>"
		},
		"46": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">46 </span>Bel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18588A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18588A\"></sup> bows down, Nebo stoops low;their idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18588B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18588B\"></sup> are borne by beasts of burden.The images that are carried<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18588C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18588C\"></sup> about are burdensome,a burden for the weary.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>They stoop and bow down together;unable to rescue the burden,they themselves go off into captivity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18589D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18589D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18590E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18590E\"></sup> to me, you descendants of Jacob,all the remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18590F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18590F\"></sup> of the people of Israel,you whom I have upheld since your birth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18590G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18590G\"></sup>and have carried<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18590H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18590H\"></sup> since you were born.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18590I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18590I\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Even to your old age and gray hairs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18591J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18591J\"></sup>I am he,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18591K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18591K\"></sup> I am he who will sustain you.I have made you and I will carry you;I will sustain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18591L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18591L\"></sup> you and I will rescue you.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“With whom will you compare me or count me equal?To whom will you liken me that we may be compared?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18592M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18592M\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Some pour out gold from their bagsand weigh out silver on the scales;they hire a goldsmith<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18593N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18593N\"></sup> to make it into a god,and they bow down and worship it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18593O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18593O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They lift it to their shoulders and carry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18594P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18594P\"></sup> it;they set it up in its place, and there it stands.From that spot it cannot move.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18594Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18594Q\"></sup>Even though someone cries out to it, it cannot answer;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18594R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18594R\"></sup>it cannot save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18594S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18594S\"></sup> them from their troubles.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Remember<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18595T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18595T\"></sup> this, keep it in mind,take it to heart, you rebels.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18595U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18595U\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Remember the former things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18596V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18596V\"></sup> those of long ago;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18596W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18596W\"></sup>I am God, and there is no other;I am God, and there is none like me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18596X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18596X\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I make known the end from the beginning,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18597Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18597Y\"></sup>from ancient times,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18597Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18597Z\"></sup> what is still to come.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18597AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18597AA\"></sup>I say, ‘My purpose will stand,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18597AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18597AB\"></sup>and I will do all that I please.’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>From the east I summon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18598AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18598AC\"></sup> a bird of prey;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18598AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18598AD\"></sup>from a far-off land, a man to fulfill my purpose.What I have said, that I will bring about;what I have planned,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18598AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18598AE\"></sup> that I will do.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18598AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18598AF\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18599AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18599AG\"></sup> to me, you stubborn-hearted,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18599AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18599AH\"></sup>you who are now far from my righteousness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18599AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18599AI\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I am bringing my righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18600AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18600AJ\"></sup> near,it is not far away;and my salvation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18600AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18600AK\"></sup> will not be delayed.I will grant salvation to Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18600AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18600AL\"></sup>my splendor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18600AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18600AM\"></sup> to Israel."
		},
		"47": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">47 </span>“Go down, sit in the dust,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18601A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18601A\"></sup>Virgin Daughter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18601B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18601B\"></sup> Babylon;sit on the ground without a throne,queen city of the Babylonians.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18601C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18601C\"></sup>No more will you be calledtender or delicate.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18601D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18601D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Take millstones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18602E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18602E\"></sup> and grind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18602F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18602F\"></sup> flour;take off your veil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18602G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18602G\"></sup>Lift up your skirts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18602H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18602H\"></sup> bare your legs,and wade through the streams.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Your nakedness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18603I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18603I\"></sup> will be exposedand your shame<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18603J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18603J\"></sup> uncovered.I will take vengeance;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18603K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18603K\"></sup>I will spare no one.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18603L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18603L\"></sup>”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Our Redeemer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18604M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18604M\"></sup>—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18604N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18604N\"></sup> is his name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18604O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18604O\"></sup>—is the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18604P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18604P\"></sup> of Israel.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Sit in silence,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18605Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18605Q\"></sup> go into darkness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18605R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18605R\"></sup>queen city of the Babylonians;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18605S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18605S\"></sup>no more will you be calledqueen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18605T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18605T\"></sup> of kingdoms.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18605U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18605U\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I was angry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18606V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18606V\"></sup> with my peopleand desecrated my inheritance;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18606W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18606W\"></sup>I gave them into your hand,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18606X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18606X\"></sup>and you showed them no mercy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18606Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18606Y\"></sup>Even on the agedyou laid a very heavy yoke.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You said, ‘I am forever<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18607Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18607Z\"></sup>—the eternal queen!’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18607AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18607AA\"></sup>But you did not consider these thingsor reflect<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18607AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18607AB\"></sup> on what might happen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18607AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18607AC\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Now then, listen, you lover of pleasure,lounging in your security<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18608AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18608AD\"></sup>and saying to yourself,‘I am, and there is none besides me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18608AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18608AE\"></sup>I will never be a widow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18608AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18608AF\"></sup>or suffer the loss of children.’",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Both of these will overtake youin a moment,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18609AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18609AG\"></sup> on a single day:loss of children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18609AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18609AH\"></sup> and widowhood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18609AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18609AI\"></sup>They will come upon you in full measure,in spite of your many sorceries<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18609AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18609AJ\"></sup>and all your potent spells.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18609AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18609AK\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>You have trusted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18610AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18610AL\"></sup> in your wickednessand have said, ‘No one sees me.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18610AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18610AM\"></sup>Your wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18610AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18610AN\"></sup> and knowledge mislead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18610AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18610AO\"></sup> youwhen you say to yourself,‘I am, and there is none besides me.’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18611AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18611AP\"></sup> will come upon you,and you will not know how to conjure it away.A calamity will fall upon youthat you cannot ward off with a ransom;a catastrophe you cannot foreseewill suddenly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18611AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18611AQ\"></sup> come upon you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Keep on, then, with your magic spellsand with your many sorceries,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18612AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18612AR\"></sup>which you have labored at since childhood.Perhaps you will succeed,perhaps you will cause terror.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>All the counsel you have received has only worn you out!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18613AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18613AS\"></sup>Let your astrologers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18613AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18613AT\"></sup> come forward,those stargazers who make predictions month by month,let them save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18613AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18613AU\"></sup> you from what is coming upon you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Surely they are like stubble;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18614AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18614AV\"></sup>the fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18614AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18614AW\"></sup> will burn them up.They cannot even save themselvesfrom the power of the flame.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18614AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18614AX\"></sup>These are not coals for warmth;this is not a fire to sit by.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>That is all they are to you—these you have dealt withand labored<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18615AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18615AY\"></sup> with since childhood.All of them go on in their error;there is not one that can save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18615AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18615AZ\"></sup> you."
		},
		"48": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">48 </span>“Listen to this, you descendants of Jacob,you who are called by the name of Israel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18616A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18616A\"></sup>and come from the line of Judah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18616B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18616B\"></sup>you who take oaths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18616C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18616C\"></sup> in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18616D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18616D\"></sup>and invoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18616E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18616E\"></sup> the God of Israel—but not in truth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18616F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18616F\"></sup> or righteousness—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>you who call yourselves citizens of the holy city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18617G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18617G\"></sup>and claim to rely<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18617H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18617H\"></sup> on the God of Israel—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty is his name:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18617I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18617I\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I foretold the former things<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18618J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18618J\"></sup> long ago,my mouth announced<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18618K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18618K\"></sup> them and I made them known;then suddenly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18618L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18618L\"></sup> I acted, and they came to pass.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For I knew how stubborn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18619M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18619M\"></sup> you were;your neck muscles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18619N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18619N\"></sup> were iron,your forehead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18619O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18619O\"></sup> was bronze.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Therefore I told you these things long ago;before they happened I announced<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18620P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18620P\"></sup> them to youso that you could not say,‘My images brought them about;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18620Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18620Q\"></sup>my wooden image and metal god ordained them.’",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>You have heard these things; look at them all.Will you not admit them?“From now on I will tell you of new things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18621R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18621R\"></sup>of hidden things unknown to you.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They are created<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18622S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18622S\"></sup> now, and not long ago;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18622T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18622T\"></sup>you have not heard of them before today.So you cannot say,‘Yes, I knew<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18622U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18622U\"></sup> of them.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>You have neither heard nor understood;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18623V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18623V\"></sup>from of old your ears<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18623W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18623W\"></sup> have not been open.Well do I know how treacherous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18623X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18623X\"></sup> you are;you were called a rebel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18623Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18623Y\"></sup> from birth.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For my own name’s sake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18624Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18624Z\"></sup> I delay my wrath;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18624AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18624AA\"></sup>for the sake of my praise I hold it back from you,so as not to destroy you completely.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18624AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18624AB\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>See, I have refined<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18625AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18625AC\"></sup> you, though not as silver;I have tested<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18625AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18625AD\"></sup> you in the furnace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18625AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18625AE\"></sup> of affliction.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For my own sake,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18626AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18626AF\"></sup> for my own sake, I do this.How can I let myself be defamed?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18626AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18626AG\"></sup>I will not yield my glory to another.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18626AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18626AH\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18627AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18627AI\"></sup> to me, Jacob,Israel, whom I have called:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18627AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18627AJ\"></sup>I am he;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18627AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18627AK\"></sup>I am the first and I am the last.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18627AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18627AL\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>My own hand laid the foundations of the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18628AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18628AM\"></sup>and my right hand spread out the heavens;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18628AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18628AN\"></sup>when I summon them,they all stand up together.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18628AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18628AO\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Come together,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18629AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18629AP\"></sup> all of you, and listen:Which of the idols has foretold<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18629AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18629AQ\"></sup> these things?The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s chosen ally<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18629AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18629AR\"></sup>will carry out his purpose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18629AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18629AS\"></sup> against Babylon;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18629AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18629AT\"></sup>his arm will be against the Babylonians.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I, even I, have spoken;yes, I have called<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18630AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18630AU\"></sup> him.I will bring him,and he will succeed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18630AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18630AV\"></sup> in his mission.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Come near<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18631AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18631AW\"></sup> me and listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18631AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18631AX\"></sup> to this:“From the first announcement I have not spoken in secret;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18631AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18631AY\"></sup>at the time it happens, I am there.”And now the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18631AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18631AZ\"></sup> has sent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18631BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18631BA\"></sup> me,endowed with his Spirit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18631BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18631BB\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says—your Redeemer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18632BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18632BC\"></sup> the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18632BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18632BD\"></sup> of Israel:“I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,who teaches<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18632BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18632BE\"></sup> you what is best for you,who directs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18632BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18632BF\"></sup> you in the way<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18632BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18632BG\"></sup> you should go.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>If only you had paid attention<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18633BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18633BH\"></sup> to my commands,your peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18633BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18633BI\"></sup> would have been like a river,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18633BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18633BJ\"></sup>your well-being<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18633BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18633BK\"></sup> like the waves of the sea.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Your descendants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18634BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18634BL\"></sup> would have been like the sand,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18634BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18634BM\"></sup>your children like its numberless grains;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18634BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18634BN\"></sup>their name would never be blotted out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18634BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18634BO\"></sup>nor destroyed from before me.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Leave Babylon,flee<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18635BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18635BP\"></sup> from the Babylonians!Announce this with shouts of joy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18635BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18635BQ\"></sup>and proclaim it.Send it out to the ends of the earth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18635BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18635BR\"></sup>say, “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has redeemed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18635BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18635BS\"></sup> his servant Jacob.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>They did not thirst<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18636BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18636BT\"></sup> when he led them through the deserts;he made water flow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18636BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18636BU\"></sup> for them from the rock;he split the rockand water gushed out.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18636BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18636BV\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“There is no peace,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18637BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18637BW\"></sup> says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “for the wicked.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18637BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18637BX\"></sup>"
		},
		"49": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">49 </span>Listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18638A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18638A\"></sup> to me, you islands;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18638B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18638B\"></sup>hear this, you distant nations:Before I was born<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18638C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18638C\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> called<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18638D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18638D\"></sup> me;from my mother’s womb he has spoken my name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18638E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18638E\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He made my mouth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18639F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18639F\"></sup> like a sharpened sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18639G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18639G\"></sup>in the shadow of his hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18639H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18639H\"></sup> he hid me;he made me into a polished arrow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18639I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18639I\"></sup>and concealed me in his quiver.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He said to me, “You are my servant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18640J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18640J\"></sup>Israel, in whom I will display my splendor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18640K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18640K\"></sup>”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But I said, “I have labored in vain;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18641L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18641L\"></sup>I have spent my strength for nothing at all.Yet what is due me is in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s hand,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18641M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18641M\"></sup>and my reward<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18641N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18641N\"></sup> is with my God.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18641O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18641O\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And now the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says—he who formed me in the womb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18642P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18642P\"></sup> to be his servantto bring Jacob back to himand gather Israel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18642Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18642Q\"></sup> to himself,for I am honored<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18642R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18642R\"></sup> in the eyes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and my God has been my strength<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18642S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18642S\"></sup>—",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>he says:“It is too small a thing for you to be my servant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18643T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18643T\"></sup>to restore the tribes of Jacoband bring back those of Israel I have kept.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18643U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18643U\"></sup>I will also make you a light<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18643V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18643V\"></sup> for the Gentiles,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18643W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18643W\"></sup>that my salvation may reach to the ends of the earth.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18643X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18643X\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says—the Redeemer and Holy One of Israel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18644Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18644Y\"></sup>—to him who was despised<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18644Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18644Z\"></sup> and abhorred by the nation,to the servant of rulers:“Kings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18644AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18644AA\"></sup> will see you and stand up,princes will see and bow down,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18644AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18644AB\"></sup>because of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, who is faithful,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18644AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18644AC\"></sup>the Holy One of Israel, who has chosen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18644AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18644AD\"></sup> you.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“In the time of my favor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18645AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18645AE\"></sup> I will answer you,and in the day of salvation I will help you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18645AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18645AF\"></sup>I will keep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18645AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18645AG\"></sup> you and will make youto be a covenant for the people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18645AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18645AH\"></sup>to restore the land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18645AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18645AI\"></sup>and to reassign its desolate inheritances,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18645AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18645AJ\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>to say to the captives,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18646AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18646AK\"></sup> ‘Come out,’and to those in darkness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18646AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18646AL\"></sup> ‘Be free!’“They will feed beside the roadsand find pasture on every barren hill.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18646AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18646AM\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They will neither hunger nor thirst,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18647AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18647AN\"></sup>nor will the desert heat or the sun beat down on them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18647AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18647AO\"></sup>He who has compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18647AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18647AP\"></sup> on them will guide<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18647AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18647AQ\"></sup> themand lead them beside springs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18647AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18647AR\"></sup> of water.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I will turn all my mountains into roads,and my highways<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18648AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18648AS\"></sup> will be raised up.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18648AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18648AT\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>See, they will come from afar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18649AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18649AU\"></sup>—some from the north, some from the west,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18649AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18649AV\"></sup>some from the region of Aswan.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Shout for joy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18650AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18650AW\"></sup> you heavens;rejoice, you earth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18650AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18650AX\"></sup>burst into song, you mountains!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18650AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18650AY\"></sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> comforts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18650AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18650AZ\"></sup> his peopleand will have compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18650BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18650BA\"></sup> on his afflicted ones.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18650BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18650BB\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But Zion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18651BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18651BC\"></sup> said, “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has forsaken<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18651BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18651BD\"></sup> me,the Lord has forgotten me.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Can a mother forget the baby at her breastand have no compassion on the child<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18652BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18652BE\"></sup> she has borne?Though she may forget,I will not forget you!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18652BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18652BF\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>See, I have engraved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18653BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18653BG\"></sup> you on the palms of my hands;your walls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18653BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18653BH\"></sup> are ever before me.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Your children hasten back,and those who laid you waste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18654BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18654BI\"></sup> depart from you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Lift up your eyes and look around;all your children gather<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18655BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18655BJ\"></sup> and come to you.As surely as I live,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18655BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18655BK\"></sup>” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“you will wear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18655BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18655BL\"></sup> them all as ornaments;you will put them on, like a bride.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Though you were ruined and made desolate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18656BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18656BM\"></sup>and your land laid waste,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18656BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18656BN\"></sup>now you will be too small for your people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18656BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18656BO\"></sup>and those who devoured<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18656BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18656BP\"></sup> you will be far away.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The children born during your bereavementwill yet say in your hearing,‘This place is too small for us;give us more space to live in.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18657BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18657BQ\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then you will say in your heart,‘Who bore me these?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18658BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18658BR\"></sup>I was bereaved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18658BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18658BS\"></sup> and barren;I was exiled and rejected.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18658BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18658BT\"></sup>Who brought these<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18658BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18658BU\"></sup> up?I was left<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18658BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18658BV\"></sup> all alone,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18658BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18658BW\"></sup>but these—where have they come from?’”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>This is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18659BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18659BX\"></sup> says:“See, I will beckon to the nations,I will lift up my banner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18659BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18659BY\"></sup> to the peoples;they will bring<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18659BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18659BZ\"></sup> your sons in their armsand carry your daughters on their hips.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18659CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18659CA\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Kings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18660CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18660CB\"></sup> will be your foster fathers,and their queens your nursing mothers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18660CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18660CC\"></sup>They will bow down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18660CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18660CD\"></sup> before you with their faces to the ground;they will lick the dust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18660CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18660CE\"></sup> at your feet.Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18660CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18660CF\"></sup>those who hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18660CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18660CG\"></sup> in me will not be disappointed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18660CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18660CH\"></sup>”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Can plunder be taken from warriors,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18661CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18661CI\"></sup>or captives be rescued from the fierce?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“Yes, captives<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18662CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18662CJ\"></sup> will be taken from warriors,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18662CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18662CK\"></sup>and plunder retrieved from the fierce;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18662CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18662CL\"></sup>I will contend with those who contend with you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18662CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18662CM\"></sup>and your children I will save.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18662CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18662CN\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I will make your oppressors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18663CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18663CO\"></sup> eat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18663CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18663CP\"></sup> their own flesh;they will be drunk on their own blood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18663CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18663CQ\"></sup> as with wine.Then all mankind will know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18663CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18663CR\"></sup>that I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, am your Savior,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18663CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18663CS\"></sup>your Redeemer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18663CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18663CT\"></sup> the Mighty One of Jacob.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18663CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18663CU\"></sup>”"
		},
		"50": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">50 </span>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“Where is your mother’s certificate of divorce<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18664A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18664A\"></sup>with which I sent her away?Or to which of my creditorsdid I sell<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18664B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18664B\"></sup> you?Because of your sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18664C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18664C\"></sup> you were sold;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18664D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18664D\"></sup>because of your transgressions your mother was sent away.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When I came, why was there no one?When I called, why was there no one to answer?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18665E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18665E\"></sup>Was my arm too short<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18665F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18665F\"></sup> to deliver you?Do I lack the strength<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18665G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18665G\"></sup> to rescue you?By a mere rebuke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18665H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18665H\"></sup> I dry up the sea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18665I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18665I\"></sup>I turn rivers into a desert;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18665J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18665J\"></sup>their fish rot for lack of waterand die of thirst.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I clothe the heavens with darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18666K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18666K\"></sup>and make sackcloth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18666L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18666L\"></sup> its covering.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18667M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18667M\"></sup> has given me a well-instructed tongue,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18667N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18667N\"></sup>to know the word that sustains the weary.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18667O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18667O\"></sup>He wakens me morning by morning,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18667P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18667P\"></sup>wakens my ear to listen like one being instructed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18667Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18667Q\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18668R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18668R\"></sup> has opened my ears;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18668S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18668S\"></sup>I have not been rebellious,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18668T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18668T\"></sup>I have not turned away.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I offered my back to those who beat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18669U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18669U\"></sup> me,my cheeks to those who pulled out my beard;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18669V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18669V\"></sup>I did not hide my facefrom mocking and spitting.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18669W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18669W\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Because the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18670X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18670X\"></sup> helps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18670Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18670Y\"></sup> me,I will not be disgraced.Therefore have I set my face like flint,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18670Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18670Z\"></sup>and I know I will not be put to shame.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18670AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18670AA\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He who vindicates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18671AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18671AB\"></sup> me is near.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18671AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18671AC\"></sup>Who then will bring charges against me?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18671AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18671AD\"></sup>Let us face each other!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18671AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18671AE\"></sup>Who is my accuser?Let him confront me!",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>It is the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18672AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18672AF\"></sup> who helps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18672AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18672AG\"></sup> me.Who will condemn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18672AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18672AH\"></sup> me?They will all wear out like a garment;the moths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18672AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18672AI\"></sup> will eat them up.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Who among you fears<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18673AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18673AJ\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and obeys<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18673AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18673AK\"></sup> the word of his servant?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18673AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18673AL\"></sup>Let the one who walks in the dark,who has no light,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18673AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18673AM\"></sup>trust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18673AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18673AN\"></sup> in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and rely on their God.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But now, all you who light firesand provide yourselves with flaming torches,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18674AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18674AO\"></sup>go, walk in the light of your fires<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18674AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18674AP\"></sup>and of the torches you have set ablaze.This is what you shall receive from my hand:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18674AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18674AQ\"></sup>You will lie down in torment.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18674AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18674AR\"></sup>"
		},
		"51": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">51 </span>“Listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18675A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18675A\"></sup> to me, you who pursue righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18675B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18675B\"></sup>and who seek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18675C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18675C\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:Look to the rock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18675D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18675D\"></sup> from which you were cutand to the quarry from which you were hewn;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>look to Abraham,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18676E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18676E\"></sup> your father,and to Sarah, who gave you birth.When I called him he was only one man,and I blessed him and made him many.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18676F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18676F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will surely comfort<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18677G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18677G\"></sup> Zion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18677H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18677H\"></sup>and will look with compassion on all her ruins;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18677I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18677I\"></sup>he will make her deserts like Eden,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18677J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18677J\"></sup>her wastelands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18677K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18677K\"></sup> like the garden of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.Joy and gladness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18677L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18677L\"></sup> will be found in her,thanksgiving<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18677M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18677M\"></sup> and the sound of singing.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Listen to me, my people;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18678N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18678N\"></sup>hear me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18678O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18678O\"></sup> my nation:Instruction<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18678P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18678P\"></sup> will go out from me;my justice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18678Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18678Q\"></sup> will become a light to the nations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18678R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18678R\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>My righteousness draws near speedily,my salvation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18679S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18679S\"></sup> is on the way,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18679T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18679T\"></sup>and my arm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18679U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18679U\"></sup> will bring justice to the nations.The islands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18679V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18679V\"></sup> will look to meand wait in hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18679W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18679W\"></sup> for my arm.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Lift up your eyes to the heavens,look at the earth beneath;the heavens will vanish like smoke,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18680X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18680X\"></sup>the earth will wear out like a garment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18680Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18680Y\"></sup>and its inhabitants die like flies.But my salvation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18680Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18680Z\"></sup> will last forever,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18680AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18680AA\"></sup>my righteousness will never fail.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18680AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18680AB\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Hear me, you who know what is right,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18681AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18681AC\"></sup>you people who have taken my instruction to heart:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18681AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18681AD\"></sup>Do not fear the reproach of mere mortalsor be terrified by their insults.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18681AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18681AE\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For the moth will eat them up like a garment;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18682AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18682AF\"></sup>the worm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18682AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18682AG\"></sup> will devour them like wool.But my righteousness will last forever,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18682AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18682AH\"></sup>my salvation through all generations.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Awake, awake,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18683AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18683AI\"></sup> arm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18683AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18683AJ\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,clothe yourself with strength!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18683AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18683AK\"></sup>Awake, as in days gone by,as in generations of old.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18683AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18683AL\"></sup>Was it not you who cut Rahab<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18683AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18683AM\"></sup> to pieces,who pierced that monster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18683AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18683AN\"></sup> through?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Was it not you who dried up the sea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18684AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18684AO\"></sup>the waters of the great deep,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18684AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18684AP\"></sup>who made a road in the depths of the sea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18684AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18684AQ\"></sup>so that the redeemed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18684AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18684AR\"></sup> might cross over?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Those the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has rescued<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18685AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18685AS\"></sup> will return.They will enter Zion with singing;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18685AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18685AT\"></sup>everlasting joy will crown their heads.Gladness and joy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18685AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18685AU\"></sup> will overtake them,and sorrow and sighing will flee away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18685AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18685AV\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I, even I, am he who comforts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18686AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18686AW\"></sup> you.Who are you that you fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18686AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18686AX\"></sup> mere mortals,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18686AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18686AY\"></sup>human beings who are but grass,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18686AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18686AZ\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>that you forget<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18687BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18687BA\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your Maker,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18687BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18687BB\"></sup>who stretches out the heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18687BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18687BC\"></sup>and who lays the foundations of the earth,that you live in constant terror<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18687BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18687BD\"></sup> every daybecause of the wrath of the oppressor,who is bent on destruction?For where is the wrath of the oppressor?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18687BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18687BE\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>The cowering prisoners will soon be set free;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18688BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18688BF\"></sup>they will not die in their dungeon,nor will they lack bread.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18688BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18688BG\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,who stirs up the sea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18689BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18689BH\"></sup> so that its waves roar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18689BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18689BI\"></sup>—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18689BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18689BJ\"></sup> is his name.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I have put my words in your mouth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18690BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18690BK\"></sup>and covered you with the shadow of my hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18690BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18690BL\"></sup>—I who set the heavens in place,who laid the foundations of the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18690BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18690BM\"></sup>and who say to Zion, ‘You are my people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18690BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18690BN\"></sup>’”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Awake, awake!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18691BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18691BO\"></sup>Rise up, Jerusalem,you who have drunk from the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>the cup<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18691BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18691BP\"></sup> of his wrath,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18691BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18691BQ\"></sup>you who have drained to its dregs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18691BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18691BR\"></sup>the goblet that makes people stagger.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18691BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18691BS\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Among all the children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18692BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18692BT\"></sup> she borethere was none to guide her;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18692BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18692BU\"></sup>among all the children she rearedthere was none to take her by the hand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18692BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18692BV\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>These double calamities<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18693BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18693BW\"></sup> have come upon you—who can comfort you?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18693BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18693BX\"></sup>—ruin and destruction,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18693BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18693BY\"></sup> famine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18693BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18693BZ\"></sup> and sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18693CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18693CA\"></sup>—who can console you?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Your children have fainted;they lie at every street corner,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18694CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18694CB\"></sup>like antelope caught in a net.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18694CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18694CC\"></sup>They are filled with the wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18694CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18694CD\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,with the rebuke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18694CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18694CE\"></sup> of your God.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Therefore hear this, you afflicted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18695CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18695CF\"></sup> one,made drunk,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18695CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18695CG\"></sup> but not with wine.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>This is what your Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says,your God, who defends<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18696CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18696CH\"></sup> his people:“See, I have taken out of your handthe cup<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18696CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18696CI\"></sup> that made you stagger;from that cup, the goblet of my wrath,you will never drink again.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I will put it into the hands of your tormentors,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18697CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18697CJ\"></sup>who said to you,‘Fall prostrate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18697CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18697CK\"></sup> that we may walk<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18697CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18697CL\"></sup> on you.’And you made your back like the ground,like a street to be walked on.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18697CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18697CM\"></sup>"
		},
		"52": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">52 </span>Awake, awake,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18698A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18698A\"></sup> Zion,clothe yourself with strength!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18698B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18698B\"></sup>Put on your garments of splendor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18698C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18698C\"></sup>Jerusalem, the holy city.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18698D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18698D\"></sup>The uncircumcised<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18698E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18698E\"></sup> and defiled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18698F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18698F\"></sup>will not enter you again.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18698G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18698G\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Shake off your dust;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18699H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18699H\"></sup>rise up,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18699I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18699I\"></sup> sit enthroned, Jerusalem.Free yourself from the chains on your neck,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18699J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18699J\"></sup>Daughter Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18699K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18699K\"></sup> now a captive.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“You were sold for nothing,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18700L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18700L\"></sup>and without money<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18700M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18700M\"></sup> you will be redeemed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18700N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18700N\"></sup>”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“At first my people went down to Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18701O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18701O\"></sup> to live;lately, Assyria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18701P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18701P\"></sup> has oppressed them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“And now what do I have here?” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“For my people have been taken away for nothing,and those who rule them mock,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“And all day longmy name is constantly blasphemed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18702Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18702Q\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore my people will know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18703R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18703R\"></sup> my name;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18703S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18703S\"></sup>therefore in that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18703T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18703T\"></sup> they will knowthat it is I who foretold<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18703U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18703U\"></sup> it.Yes, it is I.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>How beautiful on the mountains<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18704V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18704V\"></sup>are the feet of those who bring good news,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18704W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18704W\"></sup>who proclaim peace,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18704X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18704X\"></sup>who bring good tidings,who proclaim salvation,who say to Zion,“Your God reigns!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18704Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18704Y\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Listen! Your watchmen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18705Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18705Z\"></sup> lift up their voices;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18705AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18705AA\"></sup>together they shout for joy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18705AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18705AB\"></sup>When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> returns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18705AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18705AC\"></sup> to Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18705AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18705AD\"></sup>they will see it with their own eyes.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Burst into songs of joy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18706AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18706AE\"></sup> together,you ruins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18706AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18706AF\"></sup> of Jerusalem,for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has comforted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18706AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18706AG\"></sup> his people,he has redeemed Jerusalem.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18706AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18706AH\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will lay bare his holy arm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18707AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18707AI\"></sup>in the sight of all the nations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18707AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18707AJ\"></sup>and all the ends of the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18707AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18707AK\"></sup> will seethe salvation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18707AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18707AL\"></sup> of our God.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Depart,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18708AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18708AM\"></sup> depart, go out from there!Touch no unclean thing!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18708AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18708AN\"></sup>Come out from it and be pure,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18708AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18708AO\"></sup>you who carry the articles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18708AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18708AP\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s house.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But you will not leave in haste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18709AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18709AQ\"></sup>or go in flight;for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will go before you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18709AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18709AR\"></sup>the God of Israel will be your rear guard.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18709AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18709AS\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>See, my servant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18710AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18710AT\"></sup> will act wisely;he will be raised and lifted up and highly exalted.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18710AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18710AU\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Just as there were many who were appalled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18711AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18711AV\"></sup> at him—his appearance was so disfigured<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18711AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18711AW\"></sup> beyond that of any human beingand his form marred beyond human likeness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18711AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18711AX\"></sup>—",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>so he will sprinkle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18712AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18712AY\"></sup> many nations,and kings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18712AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18712AZ\"></sup> will shut their mouths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18712BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18712BA\"></sup> because of him.For what they were not told, they will see,and what they have not heard, they will understand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18712BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18712BB\"></sup>"
		},
		"53": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">53 </span>Who has believed our message<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18713A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18713A\"></sup>and to whom has the arm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18713B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18713B\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> been revealed?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18713C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18713C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He grew up before him like a tender shoot,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18714D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18714D\"></sup>and like a root<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18714E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18714E\"></sup> out of dry ground.He had no beauty or majesty to attract us to him,nothing in his appearance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18714F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18714F\"></sup> that we should desire him.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He was despised and rejected by mankind,a man of suffering,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18715G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18715G\"></sup> and familiar with pain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18715H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18715H\"></sup>Like one from whom people hide<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18715I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18715I\"></sup> their faceshe was despised,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18715J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18715J\"></sup> and we held him in low esteem.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Surely he took up our painand bore our suffering,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18716K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18716K\"></sup>yet we considered him punished by God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18716L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18716L\"></sup>stricken by him, and afflicted.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18716M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18716M\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But he was pierced<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18717N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18717N\"></sup> for our transgressions,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18717O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18717O\"></sup>he was crushed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18717P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18717P\"></sup> for our iniquities;the punishment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18717Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18717Q\"></sup> that brought us peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18717R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18717R\"></sup> was on him,and by his wounds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18717S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18717S\"></sup> we are healed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18717T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18717T\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>We all, like sheep, have gone astray,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18718U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18718U\"></sup>each of us has turned to our own way;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18718V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18718V\"></sup>and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has laid on himthe iniquity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18718W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18718W\"></sup> of us all.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He was oppressed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18719X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18719X\"></sup> and afflicted,yet he did not open his mouth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18719Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18719Y\"></sup>he was led like a lamb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18719Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18719Z\"></sup> to the slaughter,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18719AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18719AA\"></sup>and as a sheep before its shearers is silent,so he did not open his mouth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>By oppression and judgment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18720AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18720AB\"></sup> he was taken away.Yet who of his generation protested?For he was cut off from the land of the living;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18720AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18720AC\"></sup>for the transgression<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18720AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18720AD\"></sup> of my people he was punished.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He was assigned a grave with the wicked,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18721AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18721AE\"></sup>and with the rich<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18721AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18721AF\"></sup> in his death,though he had done no violence,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18721AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18721AG\"></sup>nor was any deceit in his mouth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18721AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18721AH\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Yet it was the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s will<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18722AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18722AI\"></sup> to crush<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18722AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18722AJ\"></sup> him and cause him to suffer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18722AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18722AK\"></sup>and though the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> makes his life an offering for sin,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18722AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18722AL\"></sup>he will see his offspring<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18722AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18722AM\"></sup> and prolong his days,and the will of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will prosper<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18722AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18722AN\"></sup> in his hand.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>After he has suffered,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18723AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18723AO\"></sup>he will see the light<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18723AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18723AP\"></sup> of life and be satisfied;by his knowledge my righteous servant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18723AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18723AQ\"></sup> will justify<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18723AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18723AR\"></sup> many,and he will bear their iniquities.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18723AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18723AS\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore I will give him a portion among the great,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18724AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18724AT\"></sup>and he will divide the spoils<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18724AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18724AU\"></sup> with the strong,because he poured out his life unto death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18724AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18724AV\"></sup>and was numbered with the transgressors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18724AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18724AW\"></sup>For he bore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18724AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18724AX\"></sup> the sin of many,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18724AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18724AY\"></sup>and made intercession<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18724AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18724AZ\"></sup> for the transgressors."
		},
		"54": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">54 </span>“Sing, barren woman,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18725A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18725A\"></sup>you who never bore a child;burst into song, shout for joy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18725B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18725B\"></sup>you who were never in labor;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18725C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18725C\"></sup>because more are the children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18725D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18725D\"></sup> of the desolate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18725E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18725E\"></sup> womanthan of her who has a husband,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18725F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18725F\"></sup>”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Enlarge the place of your tent,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18726G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18726G\"></sup>stretch your tent curtains wide,do not hold back;lengthen your cords,strengthen your stakes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18726H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18726H\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For you will spread out to the right and to the left;your descendants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18727I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18727I\"></sup> will dispossess nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18727J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18727J\"></sup>and settle in their desolate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18727K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18727K\"></sup> cities.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Do not be afraid;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18728L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18728L\"></sup> you will not be put to shame.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18728M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18728M\"></sup>Do not fear disgrace;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18728N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18728N\"></sup> you will not be humiliated.You will forget the shame of your youth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18728O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18728O\"></sup>and remember no more the reproach<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18728P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18728P\"></sup> of your widowhood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18728Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18728Q\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For your Maker<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18729R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18729R\"></sup> is your husband<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18729S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18729S\"></sup>—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty is his name—the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18729T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18729T\"></sup> of Israel is your Redeemer;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18729U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18729U\"></sup>he is called the God of all the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18729V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18729V\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will call you back<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18730W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18730W\"></sup>as if you were a wife deserted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18730X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18730X\"></sup> and distressed in spirit—a wife who married young,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18730Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18730Y\"></sup>only to be rejected,” says your God.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“For a brief moment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18731Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18731Z\"></sup> I abandoned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18731AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18731AA\"></sup> you,but with deep compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18731AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18731AB\"></sup> I will bring you back.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18731AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18731AC\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>In a surge of anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18732AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18732AD\"></sup>I hid<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18732AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18732AE\"></sup> my face from you for a moment,but with everlasting kindness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18732AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18732AF\"></sup>I will have compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18732AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18732AG\"></sup> on you,”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your Redeemer.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18732AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18732AH\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“To me this is like the days of Noah,when I swore that the waters of Noah would never again cover the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18733AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18733AI\"></sup>So now I have sworn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18733AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18733AJ\"></sup> not to be angry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18733AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18733AK\"></sup> with you,never to rebuke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18733AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18733AL\"></sup> you again.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Though the mountains be shaken<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18734AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18734AM\"></sup>and the hills be removed,yet my unfailing love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18734AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18734AN\"></sup> for you will not be shaken<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18734AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18734AO\"></sup>nor my covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18734AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18734AP\"></sup> of peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18734AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18734AQ\"></sup> be removed,”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, who has compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18734AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18734AR\"></sup> on you.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Afflicted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18735AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18735AS\"></sup> city, lashed by storms<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18735AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18735AT\"></sup> and not comforted,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18735AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18735AU\"></sup>I will rebuild you with stones of turquoise,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18735AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18735AV\"></sup>your foundations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18735AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18735AW\"></sup> with lapis lazuli.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18735AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18735AX\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will make your battlements of rubies,your gates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18736AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18736AY\"></sup> of sparkling jewels,and all your walls of precious stones.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>All your children will be taught by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18737AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18737AZ\"></sup>and great will be their peace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18737BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18737BA\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>In righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18738BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18738BB\"></sup> you will be established:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18738BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18738BC\"></sup>Tyranny<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18738BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18738BD\"></sup> will be far from you;you will have nothing to fear.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18738BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18738BE\"></sup>Terror<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18738BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18738BF\"></sup> will be far removed;it will not come near you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>If anyone does attack you, it will not be my doing;whoever attacks you will surrender<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18739BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18739BG\"></sup> to you.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“See, it is I who created the blacksmith<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18740BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18740BH\"></sup>who fans the coals into flameand forges a weapon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18740BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18740BI\"></sup> fit for its work.And it is I who have created the destroyer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18740BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18740BJ\"></sup> to wreak havoc;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>no weapon forged against you will prevail,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18741BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18741BK\"></sup>and you will refute<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18741BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18741BL\"></sup> every tongue that accuses you.This is the heritage of the servants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18741BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18741BM\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and this is their vindication<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18741BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18741BN\"></sup> from me,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"55": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">55 </span>“Come, all you who are thirsty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18742A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18742A\"></sup>come to the waters;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18742B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18742B\"></sup>and you who have no money,come, buy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18742C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18742C\"></sup> and eat!Come, buy wine and milk<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18742D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18742D\"></sup>without money and without cost.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18742E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18742E\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Why spend money on what is not bread,and your labor on what does not satisfy?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18743F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18743F\"></sup>Listen, listen to me, and eat what is good,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18743G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18743G\"></sup>and you will delight in the richest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18743H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18743H\"></sup> of fare.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Give ear and come to me;listen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18744I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18744I\"></sup> that you may live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18744J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18744J\"></sup>I will make an everlasting covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18744K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18744K\"></sup> with you,my faithful love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18744L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18744L\"></sup> promised to David.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18744M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18744M\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>See, I have made him a witness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18745N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18745N\"></sup> to the peoples,a ruler and commander<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18745O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18745O\"></sup> of the peoples.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Surely you will summon nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18746P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18746P\"></sup> you know not,and nations you do not know will come running to you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18746Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18746Q\"></sup>because of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18746R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18746R\"></sup> of Israel,for he has endowed you with splendor.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18746S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18746S\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Seek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18747T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18747T\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> while he may be found;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18747U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18747U\"></sup>call<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18747V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18747V\"></sup> on him while he is near.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Let the wicked forsake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18748W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18748W\"></sup> their waysand the unrighteous their thoughts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18748X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18748X\"></sup>Let them turn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18748Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18748Y\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and he will have mercy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18748Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18748Z\"></sup> on them,and to our God, for he will freely pardon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18748AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18748AA\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“For my thoughts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18749AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18749AB\"></sup> are not your thoughts,neither are your ways my ways,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18749AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18749AC\"></sup>declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“As the heavens are higher than the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18750AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18750AD\"></sup>so are my ways higher than your waysand my thoughts than your thoughts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18750AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18750AE\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>As the rain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18751AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18751AF\"></sup> and the snowcome down from heaven,and do not return to itwithout watering the earthand making it bud and flourish,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18751AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18751AG\"></sup>so that it yields seed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18751AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18751AH\"></sup> for the sower and bread for the eater,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18751AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18751AI\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>so is my word<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18752AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18752AJ\"></sup> that goes out from my mouth:It will not return to me empty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18752AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18752AK\"></sup>but will accomplish what I desireand achieve the purpose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18752AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18752AL\"></sup> for which I sent it.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>You will go out in joy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18753AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18753AM\"></sup>and be led forth in peace;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18753AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18753AN\"></sup>the mountains and hillswill burst into song<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18753AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18753AO\"></sup> before you,and all the trees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18753AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18753AP\"></sup> of the fieldwill clap their hands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18753AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18753AQ\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Instead of the thornbush will grow the juniper,and instead of briers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18754AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18754AR\"></sup> the myrtle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18754AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18754AS\"></sup> will grow.This will be for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s renown,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18754AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18754AT\"></sup>for an everlasting sign,that will endure forever.”"
		},
		"56": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">56 </span>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“Maintain justice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18755A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18755A\"></sup>and do what is right,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18755B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18755B\"></sup>for my salvation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18755C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18755C\"></sup> is close at handand my righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18755D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18755D\"></sup> will soon be revealed.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Blessed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18756E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18756E\"></sup> is the one who does this—the person who holds it fast,who keeps the Sabbath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18756F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18756F\"></sup> without desecrating it,and keeps their hands from doing any evil.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Let no foreigner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18757G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18757G\"></sup> who is bound to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> say,“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will surely exclude me from his people.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18757H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18757H\"></sup>And let no eunuch<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18757I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18757I\"></sup> complain,“I am only a dry tree.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“To the eunuchs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18758J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18758J\"></sup> who keep my Sabbaths,who choose what pleases meand hold fast to my covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18758K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18758K\"></sup>—",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>to them I will give within my temple and its walls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18759L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18759L\"></sup>a memorial<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18759M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18759M\"></sup> and a namebetter than sons and daughters;I will give them an everlasting name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18759N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18759N\"></sup>that will endure forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18759O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18759O\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And foreigners<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18760P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18760P\"></sup> who bind themselves to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>to minister<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18760Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18760Q\"></sup> to him,to love the name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18760R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18760R\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and to be his servants,all who keep the Sabbath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18760S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18760S\"></sup> without desecrating itand who hold fast to my covenant—",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>these I will bring to my holy mountain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18761T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18761T\"></sup>and give them joy in my house of prayer.Their burnt offerings and sacrifices<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18761U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18761U\"></sup>will be accepted on my altar;for my house will be calleda house of prayer for all nations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18761V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18761V\"></sup>”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18761W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18761W\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> declares—he who gathers the exiles of Israel:“I will gather<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18762X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18762X\"></sup> still others to thembesides those already gathered.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Come, all you beasts of the field,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18763Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18763Y\"></sup>come and devour, all you beasts of the forest!",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Israel’s watchmen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18764Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18764Z\"></sup> are blind,they all lack knowledge;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18764AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18764AA\"></sup>they are all mute dogs,they cannot bark;they lie around and dream,they love to sleep.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18764AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18764AB\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They are dogs with mighty appetites;they never have enough.They are shepherds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18765AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18765AC\"></sup> who lack understanding;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18765AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18765AD\"></sup>they all turn to their own way,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18765AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18765AE\"></sup>they seek their own gain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18765AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18765AF\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Come,” each one cries, “let me get wine!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18766AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18766AG\"></sup>Let us drink our fill of beer!And tomorrow will be like today,or even far better.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18766AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18766AH\"></sup>"
		},
		"57": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">57 </span>The righteous perish,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18767A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18767A\"></sup>and no one takes it to heart;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18767B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18767B\"></sup>the devout are taken away,and no one understandsthat the righteous are taken awayto be spared from evil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18767C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18767C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Those who walk uprightly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18768D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18768D\"></sup>enter into peace;they find rest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18768E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18768E\"></sup> as they lie in death.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“But you—come here, you children of a sorceress,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18769F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18769F\"></sup>you offspring of adulterers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18769G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18769G\"></sup> and prostitutes!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18769H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18769H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Who are you mocking?At whom do you sneerand stick out your tongue?Are you not a brood of rebels,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18770I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18770I\"></sup>the offspring of liars?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You burn with lust among the oaks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18771J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18771J\"></sup>and under every spreading tree;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18771K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18771K\"></sup>you sacrifice your children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18771L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18771L\"></sup> in the ravinesand under the overhanging crags.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18772M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18772M\"></sup> among the smooth stones of the ravines are your portion;indeed, they are your lot.Yes, to them you have poured out drink offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18772N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18772N\"></sup>and offered grain offerings.In view of all this, should I relent?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18772O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18772O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You have made your bed on a high and lofty hill;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18773P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18773P\"></sup>there you went up to offer your sacrifices.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18773Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18773Q\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Behind your doors and your doorpostsyou have put your pagan symbols.Forsaking me, you uncovered your bed,you climbed into it and opened it wide;you made a pact with those whose beds you love,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18774R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18774R\"></sup>and you looked with lust on their naked bodies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18774S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18774S\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>You went to Molek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18775T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18775T\"></sup> with olive oiland increased your perfumes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18775U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18775U\"></sup>You sent your ambassadors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18775V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18775V\"></sup> far away;you descended to the very realm of the dead!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18775W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18775W\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>You wearied<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18776X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18776X\"></sup> yourself by such going about,but you would not say, ‘It is hopeless.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18776Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18776Y\"></sup>You found renewal of your strength,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18776Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18776Z\"></sup>and so you did not faint.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Whom have you so dreaded and feared<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18777AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18777AA\"></sup>that you have not been true to me,and have neither remembered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18777AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18777AB\"></sup> menor taken this to heart?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18777AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18777AC\"></sup>Is it not because I have long been silent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18777AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18777AD\"></sup>that you do not fear me?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will expose your righteousness and your works,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18778AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18778AE\"></sup>and they will not benefit you.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When you cry out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18779AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18779AF\"></sup> for help,let your collection of idols save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18779AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18779AG\"></sup> you!The wind will carry all of them off,a mere breath will blow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18779AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18779AH\"></sup> them away.But whoever takes refuge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18779AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18779AI\"></sup> in mewill inherit the land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18779AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18779AJ\"></sup>and possess my holy mountain.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18779AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18779AK\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And it will be said:“Build up, build up, prepare the road!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18780AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18780AL\"></sup>Remove the obstacles out of the way of my people.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18780AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18780AM\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For this is what the high and exalted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18781AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18781AN\"></sup> One says—he who lives forever,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18781AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18781AO\"></sup> whose name is holy:“I live in a high<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18781AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18781AP\"></sup> and holy place,but also with the one who is contrite<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18781AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18781AQ\"></sup> and lowly in spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18781AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18781AR\"></sup>to revive the spirit of the lowlyand to revive the heart of the contrite.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18781AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18781AS\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I will not accuse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18782AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18782AT\"></sup> them forever,nor will I always be angry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18782AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18782AU\"></sup>for then they would faint away because of me—the very people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18782AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18782AV\"></sup> I have created.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I was enraged by their sinful greed;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18783AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18783AW\"></sup>I punished them, and hid<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18783AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18783AX\"></sup> my face in anger,yet they kept on in their willful ways.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18783AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18783AY\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I have seen their ways, but I will heal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18784AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18784AZ\"></sup> them;I will guide<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18784BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18784BA\"></sup> them and restore comfort<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18784BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18784BB\"></sup> to Israel’s mourners,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>creating praise on their lips.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18785BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18785BC\"></sup>Peace, peace,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18785BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18785BD\"></sup> to those far and near,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18785BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18785BE\"></sup>says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. “And I will heal them.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But the wicked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18786BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18786BF\"></sup> are like the tossing sea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18786BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18786BG\"></sup>which cannot rest,whose waves cast up mire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18786BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18786BH\"></sup> and mud.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“There is no peace,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18787BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18787BI\"></sup> says my God, “for the wicked.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18787BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18787BJ\"></sup>"
		},
		"58": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">58 </span>“Shout it aloud,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18788A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18788A\"></sup> do not hold back.Raise your voice like a trumpet.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18788B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18788B\"></sup>Declare to my people their rebellion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18788C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18788C\"></sup>and to the descendants of Jacob their sins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18788D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18788D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For day after day they seek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18789E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18789E\"></sup> me out;they seem eager to know my ways,as if they were a nation that does what is rightand has not forsaken<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18789F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18789F\"></sup> the commands of its God.They ask me for just decisionsand seem eager for God to come near<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18789G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18789G\"></sup> them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>‘Why have we fasted,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18790H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18790H\"></sup> they say,‘and you have not seen it?Why have we humbled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18790I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18790I\"></sup> ourselves,and you have not noticed?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18790J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18790J\"></sup>“Yet on the day of your fasting, you do as you please<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18790K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18790K\"></sup>and exploit all your workers.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Your fasting ends in quarreling and strife,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18791L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18791L\"></sup>and in striking each other with wicked fists.You cannot fast as you do todayand expect your voice to be heard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18791M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18791M\"></sup> on high.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Is this the kind of fast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18792N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18792N\"></sup> I have chosen,only a day for people to humble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18792O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18792O\"></sup> themselves?Is it only for bowing one’s head like a reed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18792P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18792P\"></sup>and for lying in sackcloth and ashes?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18792Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18792Q\"></sup>Is that what you call a fast,a day acceptable to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Is not this the kind of fasting<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18793R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18793R\"></sup> I have chosen:to loose the chains of injustice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18793S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18793S\"></sup>and untie the cords of the yoke,to set the oppressed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18793T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18793T\"></sup> freeand break every yoke?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18793U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18793U\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Is it not to share your food with the hungry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18794V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18794V\"></sup>and to provide the poor wanderer with shelter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18794W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18794W\"></sup>—when you see the naked, to clothe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18794X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18794X\"></sup> them,and not to turn away from your own flesh and blood?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18794Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18794Y\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then your light will break forth like the dawn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18795Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18795Z\"></sup>and your healing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18795AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18795AA\"></sup> will quickly appear;then your righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18795AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18795AB\"></sup> will go before you,and the glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be your rear guard.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18795AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18795AC\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then you will call,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18796AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18796AD\"></sup> and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will answer;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18796AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18796AE\"></sup>you will cry for help, and he will say: Here am I.“If you do away with the yoke of oppression,with the pointing finger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18796AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18796AF\"></sup> and malicious talk,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18796AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18796AG\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and if you spend yourselves in behalf of the hungryand satisfy the needs of the oppressed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18797AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18797AH\"></sup>then your light<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18797AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18797AI\"></sup> will rise in the darkness,and your night will become like the noonday.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18797AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18797AJ\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will guide<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18798AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18798AK\"></sup> you always;he will satisfy your needs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18798AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18798AL\"></sup> in a sun-scorched land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18798AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18798AM\"></sup>and will strengthen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18798AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18798AN\"></sup> your frame.You will be like a well-watered garden,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18798AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18798AO\"></sup>like a spring<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18798AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18798AP\"></sup> whose waters never fail.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Your people will rebuild the ancient ruins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18799AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18799AQ\"></sup>and will raise up the age-old foundations;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18799AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18799AR\"></sup>you will be called Repairer of Broken Walls,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18799AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18799AS\"></sup>Restorer of Streets with Dwellings.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“If you keep your feet from breaking the Sabbath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18800AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18800AT\"></sup>and from doing as you please on my holy day,if you call the Sabbath a delight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18800AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18800AU\"></sup>and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s holy day honorable,and if you honor it by not going your own wayand not doing as you please or speaking idle words,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18800AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18800AV\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>then you will find your joy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18801AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18801AW\"></sup> in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and I will cause you to ride in triumph on the heights<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18801AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18801AX\"></sup> of the landand to feast on the inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18801AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18801AY\"></sup> of your father Jacob.”For the mouth of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18801AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18801AZ\"></sup>"
		},
		"59": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">59 </span>Surely the arm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18802A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18802A\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is not too short<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18802B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18802B\"></sup> to save,nor his ear too dull to hear.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18802C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18802C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But your iniquities have separated<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18803D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18803D\"></sup>you from your God;your sins have hidden his face from you,so that he will not hear.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18803E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18803E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For your hands are stained with blood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18804F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18804F\"></sup>your fingers with guilt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18804G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18804G\"></sup>Your lips have spoken falsely,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18804H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18804H\"></sup>and your tongue mutters wicked things.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>No one calls for justice;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18805I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18805I\"></sup>no one pleads a case with integrity.They rely<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18805J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18805J\"></sup> on empty arguments, they utter lies;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18805K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18805K\"></sup>they conceive trouble and give birth to evil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18805L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18805L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They hatch the eggs of vipers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18806M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18806M\"></sup>and spin a spider’s web.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18806N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18806N\"></sup>Whoever eats their eggs will die,and when one is broken, an adder is hatched.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Their cobwebs are useless for clothing;they cannot cover themselves with what they make.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18807O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18807O\"></sup>Their deeds are evil deeds,and acts of violence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18807P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18807P\"></sup> are in their hands.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Their feet rush into sin;they are swift to shed innocent blood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18808Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18808Q\"></sup>They pursue evil schemes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18808R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18808R\"></sup>acts of violence mark their ways.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18808S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18808S\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The way of peace they do not know;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18809T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18809T\"></sup>there is no justice in their paths.They have turned them into crooked roads;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18809U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18809U\"></sup>no one who walks along them will know peace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18809V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18809V\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So justice is far from us,and righteousness does not reach us.We look for light, but all is darkness;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18810W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18810W\"></sup>for brightness, but we walk in deep shadows.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Like the blind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18811X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18811X\"></sup> we grope along the wall,feeling our way like people without eyes.At midday we stumble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18811Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18811Y\"></sup> as if it were twilight;among the strong, we are like the dead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18811Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18811Z\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>We all growl like bears;we moan mournfully like doves.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18812AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18812AA\"></sup>We look for justice, but find none;for deliverance, but it is far away.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For our offenses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18813AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18813AB\"></sup> are many in your sight,and our sins testify<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18813AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18813AC\"></sup> against us.Our offenses are ever with us,and we acknowledge our iniquities:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18813AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18813AD\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>rebellion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18814AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18814AE\"></sup> and treachery against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,turning our backs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18814AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18814AF\"></sup> on our God,inciting revolt and oppression,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18814AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18814AG\"></sup>uttering lies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18814AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18814AH\"></sup> our hearts have conceived.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So justice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18815AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18815AI\"></sup> is driven back,and righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18815AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18815AJ\"></sup> stands at a distance;truth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18815AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18815AK\"></sup> has stumbled in the streets,honesty cannot enter.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Truth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18816AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18816AL\"></sup> is nowhere to be found,and whoever shuns evil becomes a prey.The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> looked and was displeasedthat there was no justice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18816AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18816AM\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He saw that there was no one,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18817AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18817AN\"></sup>he was appalled that there was no one to intervene;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18817AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18817AO\"></sup>so his own arm achieved salvation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18817AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18817AP\"></sup> for him,and his own righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18817AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18817AQ\"></sup> sustained him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He put on righteousness as his breastplate,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18818AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18818AR\"></sup>and the helmet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18818AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18818AS\"></sup> of salvation on his head;he put on the garments<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18818AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18818AT\"></sup> of vengeance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18818AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18818AU\"></sup>and wrapped himself in zeal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18818AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18818AV\"></sup> as in a cloak.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>According to what they have done,so will he repay<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18819AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18819AW\"></sup>wrath to his enemiesand retribution to his foes;he will repay the islands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18819AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18819AX\"></sup> their due.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>From the west,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18820AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18820AY\"></sup> people will fear the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and from the rising of the sun,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18820AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18820AZ\"></sup> they will revere his glory.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18820BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18820BA\"></sup>For he will come like a pent-up floodthat the breath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18820BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18820BB\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> drives along.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“The Redeemer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18821BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18821BC\"></sup> will come to Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18821BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18821BD\"></sup>to those in Jacob who repent of their sins,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18821BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18821BE\"></sup>declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“As for me, this is my covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18822BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18822BF\"></sup> with them,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. “My Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18822BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18822BG\"></sup> who is on you, will not depart from you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18822BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18822BH\"></sup> and my words that I have put in your mouth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18822BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18822BI\"></sup> will always be on your lips, on the lips of your children and on the lips of their descendants—from this time on and forever,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"60": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">60 </span>“Arise,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18823A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18823A\"></sup> shine, for your light<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18823B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18823B\"></sup> has come,and the glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18823C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18823C\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> rises upon you.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>See, darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18824D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18824D\"></sup> covers the earthand thick darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18824E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18824E\"></sup> is over the peoples,but the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> rises upon youand his glory appears over you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18825F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18825F\"></sup> will come to your light,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18825G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18825G\"></sup>and kings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18825H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18825H\"></sup> to the brightness of your dawn.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Lift up your eyes and look about you:All assemble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18826I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18826I\"></sup> and come to you;your sons come from afar,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18826J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18826J\"></sup>and your daughters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18826K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18826K\"></sup> are carried on the hip.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18826L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18826L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then you will look and be radiant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18827M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18827M\"></sup>your heart will throb and swell with joy;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18827N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18827N\"></sup>the wealth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18827O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18827O\"></sup> on the seas will be brought to you,to you the riches of the nations will come.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Herds of camels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18828P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18828P\"></sup> will cover your land,young camels of Midian<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18828Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18828Q\"></sup> and Ephah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18828R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18828R\"></sup>And all from Sheba<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18828S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18828S\"></sup> will come,bearing gold and incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18828T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18828T\"></sup>and proclaiming the praise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18828U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18828U\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>All Kedar’s<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18829V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18829V\"></sup> flocks will be gathered to you,the rams of Nebaioth will serve you;they will be accepted as offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18829W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18829W\"></sup> on my altar,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18829X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18829X\"></sup>and I will adorn my glorious temple.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18829Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18829Y\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Who are these<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18830Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18830Z\"></sup> that fly along like clouds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18830AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18830AA\"></sup>like doves to their nests?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Surely the islands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18831AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18831AB\"></sup> look to me;in the lead are the ships of Tarshish,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18831AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18831AC\"></sup>bringing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18831AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18831AD\"></sup> your children from afar,with their silver and gold,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18831AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18831AE\"></sup>to the honor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18831AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18831AF\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18831AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18831AG\"></sup> of Israel,for he has endowed you with splendor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18831AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18831AH\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Foreigners<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18832AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18832AI\"></sup> will rebuild your walls,and their kings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18832AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18832AJ\"></sup> will serve you.Though in anger I struck you,in favor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18832AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18832AK\"></sup> I will show you compassion.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18832AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18832AL\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Your gates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18833AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18833AM\"></sup> will always stand open,they will never be shut, day or night,so that people may bring you the wealth of the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18833AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18833AN\"></sup>—their kings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18833AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18833AO\"></sup> led in triumphal procession.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For the nation or kingdom that will not serve<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18834AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18834AP\"></sup> you will perish;it will be utterly ruined.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18834AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18834AQ\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“The glory of Lebanon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18835AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18835AR\"></sup> will come to you,the juniper, the fir and the cypress together,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18835AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18835AS\"></sup>to adorn my sanctuary;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18835AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18835AT\"></sup>and I will glorify the place for my feet.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18835AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18835AU\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The children of your oppressors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18836AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18836AV\"></sup> will come bowing before you;all who despise you will bow down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18836AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18836AW\"></sup> at your feetand will call you the City<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18836AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18836AX\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,Zion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18836AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18836AY\"></sup> of the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18836AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18836AZ\"></sup> of Israel.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Although you have been forsaken<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18837BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18837BA\"></sup> and hated,with no one traveling<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18837BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18837BB\"></sup> through,I will make you the everlasting pride<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18837BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18837BC\"></sup>and the joy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18837BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18837BD\"></sup> of all generations.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You will drink the milk of nationsand be nursed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18838BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18838BE\"></sup> at royal breasts.Then you will know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18838BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18838BF\"></sup> that I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, am your Savior,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18838BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18838BG\"></sup>your Redeemer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18838BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18838BH\"></sup> the Mighty One of Jacob.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18838BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18838BI\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Instead of bronze I will bring you gold,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18839BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18839BJ\"></sup>and silver in place of iron.Instead of wood I will bring you bronze,and iron in place of stones.I will make peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18839BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18839BK\"></sup> your governorand well-being your ruler.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18839BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18839BL\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>No longer will violence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18840BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18840BM\"></sup> be heard in your land,nor ruin or destruction<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18840BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18840BN\"></sup> within your borders,but you will call your walls Salvation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18840BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18840BO\"></sup>and your gates Praise.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18840BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18840BP\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The sun will no more be your light by day,nor will the brightness of the moon shine on you,for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be your everlasting light,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18841BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18841BQ\"></sup>and your God will be your glory.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18841BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18841BR\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Your sun<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18842BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18842BS\"></sup> will never set again,and your moon will wane no more;the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be your everlasting light,and your days of sorrow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18842BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18842BT\"></sup> will end.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then all your people will be righteous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18843BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18843BU\"></sup>and they will possess<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18843BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18843BV\"></sup> the land forever.They are the shoot I have planted,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18843BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18843BW\"></sup>the work of my hands,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18843BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18843BX\"></sup>for the display of my splendor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18843BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18843BY\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The least of you will become a thousand,the smallest a mighty nation.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18844BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18844BZ\"></sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;in its time I will do this swiftly.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18844CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18844CA\"></sup>"
		},
		"61": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">61 </span>The Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18845A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18845A\"></sup> of the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18845B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18845B\"></sup> is on me,because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has anointed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18845C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18845C\"></sup> meto proclaim good news<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18845D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18845D\"></sup> to the poor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18845E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18845E\"></sup>He has sent me to bind up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18845F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18845F\"></sup> the brokenhearted,to proclaim freedom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18845G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18845G\"></sup> for the captives<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18845H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18845H\"></sup>and release from darkness for the prisoners,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>to proclaim the year of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s favor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18846I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18846I\"></sup>and the day of vengeance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18846J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18846J\"></sup> of our God,to comfort<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18846K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18846K\"></sup> all who mourn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18846L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18846L\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>and provide for those who grieve in Zion—to bestow on them a crown<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18847M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18847M\"></sup> of beautyinstead of ashes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18847N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18847N\"></sup>the oil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18847O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18847O\"></sup> of joyinstead of mourning,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18847P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18847P\"></sup>and a garment of praiseinstead of a spirit of despair.They will be called oaks of righteousness,a planting<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18847Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18847Q\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>for the display of his splendor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18847R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18847R\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They will rebuild the ancient ruins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18848S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18848S\"></sup>and restore the places long devastated;they will renew the ruined citiesthat have been devastated for generations.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Strangers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18849T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18849T\"></sup> will shepherd your flocks;foreigners will work your fields and vineyards.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And you will be called priests<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18850U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18850U\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,you will be named ministers of our God.You will feed on the wealth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18850V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18850V\"></sup> of nations,and in their riches you will boast.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Instead of your shame<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18851W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18851W\"></sup>you will receive a double<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18851X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18851X\"></sup> portion,and instead of disgraceyou will rejoice in your inheritance.And so you will inherit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18851Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18851Y\"></sup> a double portion in your land,and everlasting joy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18851Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18851Z\"></sup> will be yours.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“For I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, love justice;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18852AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18852AA\"></sup>I hate robbery and wrongdoing.In my faithfulness I will reward my peopleand make an everlasting covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18852AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18852AB\"></sup> with them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Their descendants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18853AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18853AC\"></sup> will be known among the nationsand their offspring among the peoples.All who see them will acknowledgethat they are a people the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has blessed.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18853AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18853AD\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I delight greatly in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;my soul rejoices<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18854AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18854AE\"></sup> in my God.For he has clothed me with garments of salvationand arrayed me in a robe of his righteousness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18854AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18854AF\"></sup>as a bridegroom adorns his head<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18854AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18854AG\"></sup> like a priest,and as a bride<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18854AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18854AH\"></sup> adorns herself with her jewels.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For as the soil makes the sprout come upand a garden<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18855AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18855AI\"></sup> causes seeds to grow,so the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will make righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18855AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18855AJ\"></sup>and praise spring up before all nations."
		},
		"62": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">62 </span>For Zion’s sake I will not keep silent,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18856A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18856A\"></sup>for Jerusalem’s sake I will not remain quiet,till her vindication<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18856B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18856B\"></sup> shines out like the dawn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18856C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18856C\"></sup>her salvation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18856D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18856D\"></sup> like a blazing torch.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18857E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18857E\"></sup> will see your vindication,and all kings your glory;you will be called by a new name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18857F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18857F\"></sup>that the mouth of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will bestow.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You will be a crown<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18858G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18858G\"></sup> of splendor in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s hand,a royal diadem in the hand of your God.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>No longer will they call you Deserted,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18859H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18859H\"></sup>or name your land Desolate.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18859I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18859I\"></sup>But you will be called Hephzibah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18859J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18859J\"></sup>and your land Beulah;for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will take delight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18859K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18859K\"></sup> in you,and your land will be married.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18859L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18859L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>As a young man marries a young woman,so will your Builder marry you;as a bridegroom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18860M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18860M\"></sup> rejoices over his bride,so will your God rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18860N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18860N\"></sup> over you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I have posted watchmen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18861O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18861O\"></sup> on your walls, Jerusalem;they will never be silent day or night.You who call on the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,give yourselves no rest,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18861P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18861P\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and give him no rest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18862Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18862Q\"></sup> till he establishes Jerusalemand makes her the praise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18862R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18862R\"></sup> of the earth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has sworn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18863S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18863S\"></sup> by his right handand by his mighty arm:“Never again will I give your grain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18863T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18863T\"></sup>as food for your enemies,and never again will foreigners drink the new winefor which you have toiled;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>but those who harvest it will eat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18864U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18864U\"></sup> itand praise the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18864V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18864V\"></sup>and those who gather the grapes will drink itin the courts of my sanctuary.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18864W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18864W\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Pass through, pass through the gates!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18865X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18865X\"></sup>Prepare the way for the people.Build up, build up the highway!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18865Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18865Y\"></sup>Remove the stones.Raise a banner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18865Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18865Z\"></sup> for the nations.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has made proclamationto the ends of the earth:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18866AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18866AA\"></sup>“Say to Daughter Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18866AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18866AB\"></sup>‘See, your Savior comes!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18866AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18866AC\"></sup>See, his reward is with him,and his recompense accompanies him.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18866AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18866AD\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They will be called<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18867AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18867AE\"></sup> the Holy People,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18867AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18867AF\"></sup>the Redeemed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18867AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18867AG\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;and you will be called Sought After,the City No Longer Deserted.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18867AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18867AH\"></sup>"
		},
		"63": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">63 </span>Who is this coming from Edom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18868A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18868A\"></sup>from Bozrah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18868B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18868B\"></sup> with his garments stained crimson?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18868C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18868C\"></sup>Who is this, robed in splendor,striding forward in the greatness of his strength?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18868D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18868D\"></sup>“It is I, proclaiming victory,mighty to save.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18868E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18868E\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Why are your garments red,like those of one treading the winepress?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18869F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18869F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“I have trodden the winepress<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18870G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18870G\"></sup> alone;from the nations no one was with me.I trampled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18870H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18870H\"></sup> them in my angerand trod them down in my wrath;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18870I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18870I\"></sup>their blood spattered my garments,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18870J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18870J\"></sup>and I stained all my clothing.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>It was for me the day of vengeance;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18871K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18871K\"></sup>the year for me to redeem had come.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I looked, but there was no one<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18872L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18872L\"></sup> to help,I was appalled that no one gave support;so my own arm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18872M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18872M\"></sup> achieved salvation for me,and my own wrath sustained me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18872N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18872N\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I trampled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18873O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18873O\"></sup> the nations in my anger;in my wrath I made them drunk<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18873P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18873P\"></sup>and poured their blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18873Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18873Q\"></sup> on the ground.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I will tell of the kindnesses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18874R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18874R\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,the deeds for which he is to be praised,according to all the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has done for us—yes, the many good things<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18874S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18874S\"></sup>he has done for Israel,according to his compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18874T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18874T\"></sup> and many kindnesses.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He said, “Surely they are my people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18875U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18875U\"></sup>children who will be true to me”;and so he became their Savior.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18875V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18875V\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>In all their distress he too was distressed,and the angel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18876W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18876W\"></sup> of his presence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18876X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18876X\"></sup> saved them.In his love and mercy he redeemed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18876Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18876Y\"></sup> them;he lifted them up and carried<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18876Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18876Z\"></sup> themall the days of old.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18876AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18876AA\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Yet they rebelled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18877AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18877AB\"></sup>and grieved his Holy Spirit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18877AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18877AC\"></sup>So he turned and became their enemy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18877AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18877AD\"></sup>and he himself fought<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18877AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18877AE\"></sup> against them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then his people recalled the days of old,the days of Moses and his people—where is he who brought them through the sea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18878AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18878AF\"></sup>with the shepherd of his flock?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18878AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18878AG\"></sup>Where is he who sethis Holy Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18878AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18878AH\"></sup> among them,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>who sent his glorious arm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18879AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18879AI\"></sup> of powerto be at Moses’ right hand,who divided the waters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18879AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18879AJ\"></sup> before them,to gain for himself everlasting renown,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18879AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18879AK\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>who led<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18880AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18880AL\"></sup> them through the depths?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18880AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18880AM\"></sup>Like a horse in open country,they did not stumble;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18880AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18880AN\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>like cattle that go down to the plain,they were given rest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18881AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18881AO\"></sup> by the Spirit of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.This is how you guided your peopleto make for yourself a glorious name.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Look down from heaven<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18882AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18882AP\"></sup> and see,from your lofty throne,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18882AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18882AQ\"></sup> holy and glorious.Where are your zeal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18882AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18882AR\"></sup> and your might?Your tenderness and compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18882AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18882AS\"></sup> are withheld<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18882AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18882AT\"></sup> from us.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But you are our Father,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18883AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18883AU\"></sup>though Abraham does not know usor Israel acknowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18883AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18883AV\"></sup> us;you, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, are our Father,our Redeemer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18883AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18883AW\"></sup> from of old is your name.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Why, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, do you make us wander<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18884AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18884AX\"></sup> from your waysand harden our hearts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18884AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18884AY\"></sup> so we do not revere<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18884AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18884AZ\"></sup> you?Return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18884BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18884BA\"></sup> for the sake of your servants,the tribes that are your inheritance.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18884BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18884BB\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For a little while<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18885BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18885BC\"></sup> your people possessed your holy place,but now our enemies have trampled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18885BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18885BD\"></sup> down your sanctuary.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18885BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18885BE\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>We are yours from of old;but you have not ruled over them,they have not been called by your name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18886BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18886BF\"></sup>"
		},
		"64": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">64 </span>Oh, that you would rend the heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18887A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18887A\"></sup> and come down,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18887B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18887B\"></sup>that the mountains<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18887C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18887C\"></sup> would tremble before you!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>As when fire sets twigs ablazeand causes water to boil,come down to make your name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18888D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18888D\"></sup> known to your enemiesand cause the nations to quake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18888E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18888E\"></sup> before you!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For when you did awesome<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18889F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18889F\"></sup> things that we did not expect,you came down, and the mountains trembled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18889G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18889G\"></sup> before you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Since ancient times no one has heard,no ear has perceived,no eye has seen any God besides you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18890H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18890H\"></sup>who acts on behalf of those who wait for him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18890I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18890I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You come to the help of those who gladly do right,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18891J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18891J\"></sup>who remember your ways.But when we continued to sin against them,you were angry.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18891K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18891K\"></sup>How then can we be saved?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>All of us have become like one who is unclean,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18892L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18892L\"></sup>and all our righteous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18892M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18892M\"></sup> acts are like filthy rags;we all shrivel up like a leaf,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18892N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18892N\"></sup>and like the wind our sins sweep us away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18892O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18892O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>No one<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18893P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18893P\"></sup> calls on your name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18893Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18893Q\"></sup>or strives to lay hold of you;for you have hidden<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18893R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18893R\"></sup> your face from usand have given us over<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18893S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18893S\"></sup> to our sins.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Yet you, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, are our Father.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18894T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18894T\"></sup>We are the clay, you are the potter;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18894U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18894U\"></sup>we are all the work of your hand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18894V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18894V\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Do not be angry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18895W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18895W\"></sup> beyond measure, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;do not remember our sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18895X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18895X\"></sup> forever.Oh, look on us, we pray,for we are all your people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18895Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18895Y\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Your sacred cities<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18896Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18896Z\"></sup> have become a wasteland;even Zion is a wasteland, Jerusalem a desolation.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18896AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18896AA\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Our holy and glorious temple,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18897AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18897AB\"></sup> where our ancestors praised you,has been burned with fire,and all that we treasured<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18897AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18897AC\"></sup> lies in ruins.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>After all this, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, will you hold yourself back?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18898AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18898AD\"></sup>Will you keep silent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18898AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18898AE\"></sup> and punish us beyond measure?"
		},
		"65": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">65 </span>“I revealed myself to those who did not ask for me;I was found by those who did not seek me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18899A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18899A\"></sup>To a nation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18899B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18899B\"></sup> that did not call on my name,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18899C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18899C\"></sup>I said, ‘Here am I, here am I.’",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>All day long I have held out my handsto an obstinate people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18900D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18900D\"></sup>who walk in ways not good,pursuing their own imaginations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18900E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18900E\"></sup>—",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>a people who continually provoke meto my very face,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18901F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18901F\"></sup>offering sacrifices in gardens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18901G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18901G\"></sup>and burning incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18901H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18901H\"></sup> on altars of brick;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>who sit among the graves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18902I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18902I\"></sup>and spend their nights keeping secret vigil;who eat the flesh of pigs,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18902J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18902J\"></sup>and whose pots hold broth of impure meat;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>who say, ‘Keep away; don’t come near me,for I am too sacred<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18903K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18903K\"></sup> for you!’Such people are smoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18903L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18903L\"></sup> in my nostrils,a fire that keeps burning all day.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“See, it stands written before me:I will not keep silent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18904M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18904M\"></sup> but will pay back<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18904N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18904N\"></sup> in full;I will pay it back into their laps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18904O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18904O\"></sup>—",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>both your sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18905P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18905P\"></sup> and the sins of your ancestors,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18905Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18905Q\"></sup>says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“Because they burned sacrifices on the mountainsand defied me on the hills,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18905R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18905R\"></sup>I will measure into their lapsthe full payment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18905S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18905S\"></sup> for their former deeds.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“As when juice is still found in a cluster of grapes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18906T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18906T\"></sup>and people say, ‘Don’t destroy it,there is still a blessing in it,’so will I do in behalf of my servants;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18906U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18906U\"></sup>I will not destroy them all.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will bring forth descendants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18907V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18907V\"></sup> from Jacob,and from Judah those who will possess<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18907W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18907W\"></sup> my mountains;my chosen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18907X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18907X\"></sup> people will inherit them,and there will my servants live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18907Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18907Y\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Sharon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18908Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18908Z\"></sup> will become a pasture for flocks,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18908AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18908AA\"></sup>and the Valley of Achor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18908AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18908AB\"></sup> a resting place for herds,for my people who seek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18908AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18908AC\"></sup> me.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“But as for you who forsake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18909AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18909AD\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and forget my holy mountain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18909AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18909AE\"></sup>who spread a table for Fortuneand fill bowls of mixed wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18909AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18909AF\"></sup> for Destiny,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will destine you for the sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18910AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18910AG\"></sup>and all of you will fall in the slaughter;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18910AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18910AH\"></sup>for I called but you did not answer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18910AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18910AI\"></sup>I spoke but you did not listen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18910AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18910AJ\"></sup>You did evil in my sightand chose what displeases me.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18910AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18910AK\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore this is what the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“My servants will eat,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18911AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18911AL\"></sup>but you will go hungry;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18911AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18911AM\"></sup>my servants will drink,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18911AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18911AN\"></sup>but you will go thirsty;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18911AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18911AO\"></sup>my servants will rejoice,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18911AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18911AP\"></sup>but you will be put to shame.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18911AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18911AQ\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>My servants will sing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18912AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18912AR\"></sup>out of the joy of their hearts,but you will cry out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18912AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18912AS\"></sup>from anguish of heartand wail in brokenness of spirit.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>You will leave your namefor my chosen ones to use in their curses;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18913AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18913AT\"></sup>the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will put you to death,but to his servants he will give another name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18913AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18913AU\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Whoever invokes a blessing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18914AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18914AV\"></sup> in the landwill do so by the one true God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18914AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18914AW\"></sup>whoever takes an oath in the landwill swear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18914AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18914AX\"></sup> by the one true God.For the past troubles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18914AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18914AY\"></sup> will be forgottenand hidden from my eyes.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“See, I will createnew heavens and a new earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18915AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18915AZ\"></sup>The former things will not be remembered,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18915BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18915BA\"></sup>nor will they come to mind.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But be glad and rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18916BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18916BB\"></sup> foreverin what I will create,for I will create Jerusalem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18916BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18916BC\"></sup> to be a delightand its people a joy.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I will rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18917BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18917BD\"></sup> over Jerusalemand take delight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18917BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18917BE\"></sup> in my people;the sound of weeping and of crying<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18917BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18917BF\"></sup>will be heard in it no more.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Never again will there be in itan infant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18918BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18918BG\"></sup> who lives but a few days,or an old man who does not live out his years;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18918BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18918BH\"></sup>the one who dies at a hundredwill be thought a mere child;the one who fails to reach a hundredwill be considered accursed.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>They will build houses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18919BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18919BI\"></sup> and dwell in them;they will plant vineyards and eat their fruit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18919BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18919BJ\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>No longer will they build houses and others live in them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18920BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18920BK\"></sup>or plant and others eat.For as the days of a tree,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18920BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18920BL\"></sup>so will be the days<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18920BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18920BM\"></sup> of my people;my chosen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18920BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18920BN\"></sup> ones will long enjoythe work of their hands.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>They will not labor in vain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18921BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18921BO\"></sup>nor will they bear children doomed to misfortune;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18921BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18921BP\"></sup>for they will be a people blessed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18921BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18921BQ\"></sup> by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,they and their descendants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18921BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18921BR\"></sup> with them.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Before they call<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18922BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18922BS\"></sup> I will answer;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18922BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18922BT\"></sup>while they are still speaking<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18922BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18922BU\"></sup> I will hear.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The wolf and the lamb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18923BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18923BV\"></sup> will feed together,and the lion will eat straw like the ox,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18923BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18923BW\"></sup>and dust will be the serpent’s<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18923BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18923BX\"></sup> food.They will neither harm nor destroyon all my holy mountain,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18923BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18923BY\"></sup>says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"66": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">66 </span>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“Heaven is my throne,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18924A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18924A\"></sup>and the earth is my footstool.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18924B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18924B\"></sup>Where is the house<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18924C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18924C\"></sup> you will build for me?Where will my resting place be?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Has not my hand made all these things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18925D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18925D\"></sup>and so they came into being?”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“These are the ones I look on with favor:those who are humble and contrite in spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18925E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18925E\"></sup>and who tremble at my word.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18925F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18925F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But whoever sacrifices a bull<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18926G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18926G\"></sup>is like one who kills a person,and whoever offers a lambis like one who breaks a dog’s neck;whoever makes a grain offeringis like one who presents pig’s<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18926H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18926H\"></sup> blood,and whoever burns memorial incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18926I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18926I\"></sup>is like one who worships an idol.They have chosen their own ways,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18926J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18926J\"></sup>and they delight in their abominations;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18926K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18926K\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>so I also will choose harsh treatment for themand will bring on them what they dread.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18927L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18927L\"></sup>For when I called, no one answered,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18927M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18927M\"></sup>when I spoke, no one listened.They did evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18927N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18927N\"></sup> in my sightand chose what displeases me.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18927O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18927O\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,you who tremble at his word:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18928P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18928P\"></sup>“Your own people who hate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18928Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18928Q\"></sup> you,and exclude you because of my name, have said,‘Let the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> be glorified,that we may see your joy!’Yet they will be put to shame.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18928R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18928R\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Hear that uproar from the city,hear that noise from the temple!It is the sound<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18929S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18929S\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>repaying<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18929T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18929T\"></sup> his enemies all they deserve.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Before she goes into labor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18930U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18930U\"></sup>she gives birth;before the pains come upon her,she delivers a son.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18930V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18930V\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Who has ever heard of such things?Who has ever seen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18931W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18931W\"></sup> things like this?Can a country be born in a day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18931X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18931X\"></sup>or a nation be brought forth in a moment?Yet no sooner is Zion in laborthan she gives birth to her children.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18931Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18931Y\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Do I bring to the moment of birth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18932Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18932Z\"></sup>and not give delivery?” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“Do I close up the wombwhen I bring to delivery?” says your God.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18933AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18933AA\"></sup> with Jerusalem and be glad for her,all you who love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18933AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18933AB\"></sup> her;rejoice greatly with her,all you who mourn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18933AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18933AC\"></sup> over her.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For you will nurse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18934AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18934AD\"></sup> and be satisfiedat her comforting breasts;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18934AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18934AE\"></sup>you will drink deeplyand delight in her overflowing abundance.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18934AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18934AF\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“I will extend peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18935AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18935AG\"></sup> to her like a river,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18935AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18935AH\"></sup>and the wealth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18935AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18935AI\"></sup> of nations like a flooding stream;you will nurse and be carried<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18935AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18935AJ\"></sup> on her armand dandled on her knees.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>As a mother comforts her child,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18936AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18936AK\"></sup>so will I comfort<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18936AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18936AL\"></sup> you;and you will be comforted over Jerusalem.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>When you see this, your heart will rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18937AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18937AM\"></sup>and you will flourish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18937AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18937AN\"></sup> like grass;the hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18937AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18937AO\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be made known to his servants,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18937AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18937AP\"></sup>but his fury<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18937AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18937AQ\"></sup> will be shown to his foes.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>See, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is coming with fire,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18938AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18938AR\"></sup>and his chariots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18938AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18938AS\"></sup> are like a whirlwind;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18938AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18938AT\"></sup>he will bring down his anger with fury,and his rebuke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18938AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18938AU\"></sup> with flames of fire.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For with fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18939AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18939AV\"></sup> and with his sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18939AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18939AW\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will execute judgment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18939AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18939AX\"></sup> on all people,and many will be those slain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18939AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18939AY\"></sup> by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Those who consecrate and purify themselves to go into the gardens,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18940AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18940AZ\"></sup> following one who is among those who eat the flesh of pigs,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18940BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18940BA\"></sup> rats<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18940BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18940BB\"></sup> and other unclean things—they will meet their end<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18940BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18940BC\"></sup> together with the one they follow,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“And I, because of what they have planned and done,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18941BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18941BD\"></sup> am about to come and gather the people of all nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18941BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18941BE\"></sup> and languages, and they will come and see my glory.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18941BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18941BF\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“I will set a sign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18942BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18942BG\"></sup> among them, and I will send some of those who survive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18942BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18942BH\"></sup> to the nations—to Tarshish,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18942BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18942BI\"></sup> to the Libyans and Lydians<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18942BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18942BJ\"></sup> (famous as archers), to Tubal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18942BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18942BK\"></sup> and Greece,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18942BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18942BL\"></sup> and to the distant islands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18942BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18942BM\"></sup> that have not heard of my fame or seen my glory.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18942BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18942BN\"></sup> They will proclaim my glory among the nations.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And they will bring<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18943BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18943BO\"></sup> all your people, from all the nations, to my holy mountain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18943BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18943BP\"></sup> in Jerusalem as an offering to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>—on horses, in chariots and wagons, and on mules and camels,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18943BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18943BQ\"></sup> says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. “They will bring them, as the Israelites bring their grain offerings, to the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in ceremonially clean vessels.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18943BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18943BR\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And I will select some of them also to be priests<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18944BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18944BS\"></sup> and Levites,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“As the new heavens and the new earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18945BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18945BT\"></sup> that I make will endure before me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “so will your name and descendants endure.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18945BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18945BU\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>From one New Moon to another and from one Sabbath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18946BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18946BV\"></sup> to another, all mankind will come and bow down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18946BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18946BW\"></sup> before me,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“And they will go out and look on the dead bodies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18947BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18947BX\"></sup> of those who rebelled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18947BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18947BY\"></sup> against me; the worms<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18947BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18947BZ\"></sup> that eat them will not die, the fire that burns them will not be quenched,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18947CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18947CA\"></sup> and they will be loathsome to all mankind.”"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;